1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedva sam i našao,dugo sam i tražio u toj ruševini, znači oni su progladnici iz Posavine, bili su pola godine pod mostom, znači hrvatski branitelj koji bio u KVO-u, bio je ranjen.

2
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nazvao mi je, rekao da ima jedan dida u Zagoru, žive, nekoj šumi. Auto sam sijeo, kupio hrane i krenio tražiti dida Franja.

3
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Došao sam u jedno selo, Sveti Križ Začrtje, ubrdo gori kroz šumu, došao sam do njega i dan danas ta slika mi se toliko urezala.

4
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dragi prijatelji, danas idemo jako, evo ja moram reći svi do sadašnji podcasti bili su mi dragi, nek se niko ne naljuti,

5
00:00:49,000 --> 00:01:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali ovaj današnji bit će mi najdražiji jer sa mnom su moja dva prijatelja i ja s ponosom mogu reći prijatelja jer radi se o braniteljima koji svoj braniteljski poziv žive čitav život.

6
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo su bili u ratu, a nakon rata svojim velikim humantarnim radom i dalje pomažu svojoj domovini.

7
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najviše kroz katoličku udrugu KAB Dobrote, čiji su članovi i s kojima smo mi nedavno i potpisali suradnju, te i to jedan od povoda ove emisije.

8
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jako su zanimljivi, tako da uvjerit ćete se i sami, ostanite s nama. Sa mnom su Marinko Šušak i Vinko Franković. Evo mladići, dobrodošli.

9
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala na pozivu. Hvala na pozivu. Evo, hvala nisu Marija, draga sestro, u Kristu i Hrvatskom rodu, evo da pozdravimo sve dobre ljude.

10
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drago nešto se nas pozvao naš brat Marin da budemo tvoji gosti, evo nešto ćemo reći mi o našem putu u domovini, tako i sada.

11
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sada ste puno bili na radiju, Vinko je vodio emisiju na radio Marija dugo godina, ali sada ste prvi put malo u podcast formi. Vjerujem, vjerujem da ćete biti zanimljivi.

12
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo odmah krenuti malo na suradnju Kapi Dobrote i Mladi za domovinu. Znači, mi smo s vama surađivali najviše na cijepanju drva i potom nekako naši mladi znaju Kap Dobrote.

13
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, ako vi možete ispričat malo što je to Kap Dobrote i ko je pater Antun Cvek, znači zval su ga Dobri dug Zagreba, pokrenuje Kap Dobrote, evo može možda Vinko ispričat okvirno o pateru Cveku i što radite.

14
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:44,000
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ovako, pater Cvek je 1990. formalno, zajedno sa svojim suradnicima, dakle ne samo on nego i suradnici, su osnovali katoličku udrugu Kap Dobrote,

15
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:56,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ali je on u istom smislu dijelovao i prijatelja, zajedno sa svojim suradnicima, kao pripadnik Hrvatskog isusovačkog reda.

16
00:02:56,000 --> 00:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_02] Statut Kap Dobrote jasno kaže da je to udruga koja brine o starim, ali i nemoćnim osobama. Zašto to govorim?

17
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:14,000
[SPEAKER_02] Zato što može biti mlađa osoba koja se ne može brinuti o sebi, a nema nikoga ko bi o njoj brinuo.

18
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:23,000
[SPEAKER_02] Znači mi brinemo onima koji ne mogu o sebi brinuti, a nemaju nikoga ko bi o njima mogao brinuti.

19
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:28,000
[SPEAKER_02] Pater Cvek je znao reći da mi idemo oko njima i tamo gdje više niko ne ide.

20
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Marinko bi znao reći najveća sirotinja grada Zagreba.

21
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:47,000
[SPEAKER_02] Da, ono što je mene i mnoge druge koji smo u toj udruzi privuklo je da u onom trenutku kad naš brat ili naša sestra u nevolji postane i naš korisnik,

22
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:57,000
[SPEAKER_02] u tom trenutku on ili sestra naša postaje, sve njihove brige postavi i brige kapi dobrote.

23
00:03:57,000 --> 00:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_02] Znači naša briga o njima i zaštita njih je stalna i potpuna.

24
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:20,000
[SPEAKER_02] Šta to znači? To znači da ukoliko neka osoba postane naš korisnik u nevolji u kojoj se nalazi, mi ne kažemo e, mi ćemo ti to riješiti, a za ove stvari mi nismo, to ćeš morati tražiti negdje drugo, nismo mi za to.

25
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:42,439
[SPEAKER_02] Sve njihove nevolje postaju i nevolje kapi dobrote. Ono što mi ne možemo riješiti ljudskim i materijalnim i duhovnim snagama, rješavamo pomoću naših podupiratelja, dobrih ljudi, liječnika, odvjetnika i drugih koji nam pomažu i tako zajedno sa njima smo naravno jači,

26
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:54,439
[SPEAKER_02] i izravno i neizravno koliko više možemo, pomažemo ih i štitimo, kažem, uvjetovani ljudskim i materijalnim i duhovnim sredstvima.

27
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:56,439
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to bi...

28
00:04:56,439 --> 00:05:00,439
[SPEAKER_00] Neko dvijesto štićenika, je li tako? Na 80 volantez.

29
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:10,439
[SPEAKER_02] Ja inače više volim, ja mislim da je to prirodno materijski jezik nego strani jezik i ako poštijem, znam prilično dobro engleski,

30
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:19,899
[SPEAKER_02] pa mi znamo reći da smo mi dragovoljci kapi dobrote jer je to najtočnijek prijevod riječi volonter.

31
00:05:19,899 --> 00:05:28,560
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, to bi ja rekao ukratko o našoj udruži i mogu reći šta me je privuklo da dođem u kap dobrote.

32
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:38,639
[SPEAKER_02] Jeste kratko na pitanje Isusu Kristu, koja je najveća zapovjed, on je odgovorio, dakle zapovjed, ne prijedlog, nego zapovjed.

33
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:44,300
[SPEAKER_02] A zapovjed je nešto što se ima izvršiti bez odgađanja i bez raspravi.

34
00:05:44,300 --> 00:05:48,100
[SPEAKER_02] Znači on je to nama dao u obliku zapovjedi, ne prijedloga.

35
00:05:48,779 --> 00:05:53,060
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubiti Boga svim srcem, svojim, svom dušom, svojom i svim umom svojim.

36
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:56,420
[SPEAKER_02] A bližnjega svoga kako? Kao samoga sebe.

37
00:05:56,420 --> 00:06:04,000
[SPEAKER_02] To je bio moj motiv da kao vjernik, kršćanin, ako u te dvije zapovjedi, kako je rekao Isus,

38
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:11,279
[SPEAKER_02] da je sav Božji zakon i svi proroci, da ja moram uvažiti i jednu, ali i ovu drugu zapovjed.

39
00:06:11,279 --> 00:06:19,579
[SPEAKER_02] I drugi razlog koji mi Bog daje preko razuma je staj da su meni mnogi ljudi u životu pomogli,

40
00:06:19,579 --> 00:06:25,060
[SPEAKER_02] Bog mi je mnogo puta pomogo, od drugih sam u nevolji tražio pomoć,

41
00:06:25,060 --> 00:06:28,259
[SPEAKER_02] i od poznatih i nepoznatih na cesti ili bilo gdje drugo,

42
00:06:28,259 --> 00:06:33,939
[SPEAKER_02] i samim tim smatrao sam se da sam i ja dužan, poznatim i nepoznatim,

43
00:06:33,939 --> 00:06:38,620
[SPEAKER_02] koji su ne volji, ako mogu, pomoći onoliko koliko mogu.

44
00:06:38,620 --> 00:06:40,720
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, u kratko, ja toliko.

45
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:44,060
[SPEAKER_00] Marink, imaš lišta možda da dodati o samoj kapi,

46
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:46,759
[SPEAKER_00] a što se tiče tih nekih stvarno teških slučajeva,

47
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:50,540
[SPEAKER_00] kojih ima jako puno, možemo detaljnije se kasnije nadovezati,

48
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali sad samo da ljudi koji možda nisu čuli za kap, dobro, ote.

49
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:59,639
[SPEAKER_01] Da, u kratkim crtama, kao vojnik se predstavio, znači,

50
00:06:59,639 --> 00:07:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] dragovoljac domovinskog rata u mirovni časni hrvatske vojske,

51
00:07:03,259 --> 00:07:06,560
[SPEAKER_01] ja znam ovako reći, da sam bio dvadeset nešto godina

52
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:10,379
[SPEAKER_01] profesionalni hrvatski vojnik, sad se trudim biti boži vojnik,

53
00:07:10,379 --> 00:07:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] gospin vojnik.

54
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:14,639
[SPEAKER_01] Znači mi, evo, vin ko ja, smo dragovoljci,

55
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:16,220
[SPEAKER_01] poznali smo se u kap i dobrote,

56
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:19,180
[SPEAKER_01] vidjali smo se ovako za vrijeme rata,

57
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:24,560
[SPEAKER_01] nismo se poznavali, božom providno sam došao u kap dobrote,

58
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:29,100
[SPEAKER_01] znao sam za tu udrugu, već sam ja prija i volontirao i pomagao.

59
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste li nam voljan općenito svoj dragovoljački,

60
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi bilo da ispravno reći, put ispričat od samog rata?

61
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:42,839
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam reći da smo mi domovinu branili na prvoj crti bojižnice,

62
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] znači evo, sad se trudimo braniti našu domovinu,

63
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:49,139
[SPEAKER_01] isto na prvoj crti bojižnice sa našim siromasima,

64
00:07:49,139 --> 00:07:51,660
[SPEAKER_01] koji su napušteni, ostalih koji nema i nikog svoga.

65
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:53,860
[SPEAKER_01] Naša udruga se izrešta u takim,

66
00:07:53,860 --> 00:07:56,600
[SPEAKER_01] a ja ne znam da li postoji u Hrvatskoj jedna slična udruga

67
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:58,759
[SPEAKER_01] koja se bavi ovako šire,

68
00:07:58,759 --> 00:08:01,339
[SPEAKER_01] znači ne samo za bojižnice, ne za uskrs,

69
00:08:01,339 --> 00:08:05,300
[SPEAKER_01] nego 24 sata, 365 dana u godini.

70
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:08,480
[SPEAKER_01] Jedno vrijeme smo imali, ali i sada kad se nešto dogodim

71
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:11,220
[SPEAKER_01] i SOS tim, tako ga je nazvao Pater Cvek,

72
00:08:11,220 --> 00:08:15,040
[SPEAKER_01] gdje smo mi znali u polnoći, ujutru ići kod bolesnika,

73
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:18,139
[SPEAKER_01] koji je pavo iza kreveta, išli smo mu pomoći

74
00:08:18,139 --> 00:08:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] da ga dignemo i da ga odvezemo u bolnicu i tako.

75
00:08:21,019 --> 00:08:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, dragovolja, mene moje srce način mobilizirala domovina.

76
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:28,980
[SPEAKER_01] To je usađeno u mene, ja sam to sa svojim majčinim mlinkom

77
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:32,639
[SPEAKER_01] podoio, usađeno u mene, i bogoljube, i domoljube.

78
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:36,879
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam odlazio prije 40 godina iz širokog Vriga,

79
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:38,740
[SPEAKER_01] iz moje svijete Hercegovine u Zagreb,

80
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] odveo me sport i školovanje,

81
00:08:40,980 --> 00:08:43,840
[SPEAKER_01] moj pokojni čača Jozo mi je ovako rekao,

82
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:46,559
[SPEAKER_01] sine, di god moreš, ko me moreš pomozi.

83
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:50,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ja u svoje sedme godine volontiram, kad nekom tako pitanem,

84
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:52,279
[SPEAKER_01] odkada volontiran i kom je uzor.

85
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:55,559
[SPEAKER_01] Da li mi je uzor pater Cvek, da li je majka Terezija?

86
00:08:55,559 --> 00:08:57,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vajem, kako će mi neko biti uzor,

87
00:08:57,820 --> 00:08:59,679
[SPEAKER_01] kojega nikaj u životu nisam upoznao,

88
00:08:59,679 --> 00:09:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] majka Terezija, počitao sam puno knjiga o njoj,

89
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:05,080
[SPEAKER_01] s patron Cvek, on je usvrđivali smo,

90
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,580
[SPEAKER_01] znači skoro blizu 15 godina,

91
00:09:06,659 --> 00:09:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] vinko ja, usko.

92
00:09:08,019 --> 00:09:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Moj pokojni čača Jozo je moj uzor.

93
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:15,340
[SPEAKER_01] On me od malih nogu učio, mi smo u selu imali dosta žena,

94
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:19,360
[SPEAKER_01] udovica koje su izgubile muževe, od malih nogu da idem pomagati,

95
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:23,279
[SPEAKER_01] što cipati drva, što donijeti iz podruma drva,

96
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:27,620
[SPEAKER_01] iz šupe, što otići na potok donijeti im vodu i tako.

97
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,779
[SPEAKER_01] Znači od malih nogu.

98
00:09:28,779 --> 00:09:31,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ta rič što je meni moj pokojni čača,

99
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] umro je prije dvije godine pokojima duši,

100
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:36,440
[SPEAKER_01] je moj uzor u životu koji je uvijek pomagao,

101
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,080
[SPEAKER_01] gdje god mogao.

102
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:40,139
[SPEAKER_01] Tako ja trudim se, evo, biti uzor u svoju obitelj,

103
00:09:40,139 --> 00:09:42,580
[SPEAKER_01] imam predivnu obitelj, četvr rodice.

104
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] Nedavno sam postao i dida, imam dvije unuke,

105
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,600
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je blagosovio.

106
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,779
[SPEAKER_01] To je smisao našeg žvota, evo,

107
00:09:48,779 --> 00:09:51,039
[SPEAKER_01] za u našu svetu, domovnu Hrvatsku,

108
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:52,879
[SPEAKER_01] za koju se velika krv prosuva.

109
00:09:53,399 --> 00:09:56,419
[SPEAKER_01] Ti sjerumasi nas kao ljude upozmjenjuju puno puta,

110
00:09:56,419 --> 00:09:57,519
[SPEAKER_01] ja znam ovako reći,

111
00:09:57,519 --> 00:10:00,500
[SPEAKER_01] stostruh ko sam više dobio nego što sam dao,

112
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:01,360
[SPEAKER_01] ne umatrijalno.

113
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:03,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ta suza tog sjerumaha,

114
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] ta toplina, kad uđem u te njihove podrume,

115
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,279
[SPEAKER_01] to je hladno, vlaga je sve,

116
00:10:08,279 --> 00:10:10,320
[SPEAKER_01] a toplina srca osjetiš toplinu

117
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:12,279
[SPEAKER_01] i kad ta suza tog sjerumaha,

118
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] kad te dotakne,

119
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:15,179
[SPEAKER_01] kad je zahvali, rekne,

120
00:10:15,179 --> 00:10:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] treba mi čovjek i budi čovjek.

121
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,820
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je moja nit vodilja u životu

122
00:10:18,820 --> 00:10:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] i trudim se to nekako prenijeti

123
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:22,240
[SPEAKER_01] i na svoju obitelj.

124
00:10:22,259 --> 00:10:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] A to se stvarno vidi,

125
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,179
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam, Vinko,

126
00:10:24,179 --> 00:10:25,100
[SPEAKER_00] isi ti ikad čuo,

127
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] pričao sam s nekim širokobriježanima,

128
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] Marinko ima nadimak presveti

129
00:10:29,139 --> 00:10:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] u svom kvartu,

130
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:31,820
[SPEAKER_00] u širokom brijegu,

131
00:10:31,820 --> 00:10:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] tako da to stvarno nešto govori.

132
00:10:34,179 --> 00:10:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] A Vinko, evo,

133
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] tvoj put, koliko si ti dugo u Kapi Dobrote

134
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] i možeš na maloj utom smije.

135
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:41,240
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ja imam jednu knjigu,

136
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] gdje bude rečeno bilježnicu,

137
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:45,019
[SPEAKER_02] koju je to Bog čudno,

138
00:10:45,019 --> 00:10:46,220
[SPEAKER_02] Bog je meni,

139
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:47,240
[SPEAKER_02] ja vjerujem i Marinku,

140
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,960
[SPEAKER_02] dao puno znakova

141
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,120
[SPEAKER_02] u tom radu,

142
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:50,980
[SPEAKER_02] Kapi Dobrote.

143
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:52,820
[SPEAKER_02] Pa evo jedan je taj znak,

144
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:55,039
[SPEAKER_02] ja ovako od svoje obitelji

145
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:55,879
[SPEAKER_02] dobijam kritiku.

146
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:57,299
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje si stavio ovaj papir?

147
00:10:57,299 --> 00:10:58,639
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje si stavio ovaj?

148
00:10:59,220 --> 00:11:00,440
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim, ta bilježnica

149
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,679
[SPEAKER_02] u koju sam upisao,

150
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:10,340
[SPEAKER_02] mjesec Sječan 2009. godine,

151
00:11:10,340 --> 00:11:11,779
[SPEAKER_02] u Sječnom mjesecu,

152
00:11:11,779 --> 00:11:12,879
[SPEAKER_02] mislim da je bio šesti,

153
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:15,779
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam imao prvi sastanak

154
00:11:15,779 --> 00:11:17,899
[SPEAKER_02] sa Kapi Dobrote 2009.

155
00:11:17,899 --> 00:11:21,240
[SPEAKER_02] I od tada ja pišem svaki dan kratko.

156
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:27,039
[SPEAKER_02] I u toj svojoj udruzi

157
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:30,700
[SPEAKER_02] na taj način

158
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:34,799
[SPEAKER_02] sam ostvario

159
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:37,279
[SPEAKER_02] ono što smatram da sam dužan ostvario.

160
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:40,179
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, za naše gledatelje,

161
00:11:40,179 --> 00:11:40,919
[SPEAKER_02] naravno,

162
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:44,279
[SPEAKER_02] mislim na našu braću i sestre Hrvate

163
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:46,679
[SPEAKER_02] u domovini i u iseljeništvu.

164
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:49,019
[SPEAKER_02] Želim kazati da se ne smatram

165
00:11:49,019 --> 00:11:51,200
[SPEAKER_02] ničim posebnim

166
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,399
[SPEAKER_02] zato što sam ja toliko godina

167
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:54,139
[SPEAKER_02] u toj udruzi

168
00:11:54,139 --> 00:11:56,220
[SPEAKER_02] ili zato što sam bio u domovinskom ratu.

169
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:59,139
[SPEAKER_02] Da si ti meni lani posudio

170
00:11:59,139 --> 00:12:00,059
[SPEAKER_02] tisuću eura,

171
00:12:00,059 --> 00:12:02,480
[SPEAKER_02] a ja ti ove godine vratio,

172
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:05,500
[SPEAKER_02] po čemu sam ja poseban što sam vratio dug.

173
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:07,120
[SPEAKER_02] Radostan je sam

174
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,820
[SPEAKER_02] i Bog daje radost,

175
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:12,700
[SPEAKER_02] ali ne smatram se ničim posebnim,

176
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:16,279
[SPEAKER_02] nego vraćam svoj dug Bogu

177
00:12:16,279 --> 00:12:17,659
[SPEAKER_02] iz svome hrvatskom narodu

178
00:12:17,659 --> 00:12:19,820
[SPEAKER_02] i našoj braći iz drugih naroda,

179
00:12:19,820 --> 00:12:21,419
[SPEAKER_02] jer sam tako odgojen.

180
00:12:21,419 --> 00:12:24,379
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam dijete,

181
00:12:24,379 --> 00:12:25,779
[SPEAKER_02] hvala Bogu to govorim,

182
00:12:25,779 --> 00:12:27,059
[SPEAKER_02] radi vas mladih,

183
00:12:27,059 --> 00:12:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] osmo dijete u svojih roditelja rođeno,

184
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:35,639
[SPEAKER_02] a deseto začeto dijete.

185
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:39,419
[SPEAKER_02] I znam to ovako ponekad reći

186
00:12:39,419 --> 00:12:40,759
[SPEAKER_02] i reći i sada,

187
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:45,519
[SPEAKER_02] moja mati je živjela

188
00:12:45,519 --> 00:12:46,960
[SPEAKER_02] dosta kratko,

189
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,000
[SPEAKER_02] jer nas je puno rodila,

190
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,360
[SPEAKER_02] kao divojčica je išla

191
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,480
[SPEAKER_02] na dnevnicu,

192
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] jer je moj dijet poginuo

193
00:12:51,559 --> 00:12:52,539
[SPEAKER_02] u Buenos Airesu,

194
00:12:52,539 --> 00:12:53,899
[SPEAKER_02] kao hrvatski seljenik

195
00:12:53,899 --> 00:12:56,039
[SPEAKER_02] ranih tih godina

196
00:12:56,039 --> 00:12:58,019
[SPEAKER_02] i dočekala je 91 godinu.

197
00:12:58,019 --> 00:13:00,299
[SPEAKER_02] I to govorim zato

198
00:13:00,299 --> 00:13:03,100
[SPEAKER_02] da za vas mlade,

199
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:05,240
[SPEAKER_02] da ne nasjedate na laži

200
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:07,120
[SPEAKER_02] da žena se iscrpljuje

201
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,460
[SPEAKER_02] u rađanju.

202
00:13:08,460 --> 00:13:10,740
[SPEAKER_02] Brojni primjeri pokazuju suprotno

203
00:13:10,740 --> 00:13:12,940
[SPEAKER_02] da se ženino tijelo

204
00:13:12,940 --> 00:13:14,740
[SPEAKER_02] i duh i tijelo jača rađanjem

205
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:16,080
[SPEAKER_02] i da se ona tako stvaruje.

206
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da svi u obitelji

207
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] imamo dosta primjera

208
00:13:19,659 --> 00:13:20,919
[SPEAKER_00] toga naših baka,

209
00:13:21,039 --> 00:13:21,600
[SPEAKER_00] pravaka,

210
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,379
[SPEAKER_00] to je lijepo,

211
00:13:22,379 --> 00:13:23,320
[SPEAKER_00] lijepo začut.

212
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:26,080
[SPEAKER_00] A što se tiče sad,

213
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,600
[SPEAKER_00] evo, opet da se malo vratimo

214
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] na kab dobrote,

215
00:13:28,679 --> 00:13:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] je li vam lako reći,

216
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,240
[SPEAKER_00] to jest preteško reći

217
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,899
[SPEAKER_00] koji su najteži slučajevi

218
00:13:34,899 --> 00:13:36,580
[SPEAKER_00] s kojima ste se susretali

219
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:37,059
[SPEAKER_00] do sad.

220
00:13:37,059 --> 00:13:38,879
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto da gledatelji malo dobiju

221
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] sliku čega to ima

222
00:13:40,279 --> 00:13:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] po Zagrebu.

223
00:13:41,139 --> 00:13:42,700
[SPEAKER_00] Naime, nedavno ste došli

224
00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] i držali ste predavanje

225
00:13:43,940 --> 00:13:45,320
[SPEAKER_00] nama u Mlade za domovinu

226
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,639
[SPEAKER_00] i čuo sam sa strane

227
00:13:46,639 --> 00:13:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] jedan komentar

228
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:48,899
[SPEAKER_00] čovječe nisam znao

229
00:13:48,899 --> 00:13:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] da toga i u Zagrebu ima.

230
00:13:50,519 --> 00:13:52,399
[SPEAKER_00] a vi ste svjedoci

231
00:13:52,399 --> 00:13:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] ovih godina rada

232
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] da toga ima sila,

233
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa evo,

234
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:56,679
[SPEAKER_00] ako vam nije teško

235
00:13:56,679 --> 00:13:58,139
[SPEAKER_00] prenijeti nam dio toga.

236
00:13:58,139 --> 00:13:58,580
[SPEAKER_02] Pa evo,

237
00:13:58,580 --> 00:13:59,639
[SPEAKER_02] neka Marinko sad

238
00:13:59,639 --> 00:14:01,559
[SPEAKER_02] počne o ovom pitanju,

239
00:14:01,559 --> 00:14:02,620
[SPEAKER_02] pa ću i jari svoje.

240
00:14:02,620 --> 00:14:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] Može, može.

241
00:14:04,340 --> 00:14:06,059
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću dva slučaja koja su mene

242
00:14:06,059 --> 00:14:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] toliko u srce.

243
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:07,980
[SPEAKER_01] Jer znam da ima,

244
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:08,460
[SPEAKER_01] e, da,

245
00:14:08,460 --> 00:14:09,340
[SPEAKER_01] ovo što ćete čuti.

246
00:14:09,340 --> 00:14:11,159
[SPEAKER_01] neki dan sam to osvjedočio vama

247
00:14:11,159 --> 00:14:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] na ovnom sastanku.

248
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:16,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ima više od 15 godina

249
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,019
[SPEAKER_01] pokojni duš,

250
00:14:17,019 --> 00:14:18,639
[SPEAKER_01] sad ćemo pokojnicima govoriti,

251
00:14:18,639 --> 00:14:20,179
[SPEAKER_01] pokojnoj baki Mari

252
00:14:20,179 --> 00:14:21,240
[SPEAKER_01] i njeznom silu,

253
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,259
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatskom branitelju,

254
00:14:22,259 --> 00:14:25,740
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo te zime,

255
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:26,720
[SPEAKER_01] to je već bila negdje

256
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,720
[SPEAKER_01] 10. i 11. mjesec,

257
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,799
[SPEAKER_01] prije 15 godina,

258
00:14:29,799 --> 00:14:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] razvozili drva

259
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,379
[SPEAKER_01] i mene je naša jedna župljanka

260
00:14:33,379 --> 00:14:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] draga zamola

261
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:35,720
[SPEAKER_01] i ona je znala

262
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,799
[SPEAKER_01] da se mi time bavimo,

263
00:14:36,799 --> 00:14:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] da sam u kapi dobrote

264
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] pitala da li imamo mi drva,

265
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:41,019
[SPEAKER_01] da li možemo pomoći

266
00:14:41,019 --> 00:14:41,700
[SPEAKER_01] jednoj sirotnje,

267
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] da su oni dolazili gore

268
00:14:42,860 --> 00:14:44,500
[SPEAKER_01] u župu Svetog Ante

269
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:45,580
[SPEAKER_01] moliti da pomognu.

270
00:14:45,580 --> 00:14:47,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ih zamolio

271
00:14:47,139 --> 00:14:48,299
[SPEAKER_01] da mi dani adresu,

272
00:14:48,299 --> 00:14:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] probao sam ih pronaći

273
00:14:50,460 --> 00:14:51,799
[SPEAKER_01] to je u Gradišćanskoj

274
00:14:51,799 --> 00:14:53,200
[SPEAKER_01] blizu pruge jedna ruševna

275
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,279
[SPEAKER_01] napuštena kuća,

276
00:14:54,279 --> 00:14:56,139
[SPEAKER_01] jedva sam ih našao,

277
00:14:56,139 --> 00:14:57,220
[SPEAKER_01] dugo sam ih tražio

278
00:14:57,220 --> 00:14:58,600
[SPEAKER_01] u toj ruševini,

279
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] znači oni su progladnici

280
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,220
[SPEAKER_01] iz Posavine,

281
00:15:01,220 --> 00:15:02,139
[SPEAKER_01] oni su ušli,

282
00:15:02,139 --> 00:15:03,100
[SPEAKER_01] bespravno,

283
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:04,840
[SPEAKER_01] bili su pola godine pod mostom.

284
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,620
[SPEAKER_01] Znači hrvatski branitelj

285
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:07,620
[SPEAKER_01] koji je bio u KVO

286
00:15:07,620 --> 00:15:08,419
[SPEAKER_01] bio je ranjen,

287
00:15:08,419 --> 00:15:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] liječen je u Slavonskom brodu

288
00:15:11,039 --> 00:15:14,240
[SPEAKER_01] i posle je navršeno liječenje

289
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:14,779
[SPEAKER_01] u Zagrebu,

290
00:15:14,779 --> 00:15:15,860
[SPEAKER_01] Draškoviće u bolnici,

291
00:15:15,860 --> 00:15:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] kada je otpušten,

292
00:15:16,519 --> 00:15:17,299
[SPEAKER_01] nisu imali gdje,

293
00:15:17,299 --> 00:15:18,399
[SPEAKER_01] nego su išli pod most,

294
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,840
[SPEAKER_01] bilo s pola godine pod mostom.

295
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kako su žijeli pod mostom?

296
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kako su živjeli

297
00:15:22,519 --> 00:15:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] i ona je meni to sve kroz suze,

298
00:15:24,940 --> 00:15:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] stavno pokoje duše,

299
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,980
[SPEAKER_01] na sveta žena paćernica pričala

300
00:15:27,980 --> 00:15:30,120
[SPEAKER_01] i saznali su za u ruševnu

301
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:32,200
[SPEAKER_01] da je prazna tu je neko živio,

302
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:32,820
[SPEAKER_01] napustio,

303
00:15:32,820 --> 00:15:33,700
[SPEAKER_01] oni su u to ušli,

304
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:35,419
[SPEAKER_01] to je za nje bio dvorac,

305
00:15:35,419 --> 00:15:37,600
[SPEAKER_01] kad su ispod vedra u neba došli u to.

306
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:41,379
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam ih našao u njihovom tome,

307
00:15:41,379 --> 00:15:41,759
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

308
00:15:41,759 --> 00:15:43,240
[SPEAKER_01] vlažnom podrumu,

309
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] u toj ruševni,

310
00:15:44,039 --> 00:15:45,379
[SPEAKER_01] najilo je na prozorima,

311
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] čećan se kojuče bio,

312
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:47,220
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam došao,

313
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:48,860
[SPEAKER_01] jedna peć je bila,

314
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:51,220
[SPEAKER_01] unutra kad sam ušao u tu sobu,

315
00:15:51,220 --> 00:15:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] nisem moglo disati

316
00:15:52,519 --> 00:15:54,179
[SPEAKER_01] od mirisa paljevine gume.

317
00:15:54,179 --> 00:15:56,600
[SPEAKER_01] I pitao sam Maru,

318
00:15:56,600 --> 00:15:59,679
[SPEAKER_01] čime se oni griju.

319
00:15:59,679 --> 00:16:02,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je toliko kroz suze rekla

320
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:05,419
[SPEAKER_01] da traže po kontenerima

321
00:16:05,419 --> 00:16:06,600
[SPEAKER_01] staru obuću

322
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:08,740
[SPEAKER_01] i robu,

323
00:16:08,740 --> 00:16:10,440
[SPEAKER_01] da oni time se griju

324
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:12,799
[SPEAKER_01] i ako nađu negdje koje drvo suho

325
00:16:12,799 --> 00:16:14,200
[SPEAKER_01] na šumi,

326
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,659
[SPEAKER_01] s time su oni već grijali

327
00:16:15,659 --> 00:16:16,899
[SPEAKER_01] dvije, tri zime.

328
00:16:16,899 --> 00:16:18,679
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je to toliko ganulo,

329
00:16:18,679 --> 00:16:21,580
[SPEAKER_01] iskreno su se otvorili,

330
00:16:21,580 --> 00:16:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] toliko smo se tada sprijateljili,

331
00:16:24,460 --> 00:16:26,259
[SPEAKER_01] 15 godina sam do smrti

332
00:16:26,259 --> 00:16:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] tu obitelj pomagao

333
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:30,220
[SPEAKER_01] i dan danas je živa,

334
00:16:30,220 --> 00:16:31,279
[SPEAKER_01] teško, bolesno,

335
00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:32,600
[SPEAKER_01] mi put je pozdravljan,

336
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,820
[SPEAKER_01] čer Marica koja je nedavno operirana.

337
00:16:34,820 --> 00:16:36,379
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan još slučaj,

338
00:16:36,379 --> 00:16:37,639
[SPEAKER_01] bio sam gost,

339
00:16:37,639 --> 00:16:39,259
[SPEAKER_01] dugo nisam htio u medije ići,

340
00:16:39,259 --> 00:16:39,620
[SPEAKER_01] pa mi je on,

341
00:16:39,620 --> 00:16:40,480
[SPEAKER_01] dragi moji prijatelj,

342
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,320
[SPEAKER_01] svećan rekao,

343
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,919
[SPEAKER_01] Marinko, nemoj odbijati,

344
00:16:42,919 --> 00:16:44,220
[SPEAKER_01] probaj svjedočitimog

345
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] da potakneš nekog drugoga

346
00:16:45,519 --> 00:16:46,360
[SPEAKER_01] da čini dobro

347
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,539
[SPEAKER_01] da se priključi

348
00:16:48,539 --> 00:16:49,340
[SPEAKER_01] da li to u kabu

349
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:50,419
[SPEAKER_01] ili koju drugu udrugu.

350
00:16:50,419 --> 00:16:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] On je gledao tu emisiju

351
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,100
[SPEAKER_01] i nije znao da sam ja

352
00:16:54,100 --> 00:16:55,779
[SPEAKER_01] u toj udruzi

353
00:16:55,779 --> 00:16:57,679
[SPEAKER_01] i nazvao mi je,

354
00:16:57,679 --> 00:16:59,240
[SPEAKER_01] rekao on da ima jedan dida

355
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] u Zagoru žive nekoj šumi,

356
00:17:01,559 --> 00:17:03,220
[SPEAKER_01] napušteno je sam,

357
00:17:03,220 --> 00:17:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] bez struje,

358
00:17:04,039 --> 00:17:04,519
[SPEAKER_01] bez vode

359
00:17:04,519 --> 00:17:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] i gdje je nikoga blizu njega.

360
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:09,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se taj dan,

361
00:17:09,220 --> 00:17:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] cijelu noć razmišljao

362
00:17:10,519 --> 00:17:11,240
[SPEAKER_01] o tom čovjeku

363
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:11,759
[SPEAKER_01] koja mi je rekao

364
00:17:11,759 --> 00:17:12,480
[SPEAKER_01] kakvim ujetima,

365
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] on je slučajno na njega

366
00:17:13,579 --> 00:17:16,779
[SPEAKER_01] naišao žive u susjednom selu.

367
00:17:16,779 --> 00:17:18,299
[SPEAKER_01] Auto sam sijeo,

368
00:17:18,299 --> 00:17:19,099
[SPEAKER_01] kupio hrane

369
00:17:19,099 --> 00:17:19,660
[SPEAKER_01] i krenio

370
00:17:19,660 --> 00:17:22,019
[SPEAKER_01] tražiti didafranju.

371
00:17:22,019 --> 00:17:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] Negde sam popodne,

372
00:17:24,519 --> 00:17:25,339
[SPEAKER_01] krenuo sam uvitru

373
00:17:25,339 --> 00:17:26,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam odvezao

374
00:17:26,039 --> 00:17:27,440
[SPEAKER_01] svoju dicu u školu,

375
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:29,299
[SPEAKER_01] negde oko jedan sat popodne

376
00:17:29,299 --> 00:17:30,740
[SPEAKER_01] sam ga uspio pronaći.

377
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:32,279
[SPEAKER_01] Došao sam u jedno selo,

378
00:17:32,279 --> 00:17:34,140
[SPEAKER_01] Sveti križ začrtje,

379
00:17:34,140 --> 00:17:35,579
[SPEAKER_01] blizu jedne škole

380
00:17:35,579 --> 00:17:36,359
[SPEAKER_01] i tu sam pitao,

381
00:17:36,359 --> 00:17:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] našao sam na poštara.

382
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:38,940
[SPEAKER_01] I poštar mi je rekao

383
00:17:38,940 --> 00:17:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] da je on tamo kod njega bio

384
00:17:40,059 --> 00:17:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] da mu i nosio socijalnu pomoć

385
00:17:41,519 --> 00:17:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] on mi je opisao u brdo gore

386
00:17:43,539 --> 00:17:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] kroz šumu,

387
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:44,960
[SPEAKER_01] došao sam do njega

388
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:48,519
[SPEAKER_01] i dan danas ta slika mi se toliko urezala.

389
00:17:48,519 --> 00:17:50,480
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo negde vrijeme,

390
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:52,720
[SPEAKER_01] proljeće znam da je bilo zelenlo,

391
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:54,140
[SPEAKER_01] drvena jedna kućca,

392
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:55,160
[SPEAKER_01] napo ruševna,

393
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] pod jednom velikom topolom,

394
00:17:57,579 --> 00:17:59,579
[SPEAKER_01] sjedi na pragu svoje te kućice

395
00:17:59,579 --> 00:18:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] što je on znao zvati njegov dvorac,

396
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:04,359
[SPEAKER_01] sjedi didafranju,

397
00:18:04,359 --> 00:18:05,680
[SPEAKER_01] na očale,

398
00:18:06,259 --> 00:18:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] na glavi,

399
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:08,859
[SPEAKER_01] nisu na očima

400
00:18:08,859 --> 00:18:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] i na koljenima mu stoji

401
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:11,819
[SPEAKER_01] stara ura,

402
00:18:11,819 --> 00:18:12,299
[SPEAKER_01] drvena,

403
00:18:12,299 --> 00:18:13,119
[SPEAKER_01] zidni sat.

404
00:18:13,119 --> 00:18:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] Saznao sam poslije

405
00:18:14,559 --> 00:18:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] da on bio i urar

406
00:18:15,420 --> 00:18:16,279
[SPEAKER_01] i tako sjedi,

407
00:18:16,279 --> 00:18:17,579
[SPEAKER_01] ja ga pozdravim,

408
00:18:17,579 --> 00:18:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] hvala nisu Marija,

409
00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako ste,

410
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,140
[SPEAKER_01] tako saznao sam

411
00:18:21,140 --> 00:18:22,299
[SPEAKER_01] da se zove među vremenu

412
00:18:22,299 --> 00:18:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] i Franjovim je ovaj

413
00:18:23,380 --> 00:18:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] moj kolega rekao

414
00:18:25,039 --> 00:18:26,700
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam došao,

415
00:18:26,700 --> 00:18:28,240
[SPEAKER_01] vidio sam toliko radosti

416
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] s tog čovjeka

417
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,220
[SPEAKER_01] u kojoj bijedi žive,

418
00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:32,220
[SPEAKER_01] znači on je ostao bez mame

419
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:33,339
[SPEAKER_01] a imao je godinu dana.

420
00:18:33,339 --> 00:18:34,900
[SPEAKER_01] Kad mu je mama umrla,

421
00:18:35,700 --> 00:18:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] sam je živio,

422
00:18:36,619 --> 00:18:38,180
[SPEAKER_01] inače školu završio

423
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:38,740
[SPEAKER_01] za urara,

424
00:18:38,740 --> 00:18:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] radio je negdje,

425
00:18:39,380 --> 00:18:41,819
[SPEAKER_01] on sve te detalje poznao

426
00:18:41,819 --> 00:18:42,400
[SPEAKER_01] u Zagrebu

427
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] kao ura jedne židovske obitelji

428
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:45,240
[SPEAKER_01] u Boškovićevoj

429
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:48,019
[SPEAKER_01] i ta radost iz toga čovjeka

430
00:18:48,019 --> 00:18:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] bez struje,

431
00:18:48,980 --> 00:18:49,740
[SPEAKER_01] bez vode,

432
00:18:49,740 --> 00:18:50,759
[SPEAKER_01] zemljani pod,

433
00:18:50,759 --> 00:18:51,720
[SPEAKER_01] sve,

434
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

435
00:18:52,019 --> 00:18:53,019
[SPEAKER_01] vin ko je bio svijedov,

436
00:18:53,019 --> 00:18:53,799
[SPEAKER_01] bili smo kod njega

437
00:18:53,799 --> 00:18:54,660
[SPEAKER_01] i pater cvek,

438
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] pater u cveku smo ispričao

439
00:18:56,019 --> 00:18:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam ga pronašao,

440
00:18:56,980 --> 00:18:58,240
[SPEAKER_01] njegova želja bila

441
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] nas trojice,

442
00:18:58,900 --> 00:19:00,400
[SPEAKER_01] smo išli ga posjetiti.

443
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:00,700
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna,

444
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:01,660
[SPEAKER_01] tri puta je,

445
00:19:01,859 --> 00:19:03,200
[SPEAKER_01] znači vodlje na streljanje,

446
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] na križnom putu je bio.

447
00:19:04,539 --> 00:19:06,779
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna radost iz čovjeka,

448
00:19:06,779 --> 00:19:07,660
[SPEAKER_01] nigdje ništa,

449
00:19:07,660 --> 00:19:09,259
[SPEAKER_01] ali njegove su to riči,

450
00:19:09,259 --> 00:19:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] kada je stavno na znao reći,

451
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:11,140
[SPEAKER_01] kada smo odlazili,

452
00:19:11,779 --> 00:19:13,859
[SPEAKER_01] budi čovjek i treba mi čovjek.

453
00:19:13,859 --> 00:19:15,240
[SPEAKER_01] Te riči to me nosi,

454
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:17,380
[SPEAKER_01] to je za mene moj drugi otac,

455
00:19:17,380 --> 00:19:19,700
[SPEAKER_01] koji je mene sadio,

456
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:21,619
[SPEAKER_01] to je u dobrotu,

457
00:19:21,619 --> 00:19:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] ali Dida Franjom je toliko uvijek bio potica,

458
00:19:24,380 --> 00:19:25,960
[SPEAKER_01] je umro je u sto toj godini,

459
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,640
[SPEAKER_01] više od petnest godina,

460
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] uz dobre ljude smo ga dvorili,

461
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:31,740
[SPEAKER_01] išli smo često od odvjetnika,

462
00:19:31,740 --> 00:19:33,420
[SPEAKER_01] svi učilišni profesora nema,

463
00:19:33,420 --> 00:19:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] kakvi ljudi nije bilo uznika,

464
00:19:35,079 --> 00:19:37,799
[SPEAKER_01] naši koji su htjeli upoznati,

465
00:19:37,799 --> 00:19:39,700
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam znao ovako slikovito ispričati

466
00:19:39,700 --> 00:19:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] o Dida Franji,

467
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,859
[SPEAKER_01] svi su htjeli otići posjetiti,

468
00:19:42,859 --> 00:19:43,799
[SPEAKER_01] viditi ovog čovjeka,

469
00:19:43,799 --> 00:19:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] kako iz njega jedna radost,

470
00:19:45,079 --> 00:19:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] nigdje ništa,

471
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:47,839
[SPEAKER_01] ali iz njega velika radost,

472
00:19:47,839 --> 00:19:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] u njegove nemaštine,

473
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:50,279
[SPEAKER_01] ali i srce bilo puno,

474
00:19:50,279 --> 00:19:52,980
[SPEAKER_01] posebno je volio kad dođu mladi ljudi,

475
00:19:52,980 --> 00:19:55,440
[SPEAKER_01] dovodili smo i mlade kod njega i tako.

476
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno su to životne pouke,

477
00:19:57,319 --> 00:19:59,680
[SPEAKER_00] koje čovjek ne može nigdje pročitati

478
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] ili od nekog drugog prepričati,

479
00:20:02,079 --> 00:20:04,740
[SPEAKER_00] jer vjerujem jednostavno se treba doživiti,

480
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:08,180
[SPEAKER_00] to u biti ispudni čovjeka više vjerujem

481
00:20:08,180 --> 00:20:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego jedan novac.

482
00:20:10,140 --> 00:20:13,640
[SPEAKER_00] A isto što meni je teško pojmit,

483
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:16,240
[SPEAKER_00] bilo mi je teško pojmit u samom centru grada,

484
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:18,299
[SPEAKER_00] gdje čovjek ono percipira da žive

485
00:20:18,299 --> 00:20:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] najveći luksuz od ljudi,

486
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] čim se malo zađe u neki suteren

487
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:25,339
[SPEAKER_00] ili u neko potkrolje tih zgrada,

488
00:20:25,339 --> 00:20:28,160
[SPEAKER_00] od Draškovića i Palmotićeve i tako,

489
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] što sve čovjek naleti.

490
00:20:29,559 --> 00:20:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] Vinko, možda ti imaš nekih primjera tog tipa ili nekog drugog.

491
00:20:33,619 --> 00:20:37,140
[SPEAKER_02] Imamo ih puno i ja i Marinko, ali ću evo reći ja

492
00:20:37,140 --> 00:20:43,740
[SPEAKER_02] da naš narod ovoga čuje i dio tih sudbina.

493
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:48,299
[SPEAKER_02] Imao sam u isto vrijeme brata i dvije sestre

494
00:20:48,299 --> 00:20:50,940
[SPEAKER_02] prognane iz posajine, naše posajine.

495
00:20:52,380 --> 00:20:56,519
[SPEAKER_02] I ono što je za primijeti tu zostalo,

496
00:20:56,519 --> 00:20:59,539
[SPEAKER_02] mogli bi mi o svakom korisniku pričati tri dana,

497
00:20:59,539 --> 00:21:03,779
[SPEAKER_02] ali ono što je dobro reći i prenijet našemu narodu.

498
00:21:03,779 --> 00:21:07,180
[SPEAKER_02] Ovoga tri, dakle, troje njih

499
00:21:07,180 --> 00:21:10,839
[SPEAKER_02] i sad s njima bija normalno razgovarao,

500
00:21:10,839 --> 00:21:13,839
[SPEAKER_02] mi smo ih pomagali stvarno i sa hranom

501
00:21:13,839 --> 00:21:17,640
[SPEAKER_02] i redovnim posjetama, pa sam se mučio

502
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:20,720
[SPEAKER_02] sa Hrvatskim zavodom za zdravstveno siguranje.

503
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:24,759
[SPEAKER_02] Vrlo je zanimljivo za one koji olako prodaju Hrvatsku zemlju,

504
00:21:24,759 --> 00:21:27,039
[SPEAKER_02] čut sad ovo što ćete čuti.

505
00:21:27,039 --> 00:21:31,579
[SPEAKER_02] I nikako ne može dati osiguranje

506
00:21:31,579 --> 00:21:34,900
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvatski zavod za zdravstveno osiguranje

507
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:39,480
[SPEAKER_02] toj prognanici, tim dvijama sestrama,

508
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:41,759
[SPEAKER_02] jer one neće ono što se traži od njih.

509
00:21:41,759 --> 00:21:44,759
[SPEAKER_02] Nikako im dati osiguranje zdravstveno.

510
00:21:44,759 --> 00:21:47,119
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam par pisama napisao,

511
00:21:47,119 --> 00:21:50,019
[SPEAKER_02] između ostalog sam napisao da su Hrvatskoj zaštićeni

512
00:21:50,019 --> 00:21:53,859
[SPEAKER_02] psi na ulici, zdravstveno.

513
00:21:53,859 --> 00:21:55,299
[SPEAKER_02] Ima gdje ih se vodi.

514
00:21:55,299 --> 00:21:57,359
[SPEAKER_02] I onda su morali odreagirat.

515
00:21:57,359 --> 00:21:59,700
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne znam, imali sačuvano to pismo

516
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:01,980
[SPEAKER_02] u našoj udruzi.

517
00:22:01,980 --> 00:22:04,700
[SPEAKER_02] Onda su mi odgovorili na jedan čudan način

518
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:06,900
[SPEAKER_02] da imaju pravo na određeni, citirano,

519
00:22:06,900 --> 00:22:07,859
[SPEAKER_02] vid osiguranja.

520
00:22:07,859 --> 00:22:09,740
[SPEAKER_02] Znači neodređeno.

521
00:22:10,059 --> 00:22:13,059
[SPEAKER_02] Ali imali smo doktoricu našu koja nas je pomagala

522
00:22:13,059 --> 00:22:15,339
[SPEAKER_02] i to pa smo mi to rješavali.

523
00:22:15,779 --> 00:22:19,759
[SPEAKER_02] A zašto ona nije mogla dobiti po njima to osiguranje?

524
00:22:19,759 --> 00:22:22,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ona nije htjela potpisati da ona živi u Zagrebu.

525
00:22:22,420 --> 00:22:27,180
[SPEAKER_02] Ne zato da, jer ona je neuka žena bila, jedna i druga.

526
00:22:27,180 --> 00:22:32,380
[SPEAKER_02] Jer ona se bojala, ako ona napiše da je ona u Zagrebu,

527
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:40,799
[SPEAKER_02] da će tu njihovu zemlju, da će ona ostati bez nje.

528
00:22:40,799 --> 00:22:44,960
[SPEAKER_02] A nijedna nije imala manje od 70 godina.

529
00:22:44,960 --> 00:22:49,799
[SPEAKER_02] Znači bila je spremna mučit se da dobije lijek,

530
00:22:49,799 --> 00:22:53,339
[SPEAKER_02] da dobije doktora, da sačuva svoju njivu i svoju kuću.

531
00:22:53,339 --> 00:22:55,440
[SPEAKER_02] Dvije sestre iz Posavine.

532
00:22:55,440 --> 00:23:02,160
[SPEAKER_02] Pa da ovo čuju svi naši ljudi na dobro i na pouku,

533
00:23:02,559 --> 00:23:04,960
[SPEAKER_02] ako olako pristupaju, prodaj i djedovi.

534
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:11,240
[SPEAKER_02] I tako smo se borili da ih zaštitimo zdravstveno.

535
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:17,339
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim, šta je dobro za njih, šta sam dobro upamtio

536
00:23:17,339 --> 00:23:20,319
[SPEAKER_02] i šta je dobro podijeliti s vama i gledateljima.

537
00:23:20,319 --> 00:23:24,779
[SPEAKER_02] A ova druga sestra, ona se nikad nije nasmijala njeseci.

538
00:23:24,779 --> 00:23:28,339
[SPEAKER_02] Ja je nikad nasmijano i veselo nisam vidio.

539
00:23:28,339 --> 00:23:32,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ali nisam imali televiziju i da skratim priču,

540
00:23:32,460 --> 00:23:34,559
[SPEAKER_02] ja dođem u drugu jer mi tako radimo.

541
00:23:34,559 --> 00:23:37,079
[SPEAKER_02] Bili imali neko možda viška televiziju,

542
00:23:37,079 --> 00:23:39,480
[SPEAKER_02] šta ćemo kupovati novo ako ima neka da je upotrebljiva.

543
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:43,160
[SPEAKER_02] Jer moramo čuvati novace, nemamo uvjetovani smo

544
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:45,559
[SPEAKER_02] i moramo paziti svaku kunu.

545
00:23:45,559 --> 00:23:48,859
[SPEAKER_02] I javi se jedna žena da ona ima televiziju.

546
00:23:48,859 --> 00:23:53,180
[SPEAKER_02] I sad ja donosim televiziju njima u stan njihov mali

547
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:59,900
[SPEAKER_02] i ona se smije ko malo djete kad mu doneseš najmiliju igračku koja postoji.

548
00:23:59,900 --> 00:24:01,640
[SPEAKER_02] Ta žena tužna uvijek.

549
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:06,579
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo nju obveselili, ja ne znam jeli šta je veseli ona doživjela u Zagrebu.

550
00:24:06,579 --> 00:24:11,980
[SPEAKER_02] Sad će ona gledat televiziju i ona je bila sva sretna, nasmijana

551
00:24:11,980 --> 00:24:15,660
[SPEAKER_02] i sretan sam bio i ja, i ova žena i naša udruga, naravno.

552
00:24:15,660 --> 00:24:20,900
[SPEAKER_02] I još ću reći samo jedan slučaj od više tih slučajeva.

553
00:24:20,900 --> 00:24:25,019
[SPEAKER_02] Evo recimo i ovo Željko jedan, on je bio invalid, isto tako.

554
00:24:25,019 --> 00:24:29,660
[SPEAKER_02] Ja bi došao k njemu, ovoga, dobro nisam rekao prezime, naravno,

555
00:24:29,660 --> 00:24:36,019
[SPEAKER_02] a ovoga ja bi došao k njemu i on je pušio i on bi uvijek gledao televiziju,

556
00:24:36,019 --> 00:24:39,599
[SPEAKER_02] uvijek ozbilja, zaplako bi samo kad bi spomenuo sina

557
00:24:39,599 --> 00:24:44,779
[SPEAKER_02] koji je bio živali, zašto i kako su bili u odnosima, nebitno.

558
00:24:44,779 --> 00:24:49,200
[SPEAKER_02] I on je isto uvijek ozbiljan, ali bi se nasmio

559
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:54,380
[SPEAKER_02] kad mi smo mu kupili novu peć, jer se smrzavo

560
00:24:54,380 --> 00:24:57,640
[SPEAKER_02] i drva je imao koliko treba, koliko treba.

561
00:24:57,640 --> 00:25:02,440
[SPEAKER_02] I onda bi on onako iz svojih ulica gledao i odjedna mu kaže

562
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:08,980
[SPEAKER_02] kadaj kako gori, smije se, kako gori, kako se zagrijala ova peć

563
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:13,099
[SPEAKER_02] i užarila. I jedan slučaj se imao, još ću reći samo to,

564
00:25:13,099 --> 00:25:17,299
[SPEAKER_02] ovoga, čovjek nije izašao iz podruma dvije godine.

565
00:25:17,299 --> 00:25:22,299
[SPEAKER_02] I naša socija nije izašla jer je sa bolesnom ženom,

566
00:25:22,299 --> 00:25:25,299
[SPEAKER_02] invalid u podrumu. Nije zraka vidio dvije godine.

567
00:25:25,299 --> 00:25:30,519
[SPEAKER_02] I ova sestra, ova socijalna radnica rekla njemu,

568
00:25:30,519 --> 00:25:34,900
[SPEAKER_02] ko će se javi, javio se ja, pa ja ću ga vozić u kolicima gore na zvijezdi.

569
00:25:34,900 --> 00:25:38,900
[SPEAKER_02] I on, kad je ona njemu rekao, on se cijeli raspraku,

570
00:25:38,900 --> 00:25:43,900
[SPEAKER_02] ali nije vjerovo da će on to doživjeti, da izađe vani dok mi nismo došli gore,

571
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:52,480
[SPEAKER_02] iznijeli ga i onda sam ga ja vozio, kako bi dogovorili vrijeme,

572
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:55,960
[SPEAKER_02] sjedali bi gore i pričani, bio sa osretom dosta psihički dobar.

573
00:25:55,960 --> 00:26:00,480
[SPEAKER_02] I umro u ponoća. I u ponoća naša mira me zvala.

574
00:26:01,119 --> 00:26:05,000
[SPEAKER_02] I ta žena, tužna koja je bila njegova žena,

575
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:09,660
[SPEAKER_02] nije imala nikoga nego nas, odnosno kap dobrote,

576
00:26:09,660 --> 00:26:14,720
[SPEAKER_02] zvala i eto, Bogu hvala u ponoća ja prema zvijezdi.

577
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:19,220
[SPEAKER_02] I malo smo je utješili, bili sa njom i ovako teške stvari,

578
00:26:19,220 --> 00:26:23,220
[SPEAKER_02] ali eto, Bog nam daje snage i Bogu hvala na pomoći.

579
00:26:23,220 --> 00:26:27,579
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo obitelji, oni nas drže da smo mi članovi njihove obitelje

580
00:26:27,579 --> 00:26:29,259
[SPEAKER_01] i obrnuti, oni naši.

581
00:26:29,259 --> 00:26:33,200
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je toliko se, ja znam ovako simbolički reći,

582
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:35,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je kao utopljeni kad se utaplja, kad se ulovi za tebe,

583
00:26:35,940 --> 00:26:38,400
[SPEAKER_01] tako i ti jednici, siromaki, napušteni,

584
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:41,440
[SPEAKER_01] kad oni osijete da je neko uz njega, oni ima jednu sigurnost.

585
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:45,339
[SPEAKER_01] I oni nas drže, ono, ko za slamku spasa se zna,

586
00:26:45,339 --> 00:26:47,799
[SPEAKER_01] drže, nemojte nas ostaviti, nemojte nas zaboraviti.

587
00:26:47,799 --> 00:26:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] Evo jedan primjer, u jesen, mi svakog mjeseca,

588
00:26:51,380 --> 00:26:55,180
[SPEAKER_01] znači, rekli smo da živimo s tom sirotinom 365 dana u godinju.

589
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:57,660
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, krene jesen, već pripreme za drva,

590
00:26:57,720 --> 00:27:00,319
[SPEAKER_01] kad mi vozimo oko desetog mjeseca pakete hrane,

591
00:27:00,319 --> 00:27:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] kad oni reknu, naš, ostavite nas bez paketa hrane,

592
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:06,579
[SPEAKER_01] nemojte nas zaboraviti, drva da nadovezete.

593
00:27:06,579 --> 00:27:09,920
[SPEAKER_01] U tom jadu, mi svi imamo neke normalne kuće,

594
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:12,880
[SPEAKER_01] dupla stakla na prozorima, pa se grijemo,

595
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:15,200
[SPEAKER_01] gledamo gledamo gdje smo toplije, gdje ćemo uz radijator,

596
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:18,759
[SPEAKER_01] oni najlu na prozorima, puše ispod vrata,

597
00:27:18,839 --> 00:27:21,839
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu se ni zatvoriti, zemlja ni počesto puta,

598
00:27:21,839 --> 00:27:23,019
[SPEAKER_01] bez struje, bez vode.

599
00:27:23,019 --> 00:27:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] Mi da im drva ne dovezemo, oni su se posmrzavali.

600
00:27:26,099 --> 00:27:29,279
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, naš preznak je katolička udruga kap dobrote.

601
00:27:29,279 --> 00:27:32,200
[SPEAKER_01] Mi nemamo vjere, nemamo nacije kako nemamo.

602
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] Na čovjek je bitan, nije bitno niko je vire, niko je nacije.

603
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo mi je birali, ćemo biti katolici Hrvati,

604
00:27:38,539 --> 00:27:41,299
[SPEAKER_01] ili ćemo biti pravoslavci, ili ćemo biti muslimani,

605
00:27:41,299 --> 00:27:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] ili nešto drugo.

606
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:44,359
[SPEAKER_00] A Marinko, ti ono što često znaš,

607
00:27:44,359 --> 00:27:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] spomenu da su korisnici kapi prava sirotinja.

608
00:27:47,579 --> 00:27:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi ti definirao tu pravu sirotinju

609
00:27:50,619 --> 00:27:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] u odnosu na možda neke druge ljude

610
00:27:53,539 --> 00:27:55,359
[SPEAKER_00] koje ljudi participiraju sirotinjom

611
00:27:55,359 --> 00:27:59,259
[SPEAKER_00] i zašto misliš da je nastala ta prava sirotinja?

612
00:27:59,259 --> 00:28:02,839
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam došao iz kraja gdje je bilo puno sirotinje,

613
00:28:02,839 --> 00:28:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] iz kamena gdje u kamenu ne može ništa narast.

614
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:09,019
[SPEAKER_01] Tako sam svom pokojnom čači pričao

615
00:28:09,019 --> 00:28:10,900
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam prvi put odlazio u te podrome

616
00:28:10,900 --> 00:28:12,700
[SPEAKER_01] po gradu Zagrebu s paterom Cvekon,

617
00:28:12,700 --> 00:28:15,319
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam vidio da ima i mene čača priča

618
00:28:15,319 --> 00:28:16,940
[SPEAKER_01] da je on za vrime drugog svjetskog rata

619
00:28:16,940 --> 00:28:19,059
[SPEAKER_01] spao na zemljanom podu,

620
00:28:19,059 --> 00:28:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] u jednoj izbi.

621
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:22,799
[SPEAKER_01] Pa sam ja pričao, on uvijek mislio da u Zagrebu

622
00:28:22,799 --> 00:28:25,480
[SPEAKER_01] žive lita gospoda, on govor ne mogu da to virovati

623
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:27,160
[SPEAKER_01] da postoji, da nema neko struje,

624
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] da nema vode i tako u centru grada Zagreba.

625
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:32,220
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo sa cvjetnoga znali nositi vodu

626
00:28:32,220 --> 00:28:33,700
[SPEAKER_01] u kanistrima toj sirotinji.

627
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je materialna sirotinja teške ljudske sudbine.

628
00:28:37,460 --> 00:28:39,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih mogao jednu knjigu napisati

629
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,680
[SPEAKER_01] ne u listovima, nego

630
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:43,140
[SPEAKER_01] dobar metar, dva koraka debelu

631
00:28:43,140 --> 00:28:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] u ljudskim sudbima, što smo se našali

632
00:28:45,599 --> 00:28:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] i emotivacan puno puta

633
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:48,859
[SPEAKER_01] sa tojim sirom asma.

634
00:28:48,859 --> 00:28:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] Smo znali i zaplakati,

635
00:28:50,539 --> 00:28:52,640
[SPEAKER_01] i skupa se, i veseliti.

636
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ta sirotinja, to su,

637
00:28:54,799 --> 00:28:56,660
[SPEAKER_01] mi o njima imamo svima,

638
00:28:56,660 --> 00:28:58,619
[SPEAKER_01] naša socijalna radnica kao da je na terenu

639
00:28:58,619 --> 00:29:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] skupi, to je ovako malo lječički žargon,

640
00:29:02,579 --> 00:29:03,380
[SPEAKER_01] anamnezu,

641
00:29:03,380 --> 00:29:06,900
[SPEAKER_01] ko su, što su i kako im se to dogodilo.

642
00:29:06,900 --> 00:29:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, teške ljudske sudbine.

643
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:10,019
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi nemamo ni ološa,

644
00:29:10,019 --> 00:29:10,859
[SPEAKER_01] ni pijance,

645
00:29:10,859 --> 00:29:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] nego istinska teška sirotinja

646
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,740
[SPEAKER_01] koju je napala i bolest,

647
00:29:14,740 --> 00:29:15,640
[SPEAKER_01] i siromaštu.

648
00:29:15,640 --> 00:29:17,500
[SPEAKER_01] Tu često puta imamo,

649
00:29:17,579 --> 00:29:19,319
[SPEAKER_01] znači, i mamu, i sina,

650
00:29:19,319 --> 00:29:21,319
[SPEAKER_01] ili mamu, i čjer često puta

651
00:29:21,319 --> 00:29:22,619
[SPEAKER_01] ima puno samaca,

652
00:29:22,619 --> 00:29:24,579
[SPEAKER_01] čak nam je jedan znao govoriti

653
00:29:24,579 --> 00:29:25,579
[SPEAKER_01] kada je bio mladić,

654
00:29:25,579 --> 00:29:28,200
[SPEAKER_01] ima puno cura i tako dalje,

655
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:29,299
[SPEAKER_01] nikad se nije ženio

656
00:29:29,299 --> 00:29:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] i kada je došla,

657
00:29:30,019 --> 00:29:32,099
[SPEAKER_01] bolest ga zatekla i tako dalje,

658
00:29:32,099 --> 00:29:33,259
[SPEAKER_01] kada je znao reći

659
00:29:33,259 --> 00:29:35,339
[SPEAKER_01] nemam i ko dodati ni čašu vode.

660
00:29:35,339 --> 00:29:37,519
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi smo njihova obitelj

661
00:29:37,519 --> 00:29:39,200
[SPEAKER_01] i mi se trudimo, evo, nekako

662
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] donijeti jednu toplinu ljudsku,

663
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,279
[SPEAKER_01] donijena, hraniti,

664
00:29:42,279 --> 00:29:43,440
[SPEAKER_01] moraš ti tom čovjeku

665
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:44,920
[SPEAKER_01] pričati o ljubavi u svemu,

666
00:29:45,000 --> 00:29:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] što je naš pokojni patec svek znao reći

667
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] vjera bez dijela je kao zdjela bez jela.

668
00:29:50,579 --> 00:29:51,720
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš mu pričati,

669
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:53,220
[SPEAKER_01] ajde, jedi iz prazne zdjele,

670
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] ne mereš se najediti,

671
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:55,099
[SPEAKER_01] treba ga i nahraniti,

672
00:29:55,099 --> 00:29:57,059
[SPEAKER_01] i napojiti, ogrnuti ga.

673
00:29:57,059 --> 00:29:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi se o njima brinemo

674
00:29:58,519 --> 00:30:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] i da imaju to pa,

675
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] svoju kućicu,

676
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,140
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno svoje dvore,

677
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:05,140
[SPEAKER_01] kako oni to zovu,

678
00:30:05,140 --> 00:30:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] da ih nahranimo, da ih obučimo,

679
00:30:07,019 --> 00:30:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] a isto tako kad umiru,

680
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:10,640
[SPEAKER_01] mi dostojno kao ljude pokopamo.

681
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,660
[SPEAKER_00] A to kad, samo prosit,

682
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] samo to kad kažeš za svoga čaču,

683
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] kako je se prije živjelo teško,

684
00:30:16,019 --> 00:30:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] ja znam i ono,

685
00:30:16,819 --> 00:30:18,180
[SPEAKER_00] i kad mi didovi pričaju,

686
00:30:18,180 --> 00:30:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] ali nekako,

687
00:30:19,220 --> 00:30:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja samo imam krivu sliku,

688
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali imam dojam,

689
00:30:21,539 --> 00:30:23,359
[SPEAKER_00] prije su ljudi u toj sirotinji,

690
00:30:23,359 --> 00:30:23,799
[SPEAKER_00] opet,

691
00:30:23,799 --> 00:30:25,700
[SPEAKER_00] imali su više ljudi

692
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] koji su im uskakali,

693
00:30:26,859 --> 00:30:28,200
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi su više živjeli

694
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:28,859
[SPEAKER_00] na selima,

695
00:30:28,859 --> 00:30:30,160
[SPEAKER_00] u zajednicama i to,

696
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] a danas uopćenito,

697
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] kada smo se izolirali

698
00:30:32,819 --> 00:30:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] jedni od drugih,

699
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:34,339
[SPEAKER_00] sve više,

700
00:30:34,339 --> 00:30:35,400
[SPEAKER_00] pa ja mislio sam,

701
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] Vinko, tebe pitat,

702
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] brine li naše društvo

703
00:30:38,119 --> 00:30:39,720
[SPEAKER_00] i narod naš dovoljno

704
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] o takvoj pravoj sirotinji

705
00:30:41,519 --> 00:30:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] i ako nije što misliš,

706
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:44,259
[SPEAKER_00] do čega je?

707
00:30:44,259 --> 00:30:45,400
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ovako,

708
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,940
[SPEAKER_02] ja bi još dodao,

709
00:30:46,940 --> 00:30:50,579
[SPEAKER_02] da radi naših gledatelja

710
00:30:50,579 --> 00:30:51,980
[SPEAKER_02] jednu bitnu stvar,

711
00:30:52,660 --> 00:30:55,500
[SPEAKER_02] ti naši korisnici,

712
00:30:55,500 --> 00:30:56,220
[SPEAKER_02] štićenici,

713
00:30:56,220 --> 00:30:57,779
[SPEAKER_02] naša braća i naše sestre,

714
00:30:57,779 --> 00:31:00,259
[SPEAKER_02] ja vam ne volim patetiku inače,

715
00:31:00,259 --> 00:31:02,220
[SPEAKER_02] ali ako ja vjerujem u Boga

716
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:03,539
[SPEAKER_02] da je on moj otac,

717
00:31:03,539 --> 00:31:05,339
[SPEAKER_02] onda je svaki čovjek moj brat,

718
00:31:05,339 --> 00:31:06,579
[SPEAKER_02] matematički točno,

719
00:31:06,579 --> 00:31:07,640
[SPEAKER_02] to nije patetika.

720
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:10,299
[SPEAKER_02] I sad ta naša braća i sestre,

721
00:31:10,299 --> 00:31:15,460
[SPEAKER_02] da kad imaju jednu organizaciju,

722
00:31:15,460 --> 00:31:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] to je bitno znat,

723
00:31:16,559 --> 00:31:17,720
[SPEAKER_02] iza sebe,

724
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:19,759
[SPEAKER_02] on se drugačije osjeća

725
00:31:19,759 --> 00:31:21,180
[SPEAKER_02] nego da ima susjeda

726
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:22,220
[SPEAKER_02] koji je jako fin,

727
00:31:22,220 --> 00:31:23,519
[SPEAKER_02] ali je na moru.

728
00:31:23,519 --> 00:31:24,400
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

729
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,839
[SPEAKER_02] Pater Cek je govorio,

730
00:31:25,839 --> 00:31:27,279
[SPEAKER_02] jedan čovjek može

731
00:31:27,279 --> 00:31:29,480
[SPEAKER_02] pomoć napraviti dobro,

732
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:31,099
[SPEAKER_02] ali puno nas,

733
00:31:31,099 --> 00:31:32,279
[SPEAKER_02] organiziranih,

734
00:31:32,279 --> 00:31:33,440
[SPEAKER_02] može napraviti puno,

735
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:35,299
[SPEAKER_02] a potreba je puno.

736
00:31:35,299 --> 00:31:36,279
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

737
00:31:36,279 --> 00:31:38,240
[SPEAKER_02] stalno i organizirano

738
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:40,519
[SPEAKER_02] pomagat bližnje u nevolji,

739
00:31:40,519 --> 00:31:42,119
[SPEAKER_02] to sam ja sebi zado,

740
00:31:42,119 --> 00:31:43,660
[SPEAKER_02] jer mi je Bog zapovjedio

741
00:31:43,660 --> 00:31:45,960
[SPEAKER_02] da ljubim bližnje kao sebe.

742
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:48,539
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ako stalno i organizirano

743
00:31:48,539 --> 00:31:49,460
[SPEAKER_02] brinem o sebi,

744
00:31:49,920 --> 00:31:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] stalno i organizirano ću

745
00:31:51,559 --> 00:31:53,000
[SPEAKER_02] negdje u ovom slučaju

746
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:54,099
[SPEAKER_02] u organizaciji,

747
00:31:54,099 --> 00:31:55,740
[SPEAKER_02] jednoj hrvatskoj

748
00:31:55,740 --> 00:31:57,240
[SPEAKER_02] i kršćanskoj organizaciji,

749
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:59,980
[SPEAKER_02] organizirano i stalno brinuti

750
00:31:59,980 --> 00:32:01,359
[SPEAKER_02] o mojim bližnjima,

751
00:32:01,359 --> 00:32:02,259
[SPEAKER_02] koliko mogu,

752
00:32:02,259 --> 00:32:02,819
[SPEAKER_02] naravno,

753
00:32:02,819 --> 00:32:04,859
[SPEAKER_02] trebaju naši gledateli

754
00:32:04,859 --> 00:32:05,579
[SPEAKER_02] i vjerujem,

755
00:32:05,579 --> 00:32:06,599
[SPEAKER_02] mnogi budući

756
00:32:06,599 --> 00:32:08,039
[SPEAKER_02] naši dragovoljci,

757
00:32:08,039 --> 00:32:09,140
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno volonteri,

758
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:09,680
[SPEAKER_02] znati,

759
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:11,819
[SPEAKER_02] da u zakonu o volontiranju

760
00:32:11,819 --> 00:32:12,960
[SPEAKER_02] ne postoji

761
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,539
[SPEAKER_02] koliko ti trebaš

762
00:32:14,539 --> 00:32:16,079
[SPEAKER_02] tjedno ili mjesečno raditi,

763
00:32:16,079 --> 00:32:17,680
[SPEAKER_02] koliko se može,

764
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:19,920
[SPEAKER_02] u našem statutu također.

765
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] A ja pi dobrote te nitko ni ne prisiljava,

766
00:32:22,619 --> 00:32:23,160
[SPEAKER_00] sve su...

767
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne,

768
00:32:23,380 --> 00:32:25,799
[SPEAKER_02] nego po savjesti koliko komože.

769
00:32:25,799 --> 00:32:27,799
[SPEAKER_02] A naše društvo,

770
00:32:27,799 --> 00:32:28,380
[SPEAKER_02] ja ću,

771
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:29,019
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam,

772
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:30,420
[SPEAKER_02] imali smo nastupa,

773
00:32:30,420 --> 00:32:31,299
[SPEAKER_02] i ja i Marinko,

774
00:32:31,299 --> 00:32:33,240
[SPEAKER_02] bio sam u nastupu

775
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,740
[SPEAKER_02] na Hrvatskoj televiziji

776
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:35,960
[SPEAKER_02] sa paterom Cvekom

777
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:38,039
[SPEAKER_02] i kad sam ja neke stvari rekao,

778
00:32:38,039 --> 00:32:40,160
[SPEAKER_02] onda je voditeljica pitala

779
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:41,460
[SPEAKER_02] patera Cveka,

780
00:32:41,460 --> 00:32:43,299
[SPEAKER_02] imam ja to sačuvano,

781
00:32:43,299 --> 00:32:44,279
[SPEAKER_02] šta on misli o ovome

782
00:32:44,279 --> 00:32:45,339
[SPEAKER_02] što sam ja rekao?

783
00:32:45,339 --> 00:32:48,420
[SPEAKER_02] A tada je pater rekao

784
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:49,619
[SPEAKER_02] da u sve mu podržava

785
00:32:49,619 --> 00:32:50,720
[SPEAKER_02] to što sam rekao.

786
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:52,980
[SPEAKER_02] A ja sam rekao sljedeće,

787
00:32:52,980 --> 00:32:54,500
[SPEAKER_02] ono što i on govori

788
00:32:54,500 --> 00:32:56,720
[SPEAKER_02] i što svi mi mislimo.

789
00:32:56,720 --> 00:32:58,400
[SPEAKER_02] Glavni krivci

790
00:32:58,400 --> 00:33:00,799
[SPEAKER_02] za stanje u društvu,

791
00:33:00,799 --> 00:33:02,400
[SPEAKER_02] za naše siromahe,

792
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:04,200
[SPEAKER_02] za naše gladne,

793
00:33:04,200 --> 00:33:06,180
[SPEAKER_02] za naše beskućnike,

794
00:33:06,180 --> 00:33:08,339
[SPEAKER_02] su, kaže pater Cvek,

795
00:33:08,339 --> 00:33:09,359
[SPEAKER_02] i kažemo mi,

796
00:33:09,359 --> 00:33:10,579
[SPEAKER_02] i kaže mi ja,

797
00:33:10,579 --> 00:33:12,160
[SPEAKER_02] su donositelji

798
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:13,359
[SPEAKER_02] nepravednih zakona.

799
00:33:13,359 --> 00:33:16,519
[SPEAKER_02] Druge,

800
00:33:16,519 --> 00:33:19,279
[SPEAKER_02] koje pater i mi smatramo

801
00:33:19,279 --> 00:33:19,819
[SPEAKER_02] da nose,

802
00:33:19,819 --> 00:33:21,460
[SPEAKER_02] ne volim riječ, krivicu,

803
00:33:21,460 --> 00:33:22,220
[SPEAKER_02] ne volim sudit,

804
00:33:22,220 --> 00:33:23,119
[SPEAKER_02] odgovornost,

805
00:33:23,119 --> 00:33:24,680
[SPEAKER_02] dakle glavnu odgovornost,

806
00:33:24,680 --> 00:33:26,160
[SPEAKER_02] snose donositelji

807
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:27,339
[SPEAKER_02] nepravednih zakona,

808
00:33:27,779 --> 00:33:29,099
[SPEAKER_02] koji recimo kažu

809
00:33:29,099 --> 00:33:31,119
[SPEAKER_02] da saborski zastupnik

810
00:33:31,119 --> 00:33:34,240
[SPEAKER_02] ima 4000 eura mirovinu,

811
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:37,799
[SPEAKER_02] a ova nacionalna naknada,

812
00:33:37,799 --> 00:33:39,619
[SPEAKER_02] koliko je sa 150 eura,

813
00:33:39,619 --> 00:33:40,119
[SPEAKER_02] koliko?

814
00:33:40,119 --> 00:33:40,759
[SPEAKER_01] Tako ne.

815
00:33:40,759 --> 00:33:41,339
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

816
00:33:41,460 --> 00:33:44,299
[SPEAKER_01] tiši nešto kuna na to.

817
00:33:44,299 --> 00:33:44,759
[SPEAKER_01] Je bila.

818
00:33:44,759 --> 00:33:45,240
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

819
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

820
00:33:45,579 --> 00:33:48,539
[SPEAKER_02] Ima dokaz,

821
00:33:48,539 --> 00:33:49,140
[SPEAKER_02] još jedan,

822
00:33:49,140 --> 00:33:52,279
[SPEAKER_02] o neozbiljnosti,

823
00:33:52,279 --> 00:33:53,660
[SPEAKER_02] nepravednosti,

824
00:33:53,660 --> 00:33:54,460
[SPEAKER_02] recimo,

825
00:33:54,460 --> 00:33:56,279
[SPEAKER_02] jedan očiti dokaz.

826
00:33:56,279 --> 00:33:57,700
[SPEAKER_02] Do nekih godina,

827
00:33:57,700 --> 00:33:59,660
[SPEAKER_02] ti si mogo biti u saboru zastupnik,

828
00:33:59,660 --> 00:34:00,319
[SPEAKER_02] dvije godine,

829
00:34:00,319 --> 00:34:02,420
[SPEAKER_02] i dobivaš saborsku mirovinu,

830
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:04,559
[SPEAKER_02] ne znam koliko,

831
00:34:04,559 --> 00:34:06,319
[SPEAKER_02] koliko veliku,

832
00:34:07,220 --> 00:34:09,199
[SPEAKER_02] samim ti što si bio dvije godine

833
00:34:09,199 --> 00:34:10,079
[SPEAKER_02] saborski zastupnik.

834
00:34:10,079 --> 00:34:11,840
[SPEAKER_02] I sad je došla neka druga vlada

835
00:34:11,840 --> 00:34:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] i to je ukinula.

836
00:34:12,559 --> 00:34:13,219
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

837
00:34:13,219 --> 00:34:15,639
[SPEAKER_02] koje je to poigravanje sa narodnim blagom

838
00:34:15,639 --> 00:34:16,679
[SPEAKER_02] i sa narodnim dobrim?

839
00:34:17,679 --> 00:34:19,139
[SPEAKER_02] I u tam smislu je,

840
00:34:19,139 --> 00:34:19,619
[SPEAKER_02] dakle,

841
00:34:19,619 --> 00:34:23,519
[SPEAKER_02] drugu razinu odgovornosti

842
00:34:23,519 --> 00:34:26,099
[SPEAKER_02] za ovo stanje uzdonositelje zakona,

843
00:34:26,099 --> 00:34:27,139
[SPEAKER_02] stanje gladnih,

844
00:34:27,139 --> 00:34:28,260
[SPEAKER_02] nemoćnih,

845
00:34:28,260 --> 00:34:29,219
[SPEAKER_02] nezbrinutih,

846
00:34:29,219 --> 00:34:30,360
[SPEAKER_02] beskućnika,

847
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,599
[SPEAKER_02] snose,

848
00:34:31,599 --> 00:34:32,420
[SPEAKER_02] oni,

849
00:34:32,420 --> 00:34:33,320
[SPEAKER_02] govorio je pater,

850
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:34,019
[SPEAKER_02] cveki mi,

851
00:34:34,019 --> 00:34:36,699
