852
00:34:36,699 --> 00:34:37,900
[SPEAKER_02] koji njima idu prilog.

853
00:34:37,900 --> 00:34:38,380
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, recimo,

854
00:34:38,380 --> 00:34:39,559
[SPEAKER_02] saborski zastupnici.

855
00:34:39,559 --> 00:34:40,480
[SPEAKER_02] Pa nije loša,

856
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:43,639
[SPEAKER_02] baš 4000 eura mjesečno

857
00:34:43,639 --> 00:34:45,480
[SPEAKER_02] ovoga plaća.

858
00:34:46,219 --> 00:34:47,860
[SPEAKER_02] pa im dobro dođu ti zakoni.

859
00:34:47,860 --> 00:34:50,280
[SPEAKER_02] A kaže pater i kažemo mi,

860
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:52,199
[SPEAKER_02] treću razinu odgovornosti

861
00:34:52,199 --> 00:34:52,900
[SPEAKER_02] snose oni

862
00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:55,079
[SPEAKER_02] koji šute na te zakone,

863
00:34:55,079 --> 00:34:58,280
[SPEAKER_02] pa ja tu uključujem i vrh naše crkve.

864
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,400
[SPEAKER_02] Da dovoljno,

865
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,000
[SPEAKER_02] da budem blag,

866
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:01,960
[SPEAKER_02] ne radi,

867
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:04,320
[SPEAKER_02] ne dijeluje u skladu sa,

868
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:06,699
[SPEAKER_02] s razmenu svom položaju,

869
00:35:06,699 --> 00:35:09,800
[SPEAKER_02] u zaštiti naše siroti.

870
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje je možda dobro vrijeme

871
00:35:13,199 --> 00:35:14,840
[SPEAKER_00] da pročitaš,

872
00:35:14,960 --> 00:35:15,760
[SPEAKER_00] ako si voljan,

873
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] svoje pismo,

874
00:35:16,739 --> 00:35:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam ko je to sve sudjelovao

875
00:35:18,940 --> 00:35:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] u pisanju,

876
00:35:19,699 --> 00:35:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] koje si poslao

877
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] svim klubovima

878
00:35:22,639 --> 00:35:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] saborskih zastupnika

879
00:35:23,940 --> 00:35:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] da pročitaju u saboru,

880
00:35:25,699 --> 00:35:27,820
[SPEAKER_00] vezano upravo s pomoći.

881
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] Zahtjev, da.

882
00:35:28,699 --> 00:35:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] I evo,

883
00:35:29,599 --> 00:35:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] možeš reći,

884
00:35:30,219 --> 00:35:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] je li itko i pročitao to

885
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno u saboru

886
00:35:33,159 --> 00:35:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili su svi samo

887
00:35:34,179 --> 00:35:35,639
[SPEAKER_00] šutke odbili?

888
00:35:35,940 --> 00:35:38,400
[SPEAKER_02] Ovako odgovornost je tada

889
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:40,260
[SPEAKER_02] za zakoniti rad udruge.

890
00:35:40,260 --> 00:35:41,900
[SPEAKER_02] Sam slučio ja kao presjednik

891
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:43,099
[SPEAKER_02] i Marinko do presjednik

892
00:35:43,099 --> 00:35:44,420
[SPEAKER_02] i mi smo stali

893
00:35:44,420 --> 00:35:45,639
[SPEAKER_02] iza tog zahtjeva.

894
00:35:45,639 --> 00:35:47,059
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ću pročita dio,

895
00:35:47,059 --> 00:35:48,360
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, ne pismo,

896
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:49,360
[SPEAKER_02] nego zahtjev,

897
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:50,099
[SPEAKER_02] vama,

898
00:35:50,099 --> 00:35:51,599
[SPEAKER_02] ja čitam onako

899
00:35:51,599 --> 00:35:52,800
[SPEAKER_02] kako sam po savjesti

900
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:53,519
[SPEAKER_02] napisao,

901
00:35:53,519 --> 00:35:54,760
[SPEAKER_02] dakle,

902
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:55,539
[SPEAKER_02] zahtjev vama

903
00:35:55,539 --> 00:35:57,260
[SPEAKER_02] takozvanim zastupnicima,

904
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,920
[SPEAKER_02] zagrade časti iznimkama.

905
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:03,059
[SPEAKER_02] Zaustaviti ubijanje ljudi

906
00:36:03,059 --> 00:36:03,659
[SPEAKER_02] glađu,

907
00:36:03,659 --> 00:36:05,679
[SPEAKER_02] smrzavanjem i nemoću

908
00:36:05,679 --> 00:36:07,559
[SPEAKER_02] u novim konclogorima

909
00:36:07,559 --> 00:36:08,380
[SPEAKER_02] u Hrvatskoj

910
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:09,619
[SPEAKER_02] s prilozima.

911
00:36:09,619 --> 00:36:12,179
[SPEAKER_02] I uz ostalo

912
00:36:12,179 --> 00:36:13,119
[SPEAKER_02] sam ja odmah

913
00:36:13,119 --> 00:36:14,500
[SPEAKER_02] na početku tog zahtjeva

914
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:15,320
[SPEAKER_02] napisao,

915
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:17,119
[SPEAKER_02] uz ostalo,

916
00:36:17,119 --> 00:36:23,559
[SPEAKER_02] citat medicinskog priručnika

917
00:36:23,559 --> 00:36:25,320
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvatskog liječničkog zbora.

918
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,840
[SPEAKER_02] Citiram.

919
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,519
[SPEAKER_02] Loša prehrana,

920
00:36:28,519 --> 00:36:30,519
[SPEAKER_02] malnutricija,

921
00:36:30,519 --> 00:36:32,880
[SPEAKER_02] razvija se u stadijima.

922
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:34,559
[SPEAKER_02] U prvom stadiju

923
00:36:34,559 --> 00:36:35,539
[SPEAKER_02] dolazi do promjena

924
00:36:35,539 --> 00:36:37,000
[SPEAKER_02] u razini hranjevih tvari,

925
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:38,519
[SPEAKER_02] u krvi i tkivima.

926
00:36:38,519 --> 00:36:40,340
[SPEAKER_02] Zatim slijede promjene

927
00:36:40,340 --> 00:36:41,480
[SPEAKER_02] u razini enzima,

928
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:44,280
[SPEAKER_02] pa dolazi do loše funkcije

929
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,840
[SPEAKER_02] tjelesnih organa i tkiva,

930
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,780
[SPEAKER_02] a zatim se pojavljaju

931
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:50,340
[SPEAKER_02] simptomi bolesti i smrt.

932
00:36:50,340 --> 00:36:52,260
[SPEAKER_02] Završen citat.

933
00:36:52,260 --> 00:36:53,699
[SPEAKER_02] Drugo,

934
00:36:53,699 --> 00:36:56,039
[SPEAKER_02] hipotermija.

935
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:58,360
[SPEAKER_02] Isto od Hrvatskog liječničkog zbora,

936
