939
00:37:07,699 --> 00:37:10,760
[SPEAKER_02] Posebno su u opasnosti stari ljudi

940
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:12,079
[SPEAKER_02] koji žive sami,

941
00:37:12,079 --> 00:37:14,179
[SPEAKER_02] a to su uglavnom naši korisnici.

942
00:37:14,559 --> 00:37:15,940
[SPEAKER_02] i sjede satima ili danima

943
00:37:15,940 --> 00:37:17,820
[SPEAKER_02] u hladnoj sobi,

944
00:37:17,820 --> 00:37:22,039
[SPEAKER_02] polako postajući zbunjenima

945
00:37:22,039 --> 00:37:23,219
[SPEAKER_02] i bespomoćnima.

946
00:37:23,219 --> 00:37:25,940
[SPEAKER_02] Polovica starijih ljudi

947
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:27,940
[SPEAKER_02] u hipotermiji umre.

948
00:37:27,940 --> 00:37:33,119
[SPEAKER_02] Prije nego ih se nađe

949
00:37:33,119 --> 00:37:34,860
[SPEAKER_02] ili ubrzo nakon toga.

950
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,619
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, to sam im napisao

951
00:37:37,619 --> 00:37:39,119
[SPEAKER_02] saborskim zastupnici.

952
00:37:39,119 --> 00:37:43,199
[SPEAKER_02] Naveo sam im par primjera.

953
00:37:43,199 --> 00:37:43,760
[SPEAKER_02] Recimo,

954
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:44,980
[SPEAKER_02] u Zagrebu,

955
00:37:44,980 --> 00:37:47,179
[SPEAKER_02] u 124 intervencije,

956
00:37:47,179 --> 00:37:48,920
[SPEAKER_02] zapovjednik

957
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:50,500
[SPEAKER_02] vatrogasne službe,

958
00:37:50,500 --> 00:37:51,260
[SPEAKER_02] kaže da je

959
00:37:51,260 --> 00:37:54,320
[SPEAKER_02] u 124 intervencije

960
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:57,519
[SPEAKER_02] 126 osob ljudskih leševa

961
00:37:57,519 --> 00:37:58,179
[SPEAKER_02] su iznijeli

962
00:37:58,179 --> 00:37:59,500
[SPEAKER_02] iz stanova

963
00:37:59,500 --> 00:38:00,519
[SPEAKER_02] gdje su samci

964
00:38:00,519 --> 00:38:01,739
[SPEAKER_02] nezbrinuti

965
