[SPEAKER_02] i možda umirali danima.

966
00:38:03,659 --> 00:38:04,940
[SPEAKER_02] U samo jednoj godini.

967
00:38:04,940 --> 00:38:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] Na pojeroći

968
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:08,679
