971
00:38:13,019 --> 00:38:14,099
[SPEAKER_02] ekonomskog instituta

972
00:38:14,099 --> 00:38:15,219
[SPEAKER_02] u to vrijeme kad pišem

973
00:38:15,219 --> 00:38:15,739
[SPEAKER_02] u Zagrebu,

974
00:38:15,739 --> 00:38:17,840
[SPEAKER_02] roditelji u svakoj petoj obitelji

975
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:19,619
[SPEAKER_02] idu na spavanje gladno.

976
00:38:19,619 --> 00:38:22,280
[SPEAKER_02] Deset posto roditelja

977
