[SPEAKER_02] ne može djeci priuštiti

978
00:38:23,599 --> 00:38:24,860
[SPEAKER_02] tri obroka dnevno,

979
00:38:24,860 --> 00:38:26,400
[SPEAKER_02] a nešto više od 30

980
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:27,880
[SPEAKER_02] nema za voće i povrće.

981
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:30,960
[SPEAKER_02] Najnovi podaci u to vrijeme

982
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:32,320
[SPEAKER_02] 156 tisuća,

983
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,559
[SPEAKER_02] ima ih dostali da ne

984
00:38:33,559 --> 00:38:36,360
[SPEAKER_02] odnosi vremena previše,

985
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:40,260
[SPEAKER_02] 156 476 stanovnika

986
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:41,800
[SPEAKER_02] ima mirovinu manju

987
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:42,679
[SPEAKER_02] od 1000 kuna.

988
00:38:42,679 --> 00:38:44,820
[SPEAKER_02] A za koje neki

989
00:38:44,820 --> 00:38:46,739
[SPEAKER_02] u to doba bestidno traže

990
00:38:46,739 --> 00:38:48,320
[SPEAKER_02] samo 100 kuna povrćice?

991
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:49,900
[SPEAKER_02] I sad na kraju

992
00:38:49,900 --> 00:38:52,280
[SPEAKER_02] isključivanje vode ili struje

993
00:38:52,280 --> 00:38:53,719
[SPEAKER_02] bilo je u slučajima

994
00:38:53,719 --> 00:38:55,159
[SPEAKER_02] naših korisnika,

995
00:38:55,159 --> 00:38:56,679
[SPEAKER_02] pa znam slučaj gde smo mi

996
00:38:56,679 --> 00:38:59,840
[SPEAKER_02] u kanistrima nosili vodu

997
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,360
[SPEAKER_02] našoj stičenici

998
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:02,219
[SPEAKER_02] dva mjeseca,

999
00:39:02,219 --> 00:39:03,000
[SPEAKER_02] nije imala vode.

1000
00:39:03,559 --> 00:39:04,739
[SPEAKER_02] A u isto vrijeme,

1001
00:39:04,739 --> 00:39:07,300
[SPEAKER_02] u samo 58 tvrtki

1002
00:39:07,300 --> 00:39:10,380
[SPEAKER_02] u paketu 2019. godine

1003
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:12,320
[SPEAKER_02] u skladu sa propisima

1004
00:39:12,320 --> 00:39:13,840
[SPEAKER_02] koji to odobravaju,

1005
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:16,219
[SPEAKER_02] a o kojima smo već rekli,

1006
00:39:16,219 --> 00:39:19,900
[SPEAKER_02] donošenje tih nepravednih zakona,

1007
00:39:19,900 --> 00:39:22,340
[SPEAKER_02] znači u paketu 2019. godine

1008
00:39:22,340 --> 00:39:24,880
[SPEAKER_02] 58 tvrtki je otpisano

1009
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:27,840
[SPEAKER_02] pola milijarde kuna duga.

1010
00:39:28,579 --> 00:39:30,119
[SPEAKER_02] Duga, znači ne morate vratiti,

1011
00:39:30,119 --> 00:39:32,179
[SPEAKER_02] 58 milijardi.

1012
00:39:32,179 --> 00:39:33,380
[SPEAKER_02] A ljudima se gasi.

1013
00:39:33,380 --> 00:39:33,860
[SPEAKER_02] Tako je.

1014
00:39:33,860 --> 00:39:35,320
[SPEAKER_02] E sad bi ja ovo pročito,

1015
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:39,840
[SPEAKER_02] da ne čitam sve ovo što smatram,

1016
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:42,519
[SPEAKER_02] da je dobro ga podijeliti,

1017
00:39:42,519 --> 00:39:43,719
[SPEAKER_02] jer je aktualno i danas.

1018
00:39:43,719 --> 00:39:45,960
[SPEAKER_02] Takozvani,

1019
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:49,179
[SPEAKER_02] znači u tom zahtjevu je napisano još ovo,

1020
00:39:49,340 --> 00:39:50,679
[SPEAKER_02] takozvani bogoljubi,

1021
00:39:50,679 --> 00:39:51,559
[SPEAKER_02] domoljubi,

1022
00:39:51,559 --> 00:39:52,840
[SPEAKER_02] čovjekoljubi,

1023
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:54,199
[SPEAKER_02] borci za ljudska prava,

1024
00:39:54,199 --> 00:39:56,139
[SPEAKER_02] koji ste plaćeni,

1025
00:39:56,139 --> 00:39:57,579
[SPEAKER_02] ne govorim ja ovolom te,

1026
00:39:57,579 --> 00:39:58,760
[SPEAKER_02] koji ste plaćeni,

1027
00:39:58,760 --> 00:40:00,619
[SPEAKER_02] da donosite zakone

1028
00:40:00,619 --> 00:40:03,380
[SPEAKER_02] i štitite siromahe slabe i nemoćne.

1029
00:40:03,380 --> 00:40:04,539
[SPEAKER_02] To vam je plaća,

1030
00:40:04,539 --> 00:40:05,619
[SPEAKER_02] plaćeni ste za to.

1031
00:40:05,619 --> 00:40:07,880
[SPEAKER_02] I njihovo pravo na života,

1032
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:09,820
[SPEAKER_02] koji donosite nepravedne zakone,

1033
00:40:09,820 --> 00:40:11,579
[SPEAKER_02] ili vi koji se mirite

1034
00:40:11,579 --> 00:40:13,780
[SPEAKER_02] i šutite na te sotonske

1035
00:40:13,780 --> 00:40:15,159
[SPEAKER_02] i zločinačke zakone,

1036
00:40:15,159 --> 00:40:17,360
[SPEAKER_02] koja to ljudska prava vi štitite?

1037
00:40:18,199 --> 00:40:19,780
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje je vaša domovina

1038
00:40:19,780 --> 00:40:20,760
[SPEAKER_02] koju vi ljubite?

1039
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:24,219
[SPEAKER_02] Ako nije tamo gdje ona najviše pati,

1040
00:40:24,219 --> 00:40:27,699
[SPEAKER_02] gdje je njezi najsveti dio,

1041
00:40:27,699 --> 00:40:28,920
[SPEAKER_02] njezini ljudi,

1042
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:30,900
[SPEAKER_02] koji su, ne zaboravite,

1043
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:32,820
[SPEAKER_02] Boži sinovi kćeri,

1044
00:40:32,820 --> 00:40:33,940
[SPEAKER_02] njegova djeca,

1045
00:40:33,940 --> 00:40:35,280
[SPEAKER_02] a naša braća.

1046
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:38,440
[SPEAKER_02] Koliko ste minuta saborske borbe

1047
00:40:38,440 --> 00:40:40,780
[SPEAKER_02] i rasprave potrošili na njih?

1048
00:40:40,780 --> 00:40:43,599
[SPEAKER_02] Za svoju gladnu,

1049
00:40:43,599 --> 00:40:45,699
[SPEAKER_02] prozemlu i nemoćnu braću.

1050
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:51,059
[SPEAKER_02] Kojoj su to manjini

1051
00:40:51,059 --> 00:40:52,519
[SPEAKER_02] u hrvatskoj životi

1052
00:40:52,519 --> 00:40:53,800
[SPEAKER_02] još toliko ugroženi?

1053
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:55,920
[SPEAKER_02] Koja još manjina

1054
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,559
[SPEAKER_02] osim njih toliko pati?

1055
00:40:57,559 --> 00:40:58,860
[SPEAKER_02] Smrzava se,

1056
00:40:58,860 --> 00:41:00,300
[SPEAKER_02] jer govore o pravima manjina.

1057
00:41:00,300 --> 00:41:02,360
[SPEAKER_02] Smrzava se i umire

1058
00:41:02,360 --> 00:41:03,800
[SPEAKER_02] gladujući danima,

1059
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,800
[SPEAKER_02] mjesecima, godinama.

1060
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:07,820
[SPEAKER_02] Koga vi zastupate,

1061
00:41:07,820 --> 00:41:09,820
[SPEAKER_02] a koga ne zastupate?

1062
00:41:10,519 --> 00:41:11,539
[SPEAKER_02] Imate li ljubavi?

1063
00:41:11,539 --> 00:41:13,639
[SPEAKER_02] I sad bi ovo još htio pročitati,

1064
00:41:13,639 --> 00:41:18,260
[SPEAKER_02] jer ljubav zle zakone ne priznaje.

1065
00:41:18,260 --> 00:41:20,940
[SPEAKER_02] Oni nju i zakrčuju put.

1066
00:41:20,940 --> 00:41:22,440
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubavi hlomi.

1067
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:25,019
[SPEAKER_02] Znači ne slaže se s njima,

1068
00:41:25,019 --> 00:41:26,340
[SPEAKER_02] suprostavlja se.

1069
00:41:26,340 --> 00:41:28,300
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav nikad ne odustaje.

1070
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:31,059
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ne pristaje na nepravdu.

1071
00:41:31,059 --> 00:41:33,599
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ne traži proviziju.

1072
00:41:33,599 --> 00:41:36,820
[SPEAKER_02] Znamo mi šta je provizija

1073
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:37,840
[SPEAKER_02] i koju je traži.

1074
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,679
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubavi se gade,

1075
00:41:39,679 --> 00:41:41,440
[SPEAKER_02] veze i korupcije,

1076
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:44,079
[SPEAKER_02] i ona s njima ne sjeda za isti stup.

1077
00:41:44,079 --> 00:41:48,099
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav se ne boji nikoga nego Boga

1078
00:41:48,099 --> 00:41:50,260
[SPEAKER_02] i samo se njemu klanja.

1079
00:41:50,260 --> 00:41:53,480
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ne poznaje povlačenje

1080
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:54,400
[SPEAKER_02] ni jedan sat,

1081
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,900
[SPEAKER_02] a kamoli jedan dan.

1082
00:41:55,900 --> 00:41:58,539
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ustrajava,

1083
00:41:58,900 --> 00:41:59,420
[SPEAKER_02] vječno.

1084
00:41:59,420 --> 00:42:01,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ne priznaje,

1085
