[SPEAKER_02] niti poznaje poraze.

1086
00:42:03,679 --> 00:42:07,340
[SPEAKER_02] Jedna kap ljubavi veća je

1087
00:42:07,340 --> 00:42:09,119
[SPEAKER_02] od bilo kojeg oceana

1088
00:42:09,119 --> 00:42:10,159
[SPEAKER_02] i stvarnosti

1089
00:42:10,159 --> 00:42:11,820
[SPEAKER_02] u kojoj nema ljubavi.

1090
00:42:11,820 --> 00:42:15,599
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ljubi svakoga brata čovjeka,

1091
00:42:15,599 --> 00:42:17,179
[SPEAKER_02] a ne čovještvo prezire.

1092
00:42:17,179 --> 00:42:19,079
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav se ne hrani

1093
00:42:19,079 --> 00:42:20,440
[SPEAKER_02] i ne svjedoči

1094
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:22,219
[SPEAKER_02] velikim, pod navodnike,

1095
00:42:22,219 --> 00:42:23,039
[SPEAKER_02] domoljubnim,

1096
00:42:23,039 --> 00:42:24,699
[SPEAKER_02] sladunjavim govorima,

1097
00:42:24,699 --> 00:42:26,139
[SPEAKER_02] nego se hrani

1098
00:42:26,139 --> 00:42:28,280
[SPEAKER_02] i svjedoči svojim dijelima.

1099
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:30,539
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ne brine za sebe,

1100
00:42:30,539 --> 00:42:31,800
[SPEAKER_02] nego brine

1101
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:35,659
[SPEAKER_02] i gine

1102
00:42:35,659 --> 00:42:38,099
[SPEAKER_02] za one koji ljubi.

1103
00:42:38,099 --> 00:42:41,260
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ne brine za svoj ego,

1104
00:42:41,260 --> 00:42:43,099
[SPEAKER_02] jer ona ega nema.

1105
00:42:43,099 --> 00:42:45,940
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav ne sumnja u pobjedu.

1106
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:50,400
[SPEAKER_02] Takozvani narodni zastupnici,

1107
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:51,519
[SPEAKER_02] čast iznimkama,

1108
00:42:51,519 --> 00:42:53,059
[SPEAKER_02] jeste li s nepravedinim

1109
00:42:53,059 --> 00:42:54,519
[SPEAKER_02] izročinačkim zakonima

1110
00:42:54,519 --> 00:42:55,519
[SPEAKER_02] prethodnih dana,

1111
00:42:55,519 --> 00:42:57,099
[SPEAKER_02] mjeseci, godina i sada,

1112
00:42:57,099 --> 00:42:59,820
[SPEAKER_02] su učesnici ubijanja naših ljudi,

1113
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:01,559
[SPEAKER_02] glađu, smrzavanjem,

1114
00:43:01,559 --> 00:43:02,719
[SPEAKER_02] žeđu i bolešću.

1115
00:43:03,139 --> 00:43:05,000
[SPEAKER_02] Zahtjer za nemoćne,

1116
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:06,059
[SPEAKER_02] mučene glađu,

1117
00:43:06,059 --> 00:43:07,940
[SPEAKER_02] bolešću i smrzavanjem,

1118
00:43:07,940 --> 00:43:10,559
[SPEAKER_02] najhitnije donijeti odredbe zakona

1119
00:43:10,559 --> 00:43:11,360
[SPEAKER_02] koje jamče,

1120
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:12,940
[SPEAKER_02] tri obroka dnevno,

1121
00:43:12,940 --> 00:43:14,820
[SPEAKER_02] vodu, struju i grijanje,

1122
00:43:14,820 --> 00:43:16,920
[SPEAKER_02] evidenciju svih ugroženih,

1123
00:43:16,920 --> 00:43:19,840
[SPEAKER_02] nemoćnih i njihovo obilaženje i zaštita.

1124
00:43:20,340 --> 00:43:22,139
[SPEAKER_02] Svakom beskućniku osiguran

1125
00:43:22,139 --> 00:43:23,239
[SPEAKER_02] stalan boravak

1126
00:43:23,239 --> 00:43:25,699
[SPEAKER_02] u zatvorenom i toplom prostoru.

1127
00:43:25,699 --> 00:43:27,579
[SPEAKER_02] Redovni nadzor

1128
00:43:27,579 --> 00:43:29,519
[SPEAKER_02] provedbe navedenih djelovanja.

1129
00:43:29,519 --> 00:43:30,820
[SPEAKER_02] Evo da ne širim,

1130
00:43:30,820 --> 00:43:32,619
[SPEAKER_02] to je bilo pismo

1131
00:43:32,619 --> 00:43:34,039
[SPEAKER_02] saborskih zastupnika,

1132
00:43:34,039 --> 00:43:36,280
[SPEAKER_02] iza kojega mi stojimo i danas

1133
00:43:36,280 --> 00:43:38,380
[SPEAKER_02] i smatrali smo da završim,

1134
00:43:38,380 --> 00:43:40,340
[SPEAKER_02] da smo mi potpisali

1135
00:43:40,340 --> 00:43:41,920
[SPEAKER_02] ugovor sa kapi dobrote,

1136
00:43:41,920 --> 00:43:43,179
[SPEAKER_02] da ćemo mi brinuti

1137
00:43:43,179 --> 00:43:46,679
[SPEAKER_02] i štititi te naše korisnike

1138
00:43:46,679 --> 00:43:48,360
[SPEAKER_02] i njihova zakonska

1139
00:43:48,360 --> 00:43:49,480
[SPEAKER_02] i svaka druga prava

1140
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:50,519
[SPEAKER_02] i to smo ja i Marinko

1141
00:43:50,519 --> 00:43:52,340
[SPEAKER_02] po savjesti tako napravili

1142
00:43:52,340 --> 00:43:53,139
[SPEAKER_02] u dva navrata,

1143
00:43:53,139 --> 00:43:54,079
[SPEAKER_02] ne samo jednom,

1144
00:43:54,079 --> 00:43:55,239
[SPEAKER_02] nego u dva navrata.

1145
00:43:55,239 --> 00:43:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] Evo Vinko, ako može

1146
00:43:56,460 --> 00:43:58,880
[SPEAKER_01] ispričati od našem dragom,

1147
00:43:58,880 --> 00:44:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] prijateljem mogu reći,

1148
00:44:00,420 --> 00:44:01,679
[SPEAKER_01] bio je nekad naši volonter,

1149
00:44:01,679 --> 00:44:02,619
[SPEAKER_01] uzorio mati,

1150
00:44:02,619 --> 00:44:04,300
[SPEAKER_01] kada je završio bolnice,

1151
00:44:04,300 --> 00:44:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] evo Vinko može to ispričati,

1152
00:44:06,039 --> 00:44:06,860
[SPEAKER_01] kako je molio

1153
00:44:06,860 --> 00:44:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] da ga ne puste iz bolnice,

1154
00:44:10,079 --> 00:44:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] evo Vinko,

1155
00:44:10,460 --> 00:44:11,579
[SPEAKER_01] u kratkim crtama, da.

1156
00:44:11,579 --> 00:44:14,320
[SPEAKER_01] Evo bili smo u neki dan u posti,

1157
00:44:14,320 --> 00:44:15,679
[SPEAKER_01] najdragi brat mate,

1158
00:44:15,679 --> 00:44:17,179
[SPEAKER_01] koji nažalost obolio,

1159
00:44:17,179 --> 00:44:18,179
[SPEAKER_01] mi ga posjećujemo,

1160
00:44:18,619 --> 00:44:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] a završio je u bolnici

1161
00:44:20,539 --> 00:44:21,500
[SPEAKER_01] u Vrapču.

1162
00:44:21,500 --> 00:44:23,679
[SPEAKER_01] I dole je,

1163
00:44:23,679 --> 00:44:26,019
[SPEAKER_01] trebalo se ga otpustiti,

1164
00:44:26,019 --> 00:44:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] on je molio svoju

1165
00:44:27,699 --> 00:44:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] doktoricu koja je ga vodila,

1166
00:44:29,559 --> 00:44:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] da ga ne otpuste,

1167
00:44:30,820 --> 00:44:31,519
[SPEAKER_01] ona ga pitala,

1168
00:44:31,519 --> 00:44:31,920
[SPEAKER_01] zašto?

1169
00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:33,400
[SPEAKER_01] Kada zato što ja ovde imam

1170
00:44:33,400 --> 00:44:34,219
[SPEAKER_01] tri objede.

1171
00:44:34,219 --> 00:44:36,320
[SPEAKER_01] On samo jedan objed dobiva,

1172
00:44:36,320 --> 00:44:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] koji dobiva od socijalne službe,

1173
00:44:38,440 --> 00:44:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] od grada,

1174
00:44:39,420 --> 00:44:40,940
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno tu od jedne župe,

1175
00:44:41,079 --> 00:44:43,460
[SPEAKER_01] jedan objed molio je da ostane u bolnici,

1176
00:44:43,460 --> 00:44:45,900
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su psihčki bolesni ljudi,

1177
00:44:45,900 --> 00:44:48,780
[SPEAKER_01] gdje on nažalost nije tamo ni pripadao za luta,

1178
00:44:48,780 --> 00:44:51,179
[SPEAKER_01] od tamo ga je odvela hitna služba,

1179
00:44:51,179 --> 00:44:52,639
[SPEAKER_01] gdje nije trebao biti,

1180
00:44:52,639 --> 00:44:54,219
[SPEAKER_01] da ostane u bolnici,

1181
00:44:54,219 --> 00:44:56,340
[SPEAKER_01] da je to da može dobiti tri objeda,

1182
00:44:56,340 --> 00:44:57,900
[SPEAKER_01] jer je rekao da je gladan.

1183
00:44:58,719 --> 00:44:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo bolinca,

1184
00:44:59,960 --> 00:45:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi u zatvoru to dobiju,

1185
00:45:01,739 --> 00:45:03,260
[SPEAKER_00] to što ste vi tu naveli,

1186
00:45:03,260 --> 00:45:06,800
[SPEAKER_00] znači nisu to neki zahtjevi za luksuziranje,

1187
00:45:06,800 --> 00:45:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] nego kakav je bio odaziv zastupnika,

1188
00:45:10,840 --> 00:45:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] je li tko odgovorio,

1189
00:45:12,119 --> 00:45:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] je li tko na to reagirao?

1190
00:45:13,900 --> 00:45:15,420
[SPEAKER_02] Još bih nešto ovdje dodao,

1191
00:45:15,420 --> 00:45:16,780
[SPEAKER_02] i ja čitano je u saboru,

1192
00:45:16,780 --> 00:45:19,400
[SPEAKER_02] evo kad me pitaš,

1193
00:45:19,400 --> 00:45:21,280
[SPEAKER_02] međutim,

1194
00:45:21,280 --> 00:45:26,920
[SPEAKER_02] taj zastupnik koji je čitao dio ovoga zahtjeva,

1195
00:45:27,380 --> 00:45:30,940
[SPEAKER_02] je imao pet minuta u tom trenutku prava na govor

1196
00:45:30,940 --> 00:45:36,340
[SPEAKER_02] i reću ime čovjeka koji ga je pristojno prekinuo,

1197
00:45:36,340 --> 00:45:38,300
[SPEAKER_02] jer je isteklo vrijeme,

1198
00:45:38,300 --> 00:45:39,860
[SPEAKER_02] ali je rekao,

1199
00:45:39,860 --> 00:45:42,980
[SPEAKER_02] znači mislim da je bio u to vrijeme

1200
00:45:42,980 --> 00:45:45,340
[SPEAKER_02] i pod presjenik vlade gospodina Radin.

1201
00:45:45,340 --> 00:45:47,219
[SPEAKER_02] Pod presjenik Sabora.

1202
00:45:47,219 --> 00:45:47,960
[SPEAKER_02] Sabora, da.

1203
00:45:47,960 --> 00:45:49,260
[SPEAKER_02] Ne vlade, Sabora.

1204
00:45:49,260 --> 00:45:50,079
[SPEAKER_02] Vodio sjednicu.

1205
00:45:50,079 --> 00:45:52,980
[SPEAKER_02] Da, i on je prekinuo radi minutaže,

1206
00:45:52,980 --> 00:45:56,179
[SPEAKER_02] ali prekinuo je, citiram ga,

1207
00:45:56,179 --> 00:45:58,260
[SPEAKER_02] znam da je ovo bolna tema,

1208
00:45:58,260 --> 00:46:02,539
[SPEAKER_02] ali morate prekinu ovoga.

1209
00:46:02,539 --> 00:46:05,340
[SPEAKER_02] I još bih nešto rekao ovdje ako mogu.

1210
00:46:06,599 --> 00:46:16,380
[SPEAKER_02] gospodin premijer sadašnji je kazao da je deset tisuća izbjeglica

1211
00:46:16,380 --> 00:46:23,559
[SPEAKER_02] iz Ukrajine pripremljeno da ih se smijesti

1212
00:46:23,559 --> 00:46:31,920
[SPEAKER_02] i da će sve napraviti da im pruži ugodni normalni boravak,

1213
00:46:31,920 --> 00:46:32,900
[SPEAKER_02] ajmo tako reći.

1214
00:46:33,039 --> 00:46:42,599
[SPEAKER_02] i to je dobro da ljudima našoj braći iz Ukrajine ili bilo kome pomognemo.

1215
00:46:42,699 --> 00:46:46,320
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim, kako to u tako kratkom vremenu

1216
00:46:46,320 --> 00:46:49,420
[SPEAKER_02] taj gospodin premijer

1217
00:46:49,420 --> 00:46:54,579
[SPEAKER_02] ima mjesta za deset tisuća izbjeglica

1218
00:46:54,579 --> 00:46:58,599
[SPEAKER_02] smjestiti i pružiti im normalni život,

1219
00:46:59,059 --> 00:47:02,400
[SPEAKER_02] a trideset godina hrvatska sirotinja,

1220
00:47:02,400 --> 00:47:04,940
[SPEAKER_02] dvije tisuće beskućnika umire

1221
00:47:04,940 --> 00:47:10,679
[SPEAKER_02] po ovim kolodvorima,

1222
00:47:10,679 --> 00:47:12,380
[SPEAKER_02] pod mostovima,

1223
00:47:12,380 --> 00:47:14,780
[SPEAKER_02] u njihovim potleušicama.

1224
00:47:14,780 --> 00:47:16,719
[SPEAKER_02] Jedno ja sam dok sam išao na posao,

1225
00:47:16,719 --> 00:47:17,619
[SPEAKER_02] idem tramajem,

1226
00:47:17,619 --> 00:47:21,679
[SPEAKER_02] izlazi žena iz jedne potleušice

1227
00:47:21,679 --> 00:47:24,440
[SPEAKER_02] i čisti ovako oči,

1228
00:47:24,440 --> 00:47:26,239
[SPEAKER_02] ne od suza,

1229
00:47:26,239 --> 00:47:27,920
[SPEAKER_02] nego bilo je hladno,

1230
00:47:27,920 --> 00:47:29,559
[SPEAKER_02] pa ono tek na spavanje,

1231
00:47:29,559 --> 00:47:31,239
[SPEAKER_02] nema jednu ruku.

1232
00:47:31,239 --> 00:47:34,500
[SPEAKER_02] I ona prosi često,

1233
00:47:34,500 --> 00:47:36,579
[SPEAKER_02] mislim da je po nacionalnosti Romkinja

1234
00:47:36,579 --> 00:47:39,039
[SPEAKER_02] naša sestra Romkinja,

1235
00:47:39,039 --> 00:47:41,119
[SPEAKER_02] i prosi ona,

1236
00:47:41,119 --> 00:47:42,420
[SPEAKER_02] i ja jednom pitam

1237
00:47:42,420 --> 00:47:44,139
[SPEAKER_02] u tramaju,

1238
00:47:44,139 --> 00:47:46,739
[SPEAKER_02] je li ti da neko je,

1239
00:47:46,739 --> 00:47:48,139
[SPEAKER_02] nema glume, nema ruke,

1240
00:47:48,139 --> 00:47:50,659
[SPEAKER_02] a nosi ponekad i djet.

1241
00:47:50,659 --> 00:47:53,619
[SPEAKER_02] Znate šta mi je odgovorila u sekundi,

1242
00:47:53,619 --> 00:47:54,719
[SPEAKER_02] na moje pitanje,

1243
00:47:54,719 --> 00:47:55,840
[SPEAKER_02] pa je li ti da,

1244
00:47:55,840 --> 00:47:57,340
[SPEAKER_02] pruži li ti narod,

1245
00:47:57,460 --> 00:47:57,639
[SPEAKER_02] što,

1246
00:47:57,639 --> 00:47:59,039
[SPEAKER_02] a ona koji stopa,

1247
00:47:59,039 --> 00:48:00,219
[SPEAKER_02] gospodine,

1248
00:48:00,219 --> 00:48:02,119
[SPEAKER_02] ljudi su zli.

1249
00:48:02,119 --> 00:48:05,420
[SPEAKER_02] To je vi odgovor.

1250
00:48:05,420 --> 00:48:07,920
[SPEAKER_02] Evo to sam htio reći još

1251
00:48:07,920 --> 00:48:08,940
[SPEAKER_02] u vezi ovoga,

1252
00:48:08,940 --> 00:48:11,099
[SPEAKER_02] ovoga slučaja,

1253
00:48:11,099 --> 00:48:13,500
[SPEAKER_02] pisma saborskim zastupnicima,

1254
00:48:13,500 --> 00:48:16,480
[SPEAKER_02] osmještaju deset tisuća izvjeglica

1255
00:48:16,480 --> 00:48:17,579
[SPEAKER_02] iz Bogu Fala,

1256
00:48:17,579 --> 00:48:18,400
[SPEAKER_02] iz Ukrajine,

1257
00:48:18,719 --> 00:48:20,460
[SPEAKER_02] a šta je sa ovima našima,

1258
00:48:20,460 --> 00:48:22,699
[SPEAKER_02] koji tu tako umiru

1259
00:48:22,699 --> 00:48:24,340
[SPEAKER_02] na cesti po ovoj hladnoći.

1260
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost,

1261
00:48:27,000 --> 00:48:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] ne znaju se prioriteti

1262
00:48:29,159 --> 00:48:31,440
[SPEAKER_00] i ne znam,

1263
00:48:31,440 --> 00:48:33,340
[SPEAKER_00] vi ste s tim mene najviše i kupili,

1264
00:48:33,340 --> 00:48:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam vas upoznao,

1265
00:48:34,400 --> 00:48:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] kad ste baš

1266
00:48:35,940 --> 00:48:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] to u svim svojim izlaganjima

1267
00:48:37,980 --> 00:48:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] okazujete na to,

1268
00:48:38,940 --> 00:48:40,400
[SPEAKER_00] kako smo mi spremni

1269
00:48:40,400 --> 00:48:42,699
[SPEAKER_00] sve moguće svjetske probleme

1270
00:48:42,699 --> 00:48:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] žaliti,

1271
00:48:43,219 --> 00:48:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] tugovat,

1272
00:48:43,940 --> 00:48:45,260
[SPEAKER_00] sve moguće ratove,

1273
00:48:45,260 --> 00:48:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] sve moguće probleme

1274
00:48:46,599 --> 00:48:47,780
[SPEAKER_00] negdje tamo daleko,

1275
00:48:47,780 --> 00:48:49,719
[SPEAKER_00] a kad je brat pored tebe,

1276
00:48:49,719 --> 00:48:51,320
[SPEAKER_00] to je najteže izaći.

1277
00:48:51,320 --> 00:48:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi ne znaju u zgradama

1278
00:48:52,719 --> 00:48:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] kako im se zove susjed,

1279
00:48:54,159 --> 00:48:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] kamo ali da nešto.

1280
00:48:55,280 --> 00:48:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] To bi se nadoveza,

1281
00:48:57,539 --> 00:48:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] Pater Cek na jednom

1282
00:48:58,599 --> 00:48:59,840
[SPEAKER_01] takvu društu pričao,

1283
00:48:59,840 --> 00:49:01,599
[SPEAKER_01] kao je majka Terezija pokojna

1284
00:49:01,599 --> 00:49:02,599
[SPEAKER_01] prolazila ko Zagreb,

1285
00:49:02,599 --> 00:49:03,440
[SPEAKER_01] te godine išla

1286
00:49:03,440 --> 00:49:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] preuzeti Nobelovu nagradu

1287
00:49:05,920 --> 00:49:06,420
[SPEAKER_01] i u Zagrebu

1288
00:49:06,420 --> 00:49:07,139
[SPEAKER_01] i se zadržala,

1289
00:49:07,139 --> 00:49:08,780
[SPEAKER_01] volila je doći u Zagrebu,

1290
00:49:08,860 --> 00:49:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatsku i višla je

1291
00:49:10,539 --> 00:49:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] nekim derutnim sandalama,

1292
00:49:11,960 --> 00:49:13,860
[SPEAKER_01] koje su bile polo raspadnute

1293
00:49:13,860 --> 00:49:15,099
[SPEAKER_01] i dan danas se te sandale

1294
00:49:15,099 --> 00:49:17,039
[SPEAKER_01] čuvaju u Zagrebu,

1295
00:49:17,039 --> 00:49:18,760
[SPEAKER_01] da je kupe neke cipale

1296
00:49:18,760 --> 00:49:19,219
[SPEAKER_01] i tako.

1297
00:49:19,219 --> 00:49:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] I ona u tom društvu

1298
00:49:20,380 --> 00:49:21,679
[SPEAKER_01] rekla, da skratim priču,

1299
00:49:21,679 --> 00:49:24,300
[SPEAKER_01] kao vi budite misjonari tu

1300
00:49:24,300 --> 00:49:25,780
[SPEAKER_01] u svom gradu,

1301
00:49:25,780 --> 00:49:26,860
[SPEAKER_01] u svoje države naša.

1302
00:49:26,860 --> 00:49:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ima vremena iz Afriku.

1303
00:49:28,539 --> 00:49:29,900
[SPEAKER_01] Tako ja znam ovako reći,

1304
00:49:29,900 --> 00:49:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] budimo misjonari

1305
00:49:31,039 --> 00:49:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] u svojoj ulici,

1306
00:49:32,019 --> 00:49:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] u svome stubištu,

1307
00:49:33,119 --> 00:49:34,639
[SPEAKER_01] u svome selu.

1308
00:49:34,639 --> 00:49:36,539
[SPEAKER_01] Svjedočimo vjeru

1309
00:49:36,539 --> 00:49:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] čineći dobra dijela.

1310
00:49:38,219 --> 00:49:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] vjera bez dijela je mrtva,

1311
00:49:39,519 --> 00:49:41,260
[SPEAKER_01] moraš milion krunica

1312
00:49:41,260 --> 00:49:43,300
[SPEAKER_01] izmoliti ako brata svoga susjeda

1313
00:49:43,300 --> 00:49:43,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji umire,

1314
00:49:43,940 --> 00:49:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] pokraj tebe tu gladan,

1315
00:49:45,579 --> 00:49:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] ne pomogneš mu badavati

1316
00:49:47,380 --> 00:49:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] i krunice,

1317
00:49:48,380 --> 00:49:49,320
[SPEAKER_01] treba moliti

1318
00:49:49,320 --> 00:49:51,860
[SPEAKER_01] i činiti dobra dijela.

1319
00:49:51,860 --> 00:49:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ona je uvijek tako znala

1320
00:49:54,300 --> 00:49:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] to simboliku jednu,

1321
00:49:56,280 --> 00:49:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] kao budite misjonari

1322
00:49:57,559 --> 00:49:58,460
[SPEAKER_01] u svojoj domovni,

1323
00:49:58,460 --> 00:49:59,280
[SPEAKER_01] imate vi ovde,

1324
00:49:59,280 --> 00:50:01,280
[SPEAKER_01] što činiti dobra,

1325
00:50:01,280 --> 00:50:02,639
[SPEAKER_01] ima i sirotinje i svega.

1326
00:50:02,780 --> 00:50:04,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ona to kaže,

1327
00:50:04,860 --> 00:50:05,699
[SPEAKER_00] onda nema ništa.

1328
00:50:05,699 --> 00:50:07,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je to zna o društvu izpričati.

1329
00:50:07,559 --> 00:50:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ja,

1330
00:50:08,039 --> 00:50:10,980
[SPEAKER_01] trudimo biti misjonar u svojoj domovini,

1331
00:50:10,980 --> 00:50:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] pomažući onima,

1332
00:50:12,619 --> 00:50:14,800
[SPEAKER_01] najprije onima koji su najbjedniji,

1333
00:50:14,800 --> 00:50:16,860
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda idemo i onima i drugima,

1334
00:50:16,860 --> 00:50:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] i tako i malima,

1335
00:50:17,860 --> 00:50:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] i starima,

1336
00:50:18,500 --> 00:50:19,199
[SPEAKER_01] i bolesnijima.

1337
00:50:19,579 --> 00:50:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] I to je možda i najbolja poruka,

1338
00:50:21,500 --> 00:50:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] koju vi sami,

1339
00:50:22,760 --> 00:50:23,260
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem,

1340
00:50:23,260 --> 00:50:24,239
[SPEAKER_00] želite poslat,

1341
00:50:24,239 --> 00:50:27,800
[SPEAKER_00] da svak od najnižih treba krenuti,

1342
00:50:27,800 --> 00:50:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] pa do državnog vrha će,

1343
00:50:29,179 --> 00:50:29,760
[SPEAKER_00] nadamo se,

1344
00:50:29,760 --> 00:50:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] doći kad se stvori dovoljna kritična masa,

1345
00:50:33,179 --> 00:50:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] ko što često pričamo,

1346
00:50:34,400 --> 00:50:36,639
[SPEAKER_00] i zaopćenito političke promjene.

1347
00:50:36,639 --> 00:50:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost,

1348
00:50:37,860 --> 00:50:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] ništa ne ide preko noći,

1349
00:50:39,420 --> 00:50:41,760
[SPEAKER_00] sve dok se ljudi sami ne potrude.

1350
00:50:41,760 --> 00:50:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] Mlade, naše moramo mlade,

1351
00:50:43,579 --> 00:50:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

1352
00:50:44,079 --> 00:50:47,440
[SPEAKER_01] Bogu hvala i slava što smo se upoznali,

1353
00:50:47,519 --> 00:50:48,800
[SPEAKER_01] i o tom ćemo spomenuti,

1354
00:50:48,800 --> 00:50:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] kako smo se upoznali sa našim prijateljima Marino,

1355
00:50:52,059 --> 00:50:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] i kako je on to pokrenuo,

1356
00:50:53,539 --> 00:50:56,440
[SPEAKER_01] evo, da smo isklopili to prijateljstvo,

1357
00:50:56,440 --> 00:50:58,059
[SPEAKER_01] između naše dvije udruge,

1358
00:50:58,059 --> 00:50:59,659
[SPEAKER_01] mladi su naši,

1359
00:50:59,659 --> 00:51:00,460
[SPEAKER_01] ja znam reće,

1360
00:51:00,460 --> 00:51:02,079
[SPEAKER_01] to mogu i potvrditi,

1361
00:51:02,079 --> 00:51:04,199
[SPEAKER_01] sada i sto puta ću potvrditi,

1362
00:51:04,199 --> 00:51:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] mladi za domovinu,

1363
00:51:05,920 --> 00:51:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] vi ste jedan rasadnik,

1364
00:51:07,460 --> 00:51:09,679
[SPEAKER_01] iz kojega trebamo zaljevati,

1365
00:51:09,679 --> 00:51:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] njegovati, gajiti,

1366
00:51:10,940 --> 00:51:12,679
[SPEAKER_01] i mladice iz tog rasadnika,

1367
00:51:12,679 --> 00:51:13,400
[SPEAKER_01] danas, sutra,

1368
00:51:13,400 --> 00:51:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] što Vinko danas rekao,

1369
00:51:14,579 --> 00:51:17,460
[SPEAKER_01] ovi gore koji imaju kameno srce,

1370
00:51:17,840 --> 00:51:19,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji odlučuju sudbine ti siromaha,

1371
00:51:19,800 --> 00:51:21,340
[SPEAKER_01] da danas, sutra,

1372
00:51:21,340 --> 00:51:23,760
[SPEAKER_01] vi budnete predstavnici naše sirotinje,

1373
00:51:23,760 --> 00:51:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] naših hrvatskog naroda,

1374
00:51:25,059 --> 00:51:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] u sabor, u vladi,

1375
00:51:26,300 --> 00:51:28,659
[SPEAKER_01] u glavnom stožaru i bilo gdje drugo,

1376
00:51:28,659 --> 00:51:30,179
[SPEAKER_01] znači, evo, mi ćemo se truditi,

1377
00:51:30,179 --> 00:51:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] koji smo branili domovno na prvoj crti,

1378
00:51:33,360 --> 00:51:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] da vam prinesem ono što je iz rata,

1379
00:51:35,539 --> 00:51:38,219
[SPEAKER_01] što je, po krvi se puno puta gazi,

1380
00:51:38,219 --> 00:51:39,219
[SPEAKER_01] zato nama često,

1381
00:51:39,219 --> 00:51:40,219
[SPEAKER_01] ja znam ovako,

1382
00:51:40,219 --> 00:51:41,780
[SPEAKER_01] kad svjedočim krenuti mi suze,

1383
00:51:41,780 --> 00:51:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] tome nije sram,

1384
00:51:42,739 --> 00:51:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] jer se gazi po krvi našim mučenika,

1385
00:51:45,079 --> 00:51:46,079
[SPEAKER_01] se krvi prosula,

1386
00:51:46,260 --> 00:51:47,239
[SPEAKER_01] ali se po njoj gazi.

1387
00:51:47,239 --> 00:51:49,280
[SPEAKER_01] Mene srce boli kad vidim mladi,

1388
00:51:49,280 --> 00:51:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] ovi dana je to bilo u medijima,

1389
00:51:50,960 --> 00:51:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] krle na ove razne pjevajke

1390
00:51:53,780 --> 00:51:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] što dodaze u Zagreb,

1391
00:51:54,940 --> 00:51:57,300
[SPEAKER_01] po tom glazbom je krv prospana,

1392
00:51:57,300 --> 00:51:59,219
[SPEAKER_01] po tom glazbom su klali,

1393
00:51:59,219 --> 00:52:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] ubijali po Vukvaru, po Banovni,

1394
00:52:01,099 --> 00:52:02,519
[SPEAKER_01] po svim krajima Hrvatske.

1395
00:52:02,519 --> 00:52:03,619
[SPEAKER_01] I ta mladež, znači,

1396
00:52:03,619 --> 00:52:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] iz kuće je sve polazi iz obitelji.

1397
00:52:05,920 --> 00:52:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ako su u kući sluša takva glazba,

1398
00:52:08,559 --> 00:52:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ta djeca primaju svoje roditelja,

1399
00:52:11,780 --> 00:52:12,860
[SPEAKER_01] to je tuga i žalje,

1400
00:52:12,860 --> 00:52:13,780
[SPEAKER_01] srce me boli.

1401
00:52:13,780 --> 00:52:15,559
[SPEAKER_01] To je borba sad na drugi način,

1402
00:52:15,559 --> 00:52:16,760
[SPEAKER_01] žalosno, ali evo...

1403
00:52:16,760 --> 00:52:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] A od druga sve polazi,

1404
00:52:18,260 --> 00:52:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] zato ti sa svojim sinom

1405
00:52:19,860 --> 00:52:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] si svake prve subote na Krunici.

1406
00:52:22,420 --> 00:52:23,739
[SPEAKER_01] Te, u Bogu hvala,

1407
00:52:23,739 --> 00:52:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja to zovem prva crta duhovnog boja

1408
00:52:26,099 --> 00:52:27,860
[SPEAKER_01] sa Krunicom ruce,

1409
00:52:27,860 --> 00:52:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] evo, nažalost,

1410
00:52:28,619 --> 00:52:29,900
[SPEAKER_01] imamo velike probleme,

1411
00:52:29,900 --> 00:52:30,860
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne predajemo se.

1412
00:52:30,860 --> 00:52:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam reći da smo mi

1413
00:52:32,480 --> 00:52:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] 1991. razmišljali,

1414
00:52:33,699 --> 00:52:34,860
[SPEAKER_01] oćemo li u rovi ići,

1415
00:52:34,860 --> 00:52:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] nećemo, oćemo ići brandom ovno,

1416
00:52:36,340 --> 00:52:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] mi je ne, mi nikad imali.

1417
00:52:37,980 --> 00:52:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] A dotaknut ćemo svi te teme.

1418
00:52:39,920 --> 00:52:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, da nije bilo našeg

1419
00:52:41,619 --> 00:52:43,840
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatskih seljenika po svijetu,

1420
00:52:44,159 --> 00:52:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] koji su slali materialnoj novci

1421
00:52:45,880 --> 00:52:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] i oblačili nas,

1422
00:52:46,780 --> 00:52:48,219
[SPEAKER_01] gdje smo išli goloruki

1423
00:52:48,219 --> 00:52:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] u tenisicama,

1424
00:52:49,539 --> 00:52:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] na prvu crtu u trapericama,

1425
00:52:50,920 --> 00:52:53,079
[SPEAKER_01] oni su nas oblačili i hranili,

1426
00:52:53,079 --> 00:52:54,119
[SPEAKER_01] mi u rovu,

1427
00:52:54,119 --> 00:52:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] mi nikad ne bi domovine imali.

1428
00:52:56,119 --> 00:52:57,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ta suradnja,

1429
00:52:57,400 --> 00:52:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] ta se negrije,

1430
00:52:58,099 --> 00:52:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] to je čudo jedno.

1431
00:52:59,199 --> 00:53:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost, malo pomalo je se to razvilo,

1432
00:53:01,300 --> 00:53:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] to je politika,

1433
00:53:02,039 --> 00:53:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] ima svoje prste u tome,

1434
00:53:03,639 --> 00:53:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] mi, devu, ponovo se trudimo,

1435
00:53:05,079 --> 00:53:06,519
[SPEAKER_01] evo, ispričat ćemo nešto

1436
00:53:06,519 --> 00:53:08,360
[SPEAKER_01] o tom suradnju sa našim seljenicima,

1437
00:53:08,360 --> 00:53:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] sa jednom predivnom

1438
00:53:09,420 --> 00:53:11,400
[SPEAKER_01] muškom molitvenom zajednicom,

1439
00:53:12,119 --> 00:53:14,480
[SPEAKER_01] zovu se Vitezovi predagocijene krvi

1440
00:53:14,480 --> 00:53:16,739
[SPEAKER_01] iz daleke naše Australije i Sidneja

1441
00:53:16,739 --> 00:53:17,420
[SPEAKER_01] i ovim putem,

1442
00:53:17,420 --> 00:53:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] evo, pozdravljam,

1443
00:53:18,039 --> 00:53:19,440
[SPEAKER_01] drage prijatelje,

1444
00:53:19,440 --> 00:53:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] što dalje je domovnije,

1445
00:53:20,980 --> 00:53:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] to jače je srce kuca za domovnu.

1446
00:53:22,739 --> 00:53:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to mogu posvjedoštiti,

1447
00:53:23,980 --> 00:53:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] od suradnje dosta sa našim seljenicima

1448
00:53:26,099 --> 00:53:27,300
[SPEAKER_01] i u Evropi,

1449
00:53:27,300 --> 00:53:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] tako i dalje.

1450
00:53:28,260 --> 00:53:29,780
[SPEAKER_00] Puno pomažu i kapi,

1451
00:53:29,780 --> 00:53:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] puno je donacija isto došlo.

1452
00:53:31,519 --> 00:53:34,539
[SPEAKER_01] Puno humanitarni akcija,

1453
00:53:34,539 --> 00:53:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] to je,

1454
00:53:34,800 --> 00:53:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] evo, kao budne,

1455
00:53:35,260 --> 00:53:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] ako se budemo dotakli od toga.

1456
00:53:36,659 --> 00:53:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo,

1457
00:53:37,019 --> 00:53:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] evo, možemo sad malo o tome,

1458
00:53:38,539 --> 00:53:40,340
[SPEAKER_00] čak i Zlatko Dalic udjelovo,

1459
00:53:40,340 --> 00:53:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako,

1460
00:53:40,880 --> 00:53:41,739
[SPEAKER_01] možete i njegovat pohvaliti.

1461
00:53:41,739 --> 00:53:42,900
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, Boga blagosovio,

1462
00:53:42,900 --> 00:53:44,699
[SPEAKER_01] da je već nekoliko godina za red,

1463
00:53:44,699 --> 00:53:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] on poklonio reprezentacije,

1464
00:53:47,940 --> 00:53:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] poklonio adres s potpisima Sviju

1465
00:53:50,579 --> 00:53:52,179
[SPEAKER_01] i zato se dobije dosta novaca

1466
00:53:52,179 --> 00:53:54,099
[SPEAKER_01] na tim humanitarnoj večer u Sidneju.

1467
00:53:54,099 --> 00:53:57,280
[SPEAKER_01] Skoro 15 godina suradnja traje,

1468
00:53:57,280 --> 00:54:00,199
[SPEAKER_01] evo, kako simbolično smo upoznali te ljude.

1469
00:54:00,199 --> 00:54:02,260
[SPEAKER_01] Moja Malenko je s nas,

1470
00:54:02,260 --> 00:54:03,420
[SPEAKER_01] jedna ekipa branditelja,

1471
00:54:03,420 --> 00:54:04,780
[SPEAKER_01] nekoliko godina za red,

1472
00:54:04,780 --> 00:54:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] smo pišačili Zagreba,

1473
00:54:06,219 --> 00:54:07,599
[SPEAKER_01] križnim putem,

1474
00:54:07,599 --> 00:54:08,760
[SPEAKER_01] znači do Blajburga.

1475
00:54:08,760 --> 00:54:11,099
[SPEAKER_01] I dva Hrvata su saznala za to

1476
00:54:11,099 --> 00:54:12,159
[SPEAKER_01] preko interneta,

1477
00:54:12,159 --> 00:54:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] prijatelj Ante,

1478
00:54:13,579 --> 00:54:14,880
[SPEAKER_01] moj vrli kum,

1479
00:54:14,880 --> 00:54:16,280
[SPEAKER_01] kojom sam posle bio kum,

1480
00:54:16,280 --> 00:54:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] i Josip Reljanović,

1481
00:54:17,800 --> 00:54:18,639
[SPEAKER_01] oni su to vidjeli,

1482
00:54:18,639 --> 00:54:20,320
[SPEAKER_01] došli su da oni pješače s nama

1483
00:54:20,320 --> 00:54:20,920
[SPEAKER_01] pet dana,

1484
00:54:20,920 --> 00:54:21,880
[SPEAKER_01] tim putem,

1485
00:54:21,880 --> 00:54:23,840
[SPEAKER_01] ako da su naši braće i sestre

1486
00:54:23,840 --> 00:54:25,219
[SPEAKER_01] u Kristu i Hrvatskom rodu

1487
00:54:25,219 --> 00:54:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] krvarla i pješačila

1488
00:54:26,820 --> 00:54:27,880
[SPEAKER_01] da spase glavu.

1489
00:54:27,880 --> 00:54:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] I tako smo se upoznali

1490
00:54:29,960 --> 00:54:30,840
[SPEAKER_01] iz prijatelji,

1491
00:54:30,840 --> 00:54:32,579
[SPEAKER_01] znači njegov bratić Zoran,

1492
00:54:32,579 --> 00:54:34,880
[SPEAKER_01] on vodi toj molitvenu zajednicu

1493
00:54:34,880 --> 00:54:36,820
[SPEAKER_01] i ja sam ispričao,

1494
00:54:36,820 --> 00:54:38,559
[SPEAKER_01] čim se bavim da sam volonter

1495
00:54:38,559 --> 00:54:39,199
[SPEAKER_01] i tako,

1496
00:54:39,559 --> 00:54:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] i oni su rekli,

1497
00:54:40,239 --> 00:54:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] kreće ovo mi u akciju

1498
00:54:41,539 --> 00:54:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] humanitarnu

1499
00:54:42,539 --> 00:54:43,739
[SPEAKER_01] i oni su nama te godine,

1500
00:54:43,739 --> 00:54:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] prve godine,

1501
00:54:44,679 --> 00:54:46,199
[SPEAKER_01] skupili novice na toj

1502
00:54:46,199 --> 00:54:47,199
[SPEAKER_01] humanitarnoj večeri,

1503
00:54:47,199 --> 00:54:49,099
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo od toga kupili drva

1504
00:54:49,099 --> 00:54:50,199
[SPEAKER_01] i dobar dio godine

1505
00:54:50,199 --> 00:54:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] nahranili našu sirotinju

1506
00:54:51,800 --> 00:54:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] i tako,

1507
00:54:52,619 --> 00:54:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] oni htili da svake godine

1508
00:54:54,000 --> 00:54:55,380
[SPEAKER_01] ide za kap dobrote,

1509
00:54:55,380 --> 00:54:56,219
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam predložio,

1510
00:54:56,219 --> 00:54:57,139
[SPEAKER_01] ima i drugi u potrebi,

1511
00:54:57,139 --> 00:54:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] ne smemo biti bahati,

1512
00:54:58,260 --> 00:55:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] ima i drugi koji su u potrebi,

1513
00:55:00,480 --> 00:55:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] tako smo odlučili,

1514
00:55:01,400 --> 00:55:02,940
[SPEAKER_01] jedne godine ide za potrebite

1515
00:55:02,940 --> 00:55:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] u našoj Bosni i Hercegovini

1516
00:55:04,960 --> 00:55:06,260
[SPEAKER_01] i tako isto u Hrvatskoj.

1517
00:55:06,260 --> 00:55:08,340
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ove godine su skupili,

1518
00:55:08,340 --> 00:55:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] to sam im predložio,

1519
00:55:09,420 --> 00:55:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] jedan plemenita akcija

1520
00:55:11,340 --> 00:55:12,699
[SPEAKER_01] naše drage časne sestre,

1521
00:55:12,699 --> 00:55:14,019
[SPEAKER_01] Kržarice sa Vrhovca,

1522
00:55:14,019 --> 00:55:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] grade prihvatilište za bolesnike,

1523
00:55:16,420 --> 00:55:18,340
[SPEAKER_01] dugo nisam nešto čuo

1524
00:55:18,340 --> 00:55:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] o ovaj plemenitije,

1525
00:55:19,699 --> 00:55:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] jednu plemenitu akciju,

1526
00:55:20,960 --> 00:55:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] grade prihvatilište za ljudi

1527
00:55:22,480 --> 00:55:24,280
[SPEAKER_01] koji dolaze svi krajeva Hrvatske

1528
00:55:24,280 --> 00:55:25,179
[SPEAKER_01] i Bosni i Hercegovine

1529
00:55:25,179 --> 00:55:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] na lječenje u Zagreb,

1530
00:55:26,179 --> 00:55:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] nemaju gdje prinošiti,

1531
00:55:27,659 --> 00:55:28,980
[SPEAKER_01] da li je to bolesna djeca

1532
00:55:28,980 --> 00:55:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] ili bilo ko,

1533
00:55:30,079 --> 00:55:31,739
[SPEAKER_01] znači negdje će biti smještaj,

1534
00:55:31,739 --> 00:55:35,559
[SPEAKER_01] negdje 20, 8, do 30 soba

1535
00:55:35,559 --> 00:55:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] gdje će ti ljudi moći

1536
00:55:37,059 --> 00:55:38,760
[SPEAKER_01] uljudno, besplatno biti smješteni

1537
00:55:38,760 --> 00:55:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] na prodoljeno lječenje.

1538
00:55:39,980 --> 00:55:42,300
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su evo imali kumantarnu večeru,

1539
00:55:42,300 --> 00:55:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] prodavane su,

1540
00:55:43,380 --> 00:55:44,500
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1541
00:55:44,500 --> 00:55:46,340
[SPEAKER_01] dresovi su prodani na ukciji,

1542
00:55:46,340 --> 00:55:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] tako smo poslali slike

1543
00:55:47,800 --> 00:55:48,820
[SPEAKER_01] od naših umjetnika,

1544
00:55:48,820 --> 00:55:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] iskupilo se dobar dio novaca

1545
00:55:51,000 --> 00:55:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] gdje će se, znači,

1546
00:55:51,920 --> 00:55:54,019
[SPEAKER_01] pomoći da se izgradi to prihvatilište

1547
00:55:54,019 --> 00:55:55,380
[SPEAKER_01] za bolesnike,

1548
00:55:55,380 --> 00:55:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] prihvatilište se simbolično zove križ.

1549
00:55:58,519 --> 00:56:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] Budnimo jedni drugim,

1550
00:56:00,559 --> 00:56:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] Šimun Sirenac,

1551
00:56:01,579 --> 00:56:03,780
[SPEAKER_01] pomosimo nositi životne križeve,

1552
00:56:03,780 --> 00:56:06,300
[SPEAKER_01] to je blagoslovo i to je ljubljenje domovine.

1553
00:56:06,300 --> 00:56:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je,

1554
00:56:07,239 --> 00:56:08,780
[SPEAKER_00] a vezano to za donacije,

1555
00:56:08,780 --> 00:56:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] dobro si rekao,

1556
00:56:09,579 --> 00:56:11,300
[SPEAKER_00] što dalje ljudi od domovine,

1557
00:56:11,300 --> 00:56:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] to srce kuca jače,

1558
00:56:12,880 --> 00:56:15,820
[SPEAKER_00] volio bi da i mi možemo od njih malo,

1559
00:56:15,820 --> 00:56:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] češće upitite njihove razine

1560
00:56:18,179 --> 00:56:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] zagrijanosti za domovinu,

1561
00:56:20,159 --> 00:56:22,280
[SPEAKER_00] a i ono vezano za Zlatka Dalća,

1562
00:56:22,280 --> 00:56:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] isto volim spomenuti,

1563
00:56:23,460 --> 00:56:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] tko ode u njegov restoran,

1564
00:56:25,820 --> 00:56:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo blizu izložene medalje srebrne iz Rusije,

1565
00:56:29,400 --> 00:56:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] može vidjeti i ovu medalju od kapi dobrote,

1566
00:56:32,320 --> 00:56:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] što stvarno isto pokazuje koliko mu znači

1567
00:56:35,440 --> 00:56:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] i koliko su to velike stvari,

1568
00:56:38,059 --> 00:56:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] a ti si se, Marinko, potrudio

1569
00:56:40,019 --> 00:56:44,780
[SPEAKER_00] i da dobiju svi koji pomažu jedan vrijednu uspomenu.

1570
00:56:44,780 --> 00:56:46,260
[SPEAKER_01] Je, to je jedna simbolika,

1571
00:56:46,260 --> 00:56:47,199
[SPEAKER_01] on je dobio,

1572
00:56:47,199 --> 00:56:50,599
[SPEAKER_01] prošle godine smo mu to poklonili,

1573
00:56:50,599 --> 00:56:52,219
[SPEAKER_01] on je stavio tamo na oltar,

1574
00:56:52,219 --> 00:56:54,260
[SPEAKER_01] i on zove gdje otkud on svaki dan polazi,

1575
00:56:54,260 --> 00:56:56,400
[SPEAKER_01] to mu je prva crta,

1576
00:56:56,400 --> 00:56:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] on govori s koje kreće na posao,

1577
00:56:59,900 --> 00:57:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] tako isto, evo jedna simbolika,

1578
00:57:01,960 --> 00:57:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] mi je zovemo medalja dobrote,

1579
00:57:03,659 --> 00:57:06,599
[SPEAKER_01] koju dodjeljamo svake godine za Božić,

1580
00:57:06,599 --> 00:57:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] evo, vi ste ove godine bili ti mladi,

1581
00:57:08,900 --> 00:57:12,039
[SPEAKER_01] gdje me potaklo da dobijete toju medalju dobrote,

1582
00:57:12,039 --> 00:57:15,460
[SPEAKER_01] koju treba zaslužiti kao bivši sportaš,

1583
00:57:15,460 --> 00:57:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] teško je dobiti,

1584
00:57:17,079 --> 00:57:18,320
[SPEAKER_01] ali kada je čovjek dobije,

1585
00:57:18,320 --> 00:57:19,559
[SPEAKER_01] to mu daje jedan poticaj,

1586
00:57:19,559 --> 00:57:21,280
[SPEAKER_01] pa zato vi toju medalju,

1587
00:57:21,280 --> 00:57:22,320
[SPEAKER_01] jedan dje ste odradili,

1588
00:57:22,320 --> 00:57:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] a jedan dobar dje morate odraditi toju medalju.

1589
00:57:24,860 --> 00:57:26,360
[SPEAKER_01] Tek smo počeli, tek smo počeli,

1590
00:57:26,360 --> 00:57:29,760
[SPEAKER_01] ali zlatna je, tako da biće motivacija.

1591
00:57:29,900 --> 00:57:30,920
[SPEAKER_00] Rako Bog, da je,

1592
00:57:30,920 --> 00:57:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] Vinko, imaš li ti išta na dodat vezano

1593
00:57:33,500 --> 00:57:36,780
[SPEAKER_00] za donacije i ljude koji pomažu,

1594
00:57:36,780 --> 00:57:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] sigurno ima puno dobri ljudi

1595
00:57:38,420 --> 00:57:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] s kojima ste se sreli?

1596
00:57:39,639 --> 00:57:44,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ima, ali zamislite, evo, ima,

1597
00:57:44,460 --> 00:57:45,219
[SPEAKER_02] hvala Bogu,

1598
00:57:45,219 --> 00:57:47,340
[SPEAKER_02] i rekao sam i na početku,

1599
00:57:47,340 --> 00:57:49,480
[SPEAKER_02] preko naših podupiratelja

1600
00:57:49,480 --> 00:57:52,440
[SPEAKER_02] i naših snaga,

1601
00:57:52,440 --> 00:57:54,199
[SPEAKER_02] jer ne možemo sve sami,

1602
00:57:54,199 --> 00:57:55,239
[SPEAKER_02] puno toga napravimo,

1603
00:57:55,239 --> 00:57:56,260
[SPEAKER_02] tih dobrih ljudi.

1604
00:57:56,260 --> 00:57:58,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, evo recimo,

1605
00:57:58,579 --> 00:58:01,199
[SPEAKER_02] ja to tako postavljam i razmišljam

1606
00:58:01,199 --> 00:58:02,460
[SPEAKER_02] u ovom trenutku,

1607
00:58:02,460 --> 00:58:07,380
[SPEAKER_02] nas je 70-80 dragovoljaca

1608
00:58:07,380 --> 00:58:08,340
[SPEAKER_02] ili ti volontera.

1609
00:58:08,340 --> 00:58:11,659
[SPEAKER_02] Šta mislite da je nas 700 tisuća Hrvata

1610
00:58:11,659 --> 00:58:13,360
[SPEAKER_02] ovako organiziranih u domovini?

1611
00:58:14,079 --> 00:58:17,699
[SPEAKER_02] A ovo je dokaz, Marinko i možda godinu dvije prije mene,

1612
00:58:17,699 --> 00:58:18,900
[SPEAKER_02] tu smo koliko?

1613
00:58:18,900 --> 00:58:21,619
[SPEAKER_02] Imamo ljudi koji su preko 20 godina,

1614
00:58:21,619 --> 00:58:22,739
[SPEAKER_02] znači da je moguće.

1615
00:58:25,739 --> 00:58:28,360
[SPEAKER_02] Dobrih ljudi ima.

1616
00:58:28,360 --> 00:58:36,699
[SPEAKER_02] Bog, kad je izabrao narod preko kojega će se objaviti svim narodima,

1617
00:58:36,699 --> 00:58:37,699
[SPEAKER_02] izraelski narod,

1618
00:58:37,699 --> 00:58:40,619
[SPEAKER_02] on nije napravio skupinu tako,

1619
00:58:40,619 --> 00:58:43,619
[SPEAKER_02] nego ga je organizirao u državu,

1620
00:58:43,619 --> 00:58:45,519
[SPEAKER_02] u zakone,

1621
00:58:45,519 --> 00:58:47,619
[SPEAKER_02] u jednu organizaciju.

1622
00:58:48,159 --> 00:58:51,920
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, svi dobri ljudi neka potraže,

1623
00:58:51,920 --> 00:58:55,420
[SPEAKER_02] ovo ne govorimo nego u dobroj i bratskoj namjeri,

1624
00:58:55,420 --> 00:58:58,800
[SPEAKER_02] neka potraže neku našu organizaciju,

1625
00:58:58,800 --> 00:59:02,039
[SPEAKER_02] da pomažemo jedni druge što nas bude više,

1626
00:59:02,039 --> 00:59:05,099
[SPEAKER_02] više ćemo učiniti jedni drugima.

1627
00:59:05,099 --> 00:59:08,900
[SPEAKER_02] Jer smo to i dužni i prema Bogu,

1628
00:59:08,900 --> 00:59:11,320
[SPEAKER_02] i prema ljudima koji su nama pomagali.

1629
00:59:11,320 --> 00:59:14,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja znam često reći da ljudi,

1630
00:59:14,559 --> 00:59:17,260
[SPEAKER_02] ne samo ljudi, nego i oni, njihova djeca i djeca,

1631
00:59:17,340 --> 00:59:18,159
[SPEAKER_02] njihove djece,

1632
00:59:18,159 --> 00:59:19,679
[SPEAKER_02] nekad i svi mi,

1633
00:59:19,679 --> 00:59:21,599
[SPEAKER_02] nekad neke ljude,

1634
00:59:21,599 --> 00:59:24,119
[SPEAKER_02] eto, hvala Bogu, sretemo i halono,

1635
00:59:24,119 --> 00:59:25,099
[SPEAKER_02] ne imamo neki odnos,

1636
00:59:25,099 --> 00:59:26,579
[SPEAKER_02] imamo neka loša iskustva,

1637
00:59:26,579 --> 00:59:28,280
[SPEAKER_02] ne mrzimo i to.

1638
00:59:28,280 --> 00:59:30,980
[SPEAKER_02] Ali postoje ljudi koji nikad nećemo zaboraviti.

1639
00:59:30,980 --> 00:59:32,679
[SPEAKER_02] To je one koji su nam pomogli

1640
00:59:32,679 --> 00:59:34,260
[SPEAKER_02] kad nam je bilo najtežno.

1641
00:59:34,260 --> 00:59:37,340
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, pozivamo i u ovoj prilici.

1642
00:59:37,340 --> 00:59:40,219
[SPEAKER_02] Lijepo je dati donaciju,

1643
00:59:40,219 --> 00:59:43,840
[SPEAKER_02] to je potrebno i valja našoj sirotinji,

1644
00:59:43,840 --> 00:59:45,219
[SPEAKER_02] bez toga se ne bi moglo.

1645
00:59:45,659 --> 00:59:47,559
[SPEAKER_02] ali to nemoćniku,

1646
00:59:47,559 --> 00:59:50,599
[SPEAKER_02] bratu Hrvatu i sestri Hrvatici

1647
00:59:50,599 --> 00:59:53,380
[SPEAKER_02] ili sestri i bratu iz drugog naroda,

1648
00:59:53,380 --> 00:59:56,119
[SPEAKER_02] koji su naša braća i žive u Hrvatskoj,

1649
00:59:56,119 --> 00:59:57,599
[SPEAKER_02] treba otići tamo.

1650
00:59:57,599 --> 00:59:59,539
[SPEAKER_02] Treba s njime popriča,

1651
00:59:59,539 --> 01:00:00,780
[SPEAKER_02] treba odesu doktora,

1652
01:00:00,780 --> 01:00:02,659
[SPEAKER_02] treba mu ta drva donijeti,

1653
01:00:02,659 --> 01:00:03,900
[SPEAKER_02] treba mu na loži drva.

1654
01:00:04,380 --> 01:00:07,320
[SPEAKER_02] a to organizacija poput ovakvih organizirano,

1655
01:00:07,320 --> 01:00:10,219
[SPEAKER_02] jedino može organizirano raditi.

1656
01:00:10,219 --> 01:00:12,840
[SPEAKER_02] Zato sve pozivamo i stare i mlade,

1657
01:00:12,840 --> 01:00:16,320
[SPEAKER_02] i u kap dobrote i bilo koju našu organizaciju,

1658
01:00:16,320 --> 01:00:17,719
[SPEAKER_02] ponavljam, naglašavam,

1659
01:00:17,719 --> 01:00:24,019
[SPEAKER_02] organizaciju u kojoj će moći organizirano dijeliti

1660
01:00:24,019 --> 01:00:27,119
[SPEAKER_02] tu lijepotu, ljubavi jednih prema drugima.

1661
01:00:28,119 --> 01:00:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] ostavit ćemo kontakte u opisu ovog podcasta,

1662
01:00:31,840 --> 01:00:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] možeš da se jave ljudi,

1663
01:00:33,440 --> 01:00:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo, recimo.

1664
01:00:35,179 --> 01:00:39,059
[SPEAKER_01] Jel ti nešto kao branitelji naše svete domovine,

1665
01:00:39,059 --> 01:00:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek ružno nama braniteljima u mediji,

1666
01:00:41,619 --> 01:00:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] znam i pisati puno puta,

1667
01:00:42,980 --> 01:00:44,099
[SPEAKER_01] nema veze ni uopće,

1668
01:00:44,099 --> 01:00:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] ni branitelj napravi ovo ono,

1669
01:00:45,579 --> 01:00:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] nikad nešto pozitivno,

1670
01:00:47,000 --> 01:00:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek neke ružne stvari na naslovinicama,

1671
01:00:49,579 --> 01:00:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] novina i tako dalje.

1672
01:00:50,760 --> 01:00:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja mogu reći nači,

1673
01:00:52,579 --> 01:00:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] u ovi 18 godina hrvatski branitelj,

1674
01:00:54,960 --> 01:00:56,239
[SPEAKER_01] dragovoljci domovske rata,

1675
01:00:56,239 --> 01:00:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] umiroljeni časnici,

1676
01:00:58,039 --> 01:01:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] studenti, radnici,

1677
01:01:00,079 --> 01:01:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] svi su bili na cijepanju drva

1678
01:01:02,539 --> 01:01:03,519
[SPEAKER_01] u našem sladište,

1679
01:01:03,519 --> 01:01:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] mar ne bio si tamo,

1680
01:01:05,000 --> 01:01:05,460
[SPEAKER_01] vidio si,

1681
01:01:05,460 --> 01:01:07,820
[SPEAKER_01] znači toliko dobra popravljanja krova,

1682
01:01:07,820 --> 01:01:09,659
[SPEAKER_01] ali ta drva, ta toplina,

1683
01:01:09,659 --> 01:01:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] kad dođe u kuću tog siromaha

1684
01:01:12,380 --> 01:01:13,820
[SPEAKER_01] i kad ga nahraniš,

1685
01:01:13,820 --> 01:01:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] to je takav radost,

1686
01:01:15,300 --> 01:01:16,199
[SPEAKER_01] takav blagosov,

1687
01:01:16,199 --> 01:01:17,480
[SPEAKER_01] kad vidješ od tog siromaha,

1688
01:01:17,480 --> 01:01:18,139
[SPEAKER_01] isto je njegove,

1689
01:01:18,139 --> 01:01:19,820
[SPEAKER_01] tog podruma vlažnoga,

1690
01:01:19,820 --> 01:01:22,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji zadiše od vlagon,

1691
01:01:22,300 --> 01:01:23,880
[SPEAKER_01] toliko blagosova,

1692
01:01:23,880 --> 01:01:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] čine velike stvari.

1693
01:01:25,500 --> 01:01:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi smo u ovi 18 godina,

1694
01:01:27,960 --> 01:01:29,780
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi svake godine se cijepa

1695
01:01:29,780 --> 01:01:31,719
[SPEAKER_01] negdje 200-250 metara drva,

1696
01:01:31,719 --> 01:01:33,940
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi ovako poredao metar visoko,

1697
01:01:33,940 --> 01:01:36,880
[SPEAKER_01] jedno, skoro 4-5 kilometara dužine drva,

1698
01:01:36,880 --> 01:01:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] što su hrvatski branitelji skupa,

1699
01:01:38,920 --> 01:01:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] najvećim dijelom sa studentima.

1700
01:01:40,820 --> 01:01:42,019
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se tamo i družimo,

1701
01:01:42,019 --> 01:01:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] nije bit samo napraviti dobro dijelo,

1702
01:01:43,880 --> 01:01:44,619
[SPEAKER_01] cijepati drva.

1703
01:01:44,619 --> 01:01:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se upoznajemo tamo,

1704
01:01:46,460 --> 01:01:49,340
[SPEAKER_01] ovi veterani pričaju svoje događaje zrata,

1705
01:01:49,340 --> 01:01:51,159
[SPEAKER_01] uključujemo malo akadete,

1706
01:01:51,159 --> 01:01:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] isto tako mlade,

1707
01:01:52,800 --> 01:01:54,019
[SPEAKER_01] naše drage studente,

1708
01:01:54,019 --> 01:01:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] sa studija,

1709
01:01:58,739 --> 01:02:00,820
[SPEAKER_01] sa črnomerca,

1710
01:02:00,820 --> 01:02:02,159
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se oni uključuju,

1711
01:02:02,159 --> 01:02:03,860
[SPEAKER_01] onda mi razmijenjamo iskustvo naše,

1712
01:02:03,860 --> 01:02:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] oni sada kao budući časnici

1713
01:02:05,960 --> 01:02:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatske vojske

1714
01:02:06,960 --> 01:02:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] i pričamo i neke događaje.

1715
01:02:08,900 --> 01:02:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] Tako oplemeniti stvari se tamo događa,

1716
01:02:11,380 --> 01:02:13,199
[SPEAKER_01] to je neopisivo.

1717
01:02:13,199 --> 01:02:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to nigdje u mediji,

1718
01:02:14,719 --> 01:02:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] niti mi želimo to da se o tom zna,

1719
01:02:17,000 --> 01:02:17,599
[SPEAKER_01] da se priča,

1720
01:02:17,599 --> 01:02:18,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali samo spominjem,

1721
01:02:18,519 --> 01:02:20,139
[SPEAKER_01] toliko oplemeniti stvari

1722
01:02:20,139 --> 01:02:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatski branitelj rade,

1723
01:02:21,539 --> 01:02:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] to se ne može opisati.

1724
01:02:22,940 --> 01:02:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ako dođe u mediji,

1725
01:02:23,980 --> 01:02:25,139
[SPEAKER_00] bude samo, evo ga,

1726
01:02:25,139 --> 01:02:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] lažna mirovina,

1727
01:02:26,380 --> 01:02:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] ili neko nasilje,

1728
01:02:27,679 --> 01:02:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] ili neka druga,

1729
01:02:28,679 --> 01:02:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] neka druga loša stvar.

1730
01:02:30,659 --> 01:02:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] Radi pet crni ovaca se pljuje po svima,

1731
01:02:33,260 --> 01:02:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] toliko oplemeniti stvari rade,

1732
01:02:34,920 --> 01:02:36,539
[SPEAKER_01] to je naša duznaju,

1733
01:02:36,539 --> 01:02:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] da ljubimo do ono.

1734
01:02:37,360 --> 01:02:38,139
[SPEAKER_01] Na drugi način,

1735
01:02:38,139 --> 01:02:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] sad smo na prvoj crti bojišnjica.

1736
01:02:39,760 --> 01:02:41,539
[SPEAKER_02] Mogu li ja nešto,

1737
01:02:41,539 --> 01:02:43,460
[SPEAKER_02] ako bi moglo se nadovezati,

1738
01:02:43,460 --> 01:02:46,500
[SPEAKER_02] ja neka glasila,

1739
01:02:46,500 --> 01:02:49,440
[SPEAKER_02] ili kako to se tuđim jezikom kaže mediji,

1740
01:02:49,440 --> 01:02:51,300
[SPEAKER_02] ovoga ja više volim,

1741
01:02:51,300 --> 01:02:52,760
[SPEAKER_02] ponavljam to namjerno,

1742
01:02:52,760 --> 01:02:53,860
[SPEAKER_02] materijski jezik,

1743
01:02:53,860 --> 01:02:54,639
[SPEAKER_02] što je prirodno,

1744
01:02:54,639 --> 01:02:56,059
[SPEAKER_02] francus voli francuski,

1745
01:02:56,059 --> 01:02:57,159
[SPEAKER_02] hrvat hrvatski,

1746
01:02:57,159 --> 01:02:59,920
[SPEAKER_02] pa više volim upoznavati svoj jezik,

1747
01:02:59,920 --> 01:03:02,119
[SPEAKER_02] koji me mati moja naučila.

1748
01:03:03,260 --> 01:03:07,440
[SPEAKER_02] Ja neke koji pišu u Hrvatskoj,

1749
01:03:07,440 --> 01:03:09,280
[SPEAKER_02] nazivam režimska,

1750
01:03:09,280 --> 01:03:11,400
[SPEAKER_02] ne da nazivam,

1751
01:03:11,400 --> 01:03:14,320
[SPEAKER_02] nego to su režimska piskarala,

1752
01:03:14,320 --> 01:03:18,980
[SPEAKER_02] koji sebe nazivaju novinarima i književnicima.

1753
01:03:19,380 --> 01:03:20,239
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto to govorim?

1754
01:03:20,239 --> 01:03:25,719
[SPEAKER_02] Zato što je novinar dužan po svojoj prirodi zanimanja širiti istinu.

1755
01:03:25,719 --> 01:03:33,719
[SPEAKER_02] Znači ako piše tendenciozno ili po zapovjedi režima,

1756
01:03:33,719 --> 01:03:35,219
[SPEAKER_02] bilo koje razine,

1757
01:03:35,219 --> 01:03:37,780
[SPEAKER_02] uredništva do najvećih razina,

1758
01:03:37,780 --> 01:03:38,900
[SPEAKER_02] to nije novina,

1759
01:03:38,900 --> 01:03:39,760
[SPEAKER_02] to je režimsko,

1760
01:03:39,760 --> 01:03:41,139
[SPEAKER_02] ja volim reći,

1761
01:03:41,139 --> 01:03:42,599
[SPEAKER_02] volio bi da ne moram.

1762
01:03:42,599 --> 01:03:44,219
[SPEAKER_02] Režimska piskarala,

1763
01:03:44,219 --> 01:03:45,000
[SPEAKER_02] bilo novinari,

1764
01:03:45,000 --> 01:03:46,079
[SPEAKER_02] bilo književnici,

1765
01:03:46,079 --> 01:03:48,599
[SPEAKER_02] koji lupaju po hrvatskim braniteljima,

1766
01:03:48,599 --> 01:03:51,179
[SPEAKER_02] a pošto mi poznamo hrvatske branitele,

1767
01:03:51,179 --> 01:03:51,880
[SPEAKER_02] jedan, ja mislim,

1768
01:03:51,880 --> 01:03:55,300
[SPEAKER_02] poznati srbijanski pisac je rekao,

1769
01:03:55,300 --> 01:03:57,639
[SPEAKER_02] ubij me preteška riječ,

1770
01:03:57,719 --> 01:03:58,559
[SPEAKER_02] ovako nekako.

1771
01:03:58,559 --> 01:04:04,539
[SPEAKER_02] I ja znam koliko to košta duhovno malo manje stabilne branitelje

1772
01:04:04,539 --> 01:04:10,460
[SPEAKER_02] kad slušaju ta tendenciozna pisanja o hrvatskim braniteljima.

1773
01:04:10,460 --> 01:04:12,780
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim, ja na takve ne bih gubio vrijeme.

1774
01:04:12,780 --> 01:04:14,219
[SPEAKER_02] Mi znamo,

1775
01:04:14,219 --> 01:04:17,840
[SPEAKER_02] jao bi nama bilo kad bi oni u nama lijepo pisali.

1776
01:04:17,840 --> 01:04:23,420
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim, nešto bih htio reći samo kratko hrvatskim novinarima,

1777
01:04:23,420 --> 01:04:26,800
[SPEAKER_02] za koje znam da žele dobro domovin isto ko i ja,

1778
01:04:27,260 --> 01:04:31,780
[SPEAKER_02] imaju tri velike greške u našim ljudima,

1779
01:04:31,780 --> 01:04:37,039
[SPEAKER_02] hrvatskim novinarima i književnicima i djelatnicima javnim,

1780
01:04:37,039 --> 01:04:40,480
[SPEAKER_02] koje bi ovdje htio upozoriti, na kratko.

1781
01:04:40,480 --> 01:04:42,920
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo, kukanje, stalna kukanje.

1782
01:04:42,920 --> 01:04:44,719
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo mali narod.

1783
01:04:44,719 --> 01:04:46,980
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo mali narod.

1784
01:04:46,980 --> 01:04:51,539
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan od najmanjih naroda na prostoru Izraela,

1785
01:04:51,539 --> 01:04:53,619
[SPEAKER_02] ako ne i najmanjih je bio izraelski narod,

1786
01:04:53,619 --> 01:04:55,760
[SPEAKER_02] njega je Bog izabrao za izabrane narod.

1787
01:04:55,760 --> 01:04:59,139
[SPEAKER_02] Brojni narodi su bili, pobjeđivali su izraelski.

1788
01:04:59,139 --> 01:05:03,320
[SPEAKER_02] Ja nikad nisam židove izraelske čuo da kukaju da su mali narod.

1789
01:05:03,320 --> 01:05:05,260
[SPEAKER_02] A država Izraela je trenutno,

1790
01:05:05,260 --> 01:05:06,539
[SPEAKER_02] paš sam to ugledao,

1791
01:05:06,539 --> 01:05:09,079
[SPEAKER_02] površino manja od Hrvatske.

1792
01:05:09,079 --> 01:05:12,179
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, veličina jednog naroda se ne mjeri

1793
01:05:12,179 --> 01:05:14,980
[SPEAKER_02] kao veličina jednog stada ili brojem grla.

1794
01:05:15,400 --> 01:05:17,280
[SPEAKER_02] Ako mi gledamo našu povijest,

1795
01:05:17,280 --> 01:05:20,500
[SPEAKER_02] našu obranu kršćanstva,

1796
01:05:20,500 --> 01:05:22,159
[SPEAKER_02] da smo dobili naziv,

1797
01:05:22,159 --> 01:05:23,980
[SPEAKER_02] predziđe kršćanstva,

1798
01:05:23,980 --> 01:05:26,739
[SPEAKER_02] da u Zagreb Turci nisu nikad ušli,

1799
01:05:26,739 --> 01:05:28,579
[SPEAKER_02] a došli su pod Beč.

1800
01:05:28,579 --> 01:05:33,280
[SPEAKER_02] Ruska carica Katarina je rekla

1801
01:05:33,280 --> 01:05:35,099
[SPEAKER_02] za vrijeme Francuske revolucije,

1802
01:05:35,099 --> 01:05:39,079
[SPEAKER_02] to je ono vrijeme kad su konjima ulazili u Notre Dame.

1803
01:05:39,260 --> 01:05:41,880
[SPEAKER_02] Znamo šta je počelo od Francuske revolucije, sve.

1804
01:05:41,880 --> 01:05:45,219
[SPEAKER_02] Kazala je, ima dokument,

1805
01:05:45,219 --> 01:05:46,599
[SPEAKER_02] to je lako provjerljivo,

1806
01:05:46,599 --> 01:05:49,260
[SPEAKER_02] kaže, između ostalog, citiram,

1807
01:05:49,260 --> 01:05:50,920
[SPEAKER_02] šest tisuća Hrvata

1808
01:05:50,920 --> 01:05:52,980
[SPEAKER_02] i dvije tisuće Kozaka,

1809
01:05:52,980 --> 01:05:54,360
[SPEAKER_02] dovoljno je da padne Pariz.

1810
01:05:54,360 --> 01:05:59,079
[SPEAKER_02] Napoleon je rekao da mi je sto tisuća Hrvata

1811
01:05:59,079 --> 01:06:00,559
[SPEAKER_02] osvojio bi cijeli svijet.

1812
01:06:00,559 --> 01:06:03,219
[SPEAKER_02] Obranili smo se,

1813
01:06:03,219 --> 01:06:05,500
[SPEAKER_02] prva zemlja koja je padom komunizma

1814
01:06:05,500 --> 01:06:06,420
[SPEAKER_02] bila napadnuta.

1815
01:06:09,260 --> 01:06:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] I sve smo to izdržali.

1816
01:06:10,940 --> 01:06:12,400
[SPEAKER_02] I narod.

1817
01:06:12,400 --> 01:06:14,519
[SPEAKER_02] To smo bili mi.

1818
01:06:14,519 --> 01:06:16,659
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo su udarili na nas.

1819
01:06:16,659 --> 01:06:20,760
[SPEAKER_02] Slovačka, Češka, Ukrajina,

1820
01:06:20,760 --> 01:06:22,460
[SPEAKER_02] svi su ovoga,

1821
01:06:22,460 --> 01:06:24,840
[SPEAKER_02] Bogu fala, uživali u slobodi,

1822
01:06:24,840 --> 01:06:26,119
[SPEAKER_02] na nas se udarilo.

1823
01:06:26,119 --> 01:06:29,219
[SPEAKER_02] Kad se gleda veličina jednog naroda,

1824
01:06:29,219 --> 01:06:31,519
[SPEAKER_02] onda se gleda veličina njegovih dijela,

1825
01:06:31,519 --> 01:06:33,159
[SPEAKER_02] veličina njegovih trpljenja.

1826
01:06:33,159 --> 01:06:34,679
[SPEAKER_02] I kad se tako gleda,

1827
01:06:34,679 --> 01:06:37,719
[SPEAKER_02] ja se osjećam i širim to u mojoj obitelj,

1828
01:06:37,780 --> 01:06:39,440
[SPEAKER_02] i šire, ja se osjećam,

1829
01:06:39,440 --> 01:06:40,420
[SPEAKER_02] javno to govorim,

1830
01:06:40,420 --> 01:06:43,260
[SPEAKER_02] pripadnik velikog hrvatskog naroda

1831
01:06:43,260 --> 01:06:45,440
[SPEAKER_02] i pripadnik velike Hrvatske.

1832
01:06:45,440 --> 01:06:48,079
[SPEAKER_02] Ne veće od nekog drugog naroda.

1833
01:06:48,079 --> 01:06:48,440
[SPEAKER_02] Ne!

1834
01:06:48,440 --> 01:06:50,599
[SPEAKER_02] Za mene je moja kuća

1835
01:06:50,599 --> 01:06:52,340
[SPEAKER_02] najveća i najljepša na svijetu.

1836
01:06:52,340 --> 01:06:54,000
[SPEAKER_02] Za mene je moja domovina

1837
01:06:54,000 --> 01:06:54,760
[SPEAKER_02] i moj narod

1838
01:06:54,760 --> 01:06:56,960
[SPEAKER_02] najmili i najveći na svijetu

1839
01:06:56,960 --> 01:06:57,780
[SPEAKER_02] u svakom pogledu.

1840
01:06:57,780 --> 01:07:00,079
[SPEAKER_02] Jer veličina jednog naroda

1841
01:07:00,079 --> 01:07:01,780
[SPEAKER_02] se mjeri po ovome što sam rekao.

1842
01:07:01,780 --> 01:07:05,280
[SPEAKER_02] A stalna kukanja mi smo mali, neznak,

1843
01:07:05,280 --> 01:07:07,260
[SPEAKER_02] mi smo s Bogom veliki

1844
01:07:07,260 --> 01:07:10,039
[SPEAKER_02] i sa istinom ako branimo svoje,

1845
01:07:10,039 --> 01:07:11,099
[SPEAKER_02] a nećemo tuđe.

1846
01:07:11,099 --> 01:07:12,119
[SPEAKER_02] Evo da im,

1847
01:07:12,119 --> 01:07:13,940
[SPEAKER_02] Jovana Jovanovića Zmaja,

1848
01:07:13,940 --> 01:07:15,500
[SPEAKER_02] dobrog pisca iz Srbije,

1849
01:07:15,500 --> 01:07:17,659
[SPEAKER_02] citiram sad ovima koji kukaju

1850
01:07:17,659 --> 01:07:19,760
[SPEAKER_02] o našim budućnostima,

1851
01:07:20,559 --> 01:07:21,679
[SPEAKER_02] kaže, citiram,

1852
01:07:21,679 --> 01:07:25,880
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvat se ne bori da šta otme kome,

1853
01:07:25,880 --> 01:07:27,579
[SPEAKER_02] čuva svet i plamen

1854
01:07:27,579 --> 01:07:29,199
[SPEAKER_02] na ognjištu svome

1855
01:07:29,199 --> 01:07:31,480
[SPEAKER_02] i dok tako živi

1856
01:07:31,480 --> 01:07:33,179
[SPEAKER_02] u najteži dani

1857
01:07:33,179 --> 01:07:35,599
[SPEAKER_02] i Bog je i pravda na njegovoj strani.

1858
01:07:35,599 --> 01:07:37,480
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, on nije sumnjo

1859
01:07:37,480 --> 01:07:39,739
[SPEAKER_02] u budućnost naroda koji tako živi.

1860
01:07:39,739 --> 01:07:41,000
[SPEAKER_02] A naši ljudi,

1861
01:07:41,000 --> 01:07:42,599
[SPEAKER_02] govorimo o hrvatskim medijima,

1862
01:07:42,599 --> 01:07:44,300
[SPEAKER_02] iz neznanja,

1863
01:07:44,300 --> 01:07:46,320
[SPEAKER_02] iz tolikog pritiska,

1864
01:07:46,320 --> 01:07:48,239
[SPEAKER_02] čine tu grešku

1865
01:07:48,239 --> 01:07:50,260
[SPEAKER_02] i prenose to

1866
01:07:50,260 --> 01:07:51,940
[SPEAKER_02] i na narod

1867
01:07:51,940 --> 01:07:53,900
[SPEAKER_02] i samo umalovažavanje,

1868
01:07:53,900 --> 01:07:55,460
[SPEAKER_02] to je nešto nedopustivo.

1869
01:07:55,460 --> 01:07:56,519
[SPEAKER_02] Druga greška,

1870
01:07:56,519 --> 01:07:58,440
[SPEAKER_02] samo na brzinu ću reći,

1871
01:07:58,440 --> 01:08:01,579
[SPEAKER_02] nisu se neki odrekli nečega,

1872
01:08:01,579 --> 01:08:02,659
[SPEAKER_02] neke linije,

1873
01:08:02,659 --> 01:08:03,800
[SPEAKER_02] neki Karlovac,

1874
01:08:03,800 --> 01:08:05,699
[SPEAKER_02] pa to je smiješno.

1875
01:08:05,699 --> 01:08:08,579
[SPEAKER_02] To je ko da mi osvrtati se uopće na to.

1876
01:08:08,579 --> 01:08:10,699
[SPEAKER_02] Ko da mi kažemo u Americi

1877
01:08:10,699 --> 01:08:12,019
[SPEAKER_02] da je dio Pensilvanije naš

1878
01:08:12,019 --> 01:08:13,119
[SPEAKER_02] jer tamo živi Hrvati.

1879
01:08:13,119 --> 01:08:14,260
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

1880
01:08:14,260 --> 01:08:15,539
[SPEAKER_02] neki se ni svako,

1881
01:08:15,539 --> 01:08:16,260
[SPEAKER_02] stjedan,

1882
01:08:16,260 --> 01:08:18,199
[SPEAKER_02] nije se odrekli neke linije,

1883
01:08:18,239 --> 01:08:19,359
[SPEAKER_02] neću je ni spominjati.

1884
01:08:19,359 --> 01:08:20,640
[SPEAKER_02] I treća,

1885
01:08:20,640 --> 01:08:21,979
[SPEAKER_02] najopasnija stvar,

1886
01:08:21,979 --> 01:08:23,720
[SPEAKER_02] da Hrvatska ne brine

1887
01:08:23,720 --> 01:08:25,380
[SPEAKER_02] o svojim braniteljima,

1888
01:08:25,380 --> 01:08:26,180
[SPEAKER_02] siromasima

1889
01:08:26,180 --> 01:08:27,060
[SPEAKER_02] i udara se

1890
01:08:27,060 --> 01:08:28,239
[SPEAKER_02] i država se,

1891
01:08:28,239 --> 01:08:30,680
[SPEAKER_02] naša Hrvatska omalovažava.

1892
01:08:30,680 --> 01:08:32,720
[SPEAKER_02] Odluke ne donosi država,

1893
01:08:32,720 --> 01:08:33,840
[SPEAKER_02] ima vlada i sabro

1894
01:08:33,840 --> 01:08:34,859
[SPEAKER_02] u kojima sam govorio.

1895
01:08:34,859 --> 01:08:36,199
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvatska država

1896
01:08:36,199 --> 01:08:38,180
[SPEAKER_02] svojoj djeci daje sve što ima,

1897
01:08:38,180 --> 01:08:39,039
[SPEAKER_02] i more,

1898
01:08:39,039 --> 01:08:39,979
[SPEAKER_02] i planine,

1899
01:08:39,979 --> 01:08:41,239
[SPEAKER_02] i šume,

1900
01:08:41,239 --> 01:08:42,640
[SPEAKER_02] i sve što ima,

1901
01:08:42,640 --> 01:08:44,380
[SPEAKER_02] ona svojoj djeci daje i čuva.

1902
01:08:44,380 --> 01:08:46,619
[SPEAKER_02] Probleme i ne brigu

1903
01:08:46,619 --> 01:08:47,479
[SPEAKER_02] stvaraju oni,

1904
01:08:47,479 --> 01:08:48,520
[SPEAKER_02] one grupe

1905
01:08:48,520 --> 01:08:49,340
[SPEAKER_02] i pojedinci

1906
01:08:49,340 --> 01:08:50,399
[SPEAKER_02] koji su dobili

1907
01:08:50,399 --> 01:08:51,500
[SPEAKER_02] određene zadaće

1908
01:08:51,500 --> 01:08:52,600
[SPEAKER_02] za koje su plaćeni

1909
01:08:52,600 --> 01:08:53,380
[SPEAKER_02] da rade.

1910
01:08:53,380 --> 01:08:54,420
[SPEAKER_02] Oni ne brinu

1911
01:08:54,420 --> 01:08:56,239
[SPEAKER_02] onima o kojima bi trebalo brinuti.

1912
01:08:56,239 --> 01:08:57,720
[SPEAKER_02] A kad se spominje

1913
01:08:57,720 --> 01:08:58,739
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvatska država,

1914
01:08:58,739 --> 01:09:00,520
[SPEAKER_02] skoro pa da se treba

1915
01:09:00,520 --> 01:09:01,359
[SPEAKER_02] ustati na noge,

1916
01:09:01,359 --> 01:09:02,779
[SPEAKER_02] a ne udarati na državu,

1917
01:09:02,779 --> 01:09:04,579
[SPEAKER_02] nego na one koji čine zlo,

1918
01:09:04,579 --> 01:09:06,840
[SPEAKER_02] a podupirati one koji čine dobro.

1919
01:09:07,140 --> 01:09:09,060
[SPEAKER_02] Ali nije kriva Hrvatska država,

1920
01:09:09,060 --> 01:09:11,000
[SPEAKER_02] nego pojedinac ili grupa

1921
01:09:11,000 --> 01:09:12,720
[SPEAKER_02] koji nešto loše napravi

1922
01:09:12,720 --> 01:09:14,020
[SPEAKER_02] ili loše upravlja.

1923
01:09:14,020 --> 01:09:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] Bravo, bravo.

1924
01:09:14,720 --> 01:09:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] I oprosi,

1925
01:09:15,300 --> 01:09:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] samo da kažem još,

1926
01:09:16,319 --> 01:09:17,899
[SPEAKER_00] kad me Vinko pitao

1927
01:09:17,899 --> 01:09:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] ima li cenzure ovde,

1928
01:09:19,199 --> 01:09:20,140
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam baš rekao,

1929
01:09:20,140 --> 01:09:22,140
[SPEAKER_00] ti koji si toliko dao

1930
01:09:22,140 --> 01:09:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] i toliko daješ za domovinu,

1931
01:09:23,760 --> 01:09:25,520
[SPEAKER_00] nema nikakve cenzure,

1932
01:09:25,520 --> 01:09:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] jer znam,

1933
01:09:26,039 --> 01:09:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] i sve ove kritike koje govoriš,

1934
01:09:27,880 --> 01:09:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] i kritike prije,

1935
01:09:28,739 --> 01:09:30,140
[SPEAKER_00] i saborskim zastupnicima,

1936
01:09:30,140 --> 01:09:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] i sve,

1937
01:09:30,539 --> 01:09:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] to je biti kritika iz ljubavi,

1938
01:09:32,520 --> 01:09:34,220
[SPEAKER_00] ne govoriš ti to iz neke mržnje,

1939
01:09:34,220 --> 01:09:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] i kad bi svi tako gledali,

1940
01:09:35,899 --> 01:09:37,720
[SPEAKER_00] onda bi svi mogli otvorenije pričati,

1941
01:09:37,720 --> 01:09:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi se trebali...

1942
01:09:37,960 --> 01:09:38,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, kritiziram i sebe.

1943
01:09:38,680 --> 01:09:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, da,

1944
01:09:39,739 --> 01:09:41,060
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi se trebali ni pitati

1945
01:09:41,060 --> 01:09:42,439
[SPEAKER_00] cenzura, ne cenzura.

1946
01:09:42,439 --> 01:09:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kad čovjek govori iz ljubavi,

1947
01:09:43,880 --> 01:09:45,439
[SPEAKER_00] kad dijela potvrđuju to,

1948
01:09:45,439 --> 01:09:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] onda šiba je sve.

1949
01:09:47,619 --> 01:09:49,159
[SPEAKER_02] Kršćani nama,

1950
01:09:49,159 --> 01:09:50,739
[SPEAKER_02] i ovo još ću samo reći,

1951
01:09:50,739 --> 01:09:52,619
[SPEAKER_02] vi ližete oltare,

1952
01:09:52,619 --> 01:09:53,720
[SPEAKER_02] vi ovo i ono,

1953
01:09:53,720 --> 01:09:55,560
[SPEAKER_02] mi, nama ne trebaju oni govoriti,

1954
01:09:55,560 --> 01:09:57,800
[SPEAKER_02] mi kršćani se priznajemo

1955
01:09:57,800 --> 01:09:58,619
[SPEAKER_02] da smo mi grešnici.

1956
01:09:59,319 --> 01:10:00,579
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo grešni ljudi svi,

1957
01:10:00,579 --> 01:10:02,060
[SPEAKER_02] i ja bi volio da,

1958
01:10:02,060 --> 01:10:03,359
[SPEAKER_02] kao i svi mi,

1959
01:10:03,359 --> 01:10:05,079
[SPEAKER_02] da je stanje bolje u tu svrhu,

1960
01:10:05,079 --> 01:10:05,560
[SPEAKER_02] i govorim,

1961
01:10:05,560 --> 01:10:08,100
[SPEAKER_02] da opominjem i sebe i oko sebe.

1962
01:10:08,100 --> 01:10:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] Evo.

1963
01:10:08,380 --> 01:10:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi sam odvezano vinka,

1964
01:10:10,239 --> 01:10:11,760
[SPEAKER_01] ja znam reći,

1965
01:10:11,760 --> 01:10:13,680
[SPEAKER_01] dosta je bila umiranja

1966
01:10:13,680 --> 01:10:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] za našu svetu,

1967
01:10:14,579 --> 01:10:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] domovinu Hrvatsku,

1968
01:10:15,579 --> 01:10:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] koja je natopljena krvlju

1969
01:10:17,000 --> 01:10:17,859
[SPEAKER_01] naših mučenika

1970
01:10:17,859 --> 01:10:18,640
[SPEAKER_01] kroz povijest,

1971
01:10:18,640 --> 01:10:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] i noviju povijest,

1972
01:10:20,539 --> 01:10:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] počnemo za nju živjeti,

1973
01:10:22,960 --> 01:10:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] čineći dobro,

1974
01:10:23,800 --> 01:10:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] ljubioći je na taj način.

1975
01:10:25,260 --> 01:10:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] I jedna molitva,

1976
01:10:26,539 --> 01:10:29,140
[SPEAKER_01] prekrasna kraju ću reći,

1977
01:10:29,140 --> 01:10:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1978
01:10:29,500 --> 01:10:31,500
[SPEAKER_01] tvoj križ i moj križ.

1979
01:10:31,500 --> 01:10:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ne idi, brate,

1980
01:10:32,760 --> 01:10:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] od mene,

1981
01:10:33,119 --> 01:10:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] skupa smo jači.

1982
01:10:34,159 --> 01:10:35,779
[SPEAKER_01] Budimo jedni drugima,

1983
01:10:35,779 --> 01:10:37,239
[SPEAKER_01] Šimun Cirenac,

1984
01:10:37,239 --> 01:10:39,600
[SPEAKER_01] i pomozimo nositi

1985
01:10:39,600 --> 01:10:40,600
[SPEAKER_01] životne križeve,

1986
01:10:40,600 --> 01:10:41,199
[SPEAKER_01] posebce,

1987
01:10:41,199 --> 01:10:42,180
[SPEAKER_01] onima koji pate

1988
01:10:42,180 --> 01:10:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] u bolesti i u siromaštu.

1989
01:10:43,579 --> 01:10:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] A mi da nije bilo naše sve,

1990
01:10:46,039 --> 01:10:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] onog na nebesima,

1991
01:10:47,119 --> 01:10:48,760
[SPEAKER_01] majke Božje i mi u rovu,

1992
01:10:48,760 --> 01:10:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] i ovo, ja to zovem,

1993
01:10:50,420 --> 01:10:51,619
[SPEAKER_01] Božja puška,

1994
01:10:51,619 --> 01:10:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] krunice u rucu,

1995
01:10:52,819 --> 01:10:54,859
[SPEAKER_01] koja je nas držala na okupu i u rovu,

1996
01:10:54,859 --> 01:10:55,859
[SPEAKER_01] molili smo,

1997
01:10:55,859 --> 01:10:56,199
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1998
01:10:56,199 --> 01:10:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] kad najteže je bilo,

1999
01:10:57,460 --> 01:10:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] bez ovoga nema ništa,

2000
01:10:58,960 --> 01:11:00,220
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je najjače oružje

2001
01:11:00,220 --> 01:11:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] što ima na svijetu,

2002
01:11:01,300 --> 01:11:01,600
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

2003
01:11:01,600 --> 01:11:02,180
[SPEAKER_01] krunica,

2004
01:11:02,180 --> 01:11:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] molimo je u našoj domovini,

2005
01:11:04,039 --> 01:11:05,279
[SPEAKER_01] molimo je obitelji,

2006
01:11:05,279 --> 01:11:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] i bit će naša domovina svijeta,

2007
01:11:07,960 --> 01:11:08,880
[SPEAKER_01] a isto tako,

2008
01:11:08,880 --> 01:11:10,760
[SPEAKER_01] progledajmo dobri ljudi,

2009
01:11:10,760 --> 01:11:12,560
[SPEAKER_01] dragi braća i sestro Hrvati,

2010
01:11:12,560 --> 01:11:13,359
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

2011
01:11:13,359 --> 01:11:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] nedavno su bili izbori,

2012
01:11:14,760 --> 01:11:16,800
[SPEAKER_01] stavno na neko drugi kriv,

2013
01:11:16,800 --> 01:11:17,239
[SPEAKER_01] biran,

2014
01:11:17,239 --> 01:11:19,439
[SPEAKER_01] mi sami moramo otvoriti oči

2015
01:11:19,439 --> 01:11:20,699
[SPEAKER_01] i progledati neke stvari,

2016
01:11:20,699 --> 01:11:22,600
[SPEAKER_01] promijeniti u našoj domovini na bolje.

2017
01:11:22,600 --> 01:11:24,020
[SPEAKER_01] Puno dobra imamo uvijek,

2018
01:11:24,020 --> 01:11:25,380
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo mi koji smo u vjeri,

2019
01:11:25,380 --> 01:11:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek čovjeku gledati ono što je dobro,

2020
01:11:27,380 --> 01:11:28,439
[SPEAKER_01] a ono što ne volja,

2021
01:11:28,439 --> 01:11:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] trebamo mijenjati,

2022
01:11:29,500 --> 01:11:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] i te ljude,

2023
01:11:30,579 --> 01:11:31,380
[SPEAKER_01] tako isto,

2024
01:11:31,380 --> 01:11:32,100
[SPEAKER_01] i zakone,

2025
01:11:32,100 --> 01:11:33,520
[SPEAKER_01] zakoni su da se mijenjaju,

2026
01:11:33,520 --> 01:11:34,899
[SPEAKER_01] da budne dobro.

2027
01:11:34,899 --> 01:11:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je i krv prosuta

2028
01:11:37,000 --> 01:11:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] da ova domovina budne sveta

2029
01:11:38,920 --> 01:11:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] i da u njoj svi su sretni,

2030
01:11:40,819 --> 01:11:41,720
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo Hrvati,

2031
01:11:41,720 --> 01:11:42,020
[SPEAKER_01] svi,

2032
01:11:42,020 --> 01:11:42,899
[SPEAKER_01] kad su svi sretni,

2033
01:11:42,899 --> 01:11:44,760
[SPEAKER_01] onda je blagoslav u toj domovini.

2034
01:11:45,180 --> 01:11:49,560
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi sad samo volio malo što privodimo kraju

2035
01:11:49,560 --> 01:11:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] da vas pitan malo i s osobne strane,

2036
01:11:51,779 --> 01:11:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] vidi se i po pričama da je vama pomaganje drugima jako puno donijelo u vašem životu,

2037
01:11:57,319 --> 01:11:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali možete to malo i podijeliti s drugima.

2038
01:11:59,539 --> 01:12:04,779
[SPEAKER_00] Što pomaganje donosi i meni osobno, i mom osobnom rastu i razvoju?

2039
01:12:05,579 --> 01:12:14,399
[SPEAKER_01] Ja evo mogu reći kao hrvatski vojnik sam svoje ratne rane zalječio pomažući.

2040
01:12:14,399 --> 01:12:18,699
[SPEAKER_01] Još dok sam bio u službi znao sam često i zapaliti sviću na kamenita vrata

2041
01:12:18,699 --> 01:12:22,220
[SPEAKER_01] i gore sam susreo nekako siromaha,

2042
01:12:22,220 --> 01:12:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] posebice, evo mogu krenuti od bake,

2043
01:12:24,840 --> 01:12:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] ane koja je srema,

2044
01:12:25,920 --> 01:12:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] prognana, znači doveliš je do granice,

2045
01:12:29,340 --> 01:12:31,720
[SPEAKER_01] morala se odreći svoje imovne koja je tu domovne,

2046
01:12:31,720 --> 01:12:32,899
[SPEAKER_01] umrla nju sam susreo,

2047
01:12:33,439 --> 01:12:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] Marta koji su isto susreo na kamenitim vratima

2048
01:12:37,460 --> 01:12:39,819
[SPEAKER_01] iz privlake kod Vingovaca,

2049
01:12:39,819 --> 01:12:42,560
[SPEAKER_01] sirotica koja je tu došla i umrla isto,

2050
01:12:42,560 --> 01:12:46,560
[SPEAKER_01] evo mogu, sve su većina susretao su na ti ulicama

2051
01:12:46,560 --> 01:12:48,340
[SPEAKER_01] i njihove životne priče,

2052
01:12:48,340 --> 01:12:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] neka čovjek treba znači sasvišati,

2053
01:12:50,119 --> 01:12:51,899
[SPEAKER_01] njima je to melem na ranu

2054
01:12:51,899 --> 01:12:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] kad oni iznesu iz sebe svoje probleme,

2055
01:12:54,699 --> 01:12:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] svoje križeve koje nose.

2056
01:12:56,119 --> 01:12:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam zacijelio svoje ratne rane

2057
01:12:58,420 --> 01:13:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] s to struko sam više dobio

2058
01:13:01,300 --> 01:13:02,319
[SPEAKER_01] nego što sam dao,

2059
01:13:02,399 --> 01:13:05,520
[SPEAKER_01] i u materialnoj svojih volonterskih tišće, tišće sati

2060
01:13:05,520 --> 01:13:08,819
[SPEAKER_01] u 18 godina što sam dao za tu sirotnju,

2061
01:13:08,819 --> 01:13:11,479
[SPEAKER_01] to me kao čovjeka oplemenilo i ojačalo.

2062
01:13:11,479 --> 01:13:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] Tako isto, evo, trudim se biti svjedok

2063
01:13:14,119 --> 01:13:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] svojoj obitelji,

2064
01:13:16,699 --> 01:13:19,600
[SPEAKER_01] svoji obitelji isto tako sam uključio svu djecu

2065
01:13:19,600 --> 01:13:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] da znaju se osjećati sa onima koji pate.

2066
01:13:23,279 --> 01:13:28,479
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, puno, puno sam dobio, to se ne može ni riječma, ni izgovoriti.

2067
01:13:30,579 --> 01:13:36,779
[SPEAKER_02] Pa evo ja ću reći, Robin Harris, savjetnik engleske vlade,

2068
01:13:36,779 --> 01:13:39,840
[SPEAKER_02] Margaret Thatcher je kazao, citiram,

2069
01:13:39,840 --> 01:13:43,739
[SPEAKER_02] da je, kad je Hrvatska malo prije se rekao,

2070
01:13:43,739 --> 01:13:46,199
[SPEAKER_02] prva napadnuta slovom komunizma,

2071
01:13:46,279 --> 01:13:48,119
[SPEAKER_02] neslučajno, neslučajno.

2072
01:13:48,119 --> 01:13:52,220
[SPEAKER_02] Rekao je, kaže, neki dobar čovjek stvarno,

2073
01:13:52,220 --> 01:13:55,199
[SPEAKER_02] taj engleski savjetnik engleske vlade,

2074
01:13:55,199 --> 01:13:55,760
[SPEAKER_02] kaže,

2075
01:13:55,760 --> 01:14:00,420
[SPEAKER_02] Sjedinjen američke države,

2076
01:14:00,420 --> 01:14:02,579
[SPEAKER_02] Francuska i Engleska,

2077
01:14:02,579 --> 01:14:04,180
[SPEAKER_02] rekao bi čovjek,

2078
01:14:04,180 --> 01:14:05,359
[SPEAKER_02] ako više treba,

2079
01:14:05,359 --> 01:14:07,560
[SPEAKER_02] su, kaže, odlučile

2080
01:14:07,560 --> 01:14:10,159
[SPEAKER_02] da JNA, doslovno,

2081
01:14:10,159 --> 01:14:13,039
[SPEAKER_02] brzo uveze stabilnost

2082
01:14:13,039 --> 01:14:14,779
[SPEAKER_02] začuva Jugoslaviju.

2083
01:14:14,779 --> 01:14:17,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, sad citiram savjetnika

2084
01:14:17,460 --> 01:14:19,739
[SPEAKER_02] Evropske,

2085
01:14:19,739 --> 01:14:21,960
[SPEAKER_02] savjetnika engleske vlade,

2086
01:14:21,960 --> 01:14:24,659
[SPEAKER_02] dragi slušatelji, draga braćo i sestre,

2087
01:14:24,659 --> 01:14:26,119
[SPEAKER_02] citiram ga šta je rekao,

2088
01:14:26,119 --> 01:14:28,520
[SPEAKER_02] kaže, da brzo sredi JNA

2089
01:14:28,520 --> 01:14:30,079
[SPEAKER_02] odluka je bila

2090
01:14:30,079 --> 01:14:32,260
[SPEAKER_02] i ostane Jugoslavija,

2091
01:14:32,260 --> 01:14:33,619
[SPEAKER_02] ali kaže,

2092
01:14:33,619 --> 01:14:36,319
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati nisu pristali

2093
01:14:36,319 --> 01:14:38,359
[SPEAKER_02] biti poraženi.

2094
01:14:38,359 --> 01:14:43,159
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, plan Sjedinenih američkih država,

2095
01:14:43,159 --> 01:14:44,840
[SPEAKER_02] plan Francuzke

2096
01:14:44,840 --> 01:14:46,840
[SPEAKER_02] i plan Engleske

2097
01:14:46,840 --> 01:14:48,899
[SPEAKER_02] su razbili

2098
01:14:48,899 --> 01:14:50,479
[SPEAKER_02] Bog i Hrvati.

2099
01:14:50,479 --> 01:14:52,100
[SPEAKER_02] Zato ja i ovom prilikom

2100
01:14:52,100 --> 01:14:54,840
[SPEAKER_02] zapito si šta nam je donijela kap dobrotu.

2101
01:14:54,840 --> 01:14:57,840
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo, zahvalijem Bogu što me ovdje pozvao.

2102
01:15:00,840 --> 01:15:02,979
[SPEAKER_02] A onda naravno i roditeljima.

2103
01:15:02,979 --> 01:15:07,619
[SPEAKER_02] I došao sam ovdje iz ljubavi prema svome narodu

2104
01:15:07,619 --> 01:15:11,619
[SPEAKER_02] kao što sam tu ljubav zajedno sa svim hrvatskim braniteljima

2105
01:15:11,619 --> 01:15:15,460
[SPEAKER_02] dijelio i svjedočio u domovinskom ratu

2106
01:15:15,460 --> 01:15:19,159
[SPEAKER_02] kad smo za svoj narod dnevno mogli izginuti tisuću puta

2107
01:15:19,159 --> 01:15:21,840
[SPEAKER_02] ako je palo tisuću granata.

2108
01:15:21,840 --> 01:15:30,000
[SPEAKER_02] I najljepše stanje u kojemu čovjek može biti to je stanje ljubavi.

2109
01:15:30,000 --> 01:15:31,920
[SPEAKER_02] Nema ljepšeg stanja.

2110
01:15:31,920 --> 01:15:35,439
[SPEAKER_02] To znaju djedovi kad dignu svoje unuke i unučice,

2111
01:15:35,439 --> 01:15:39,039
[SPEAKER_02] mati kad uzme dijete, sestra kad zagrli brata.

2112
01:15:40,039 --> 01:15:43,359
[SPEAKER_02] I to stanje ljubavi preporučan svima.

2113
01:15:43,359 --> 01:15:46,340
[SPEAKER_02] Što više ljubavi, više sretniji.

2114
01:15:46,340 --> 01:15:49,920
[SPEAKER_02] Znači u ljubavi prema svom narodu, prema svojoj obitelji

2115
01:15:49,920 --> 01:15:54,079
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam sretan čovjek i doživljavam radost.

2116
01:15:54,079 --> 01:15:57,979
[SPEAKER_02] Jer je Bog tu ljubav dao kao nešto, tu smo njemu najsličniji.

2117
01:15:57,979 --> 01:16:00,539
[SPEAKER_02] Jedino smo tu neograničeni.

2118
01:16:00,539 --> 01:16:02,979
[SPEAKER_02] U svemu drugomu je čovjek ograničen.

2119
01:16:02,979 --> 01:16:06,199
[SPEAKER_02] A ljubav ja ne znam gdje može se postavi granica

2120
01:16:06,199 --> 01:16:08,079
[SPEAKER_02] i tu smo možda Bogu najsličniji.

2121
01:16:09,100 --> 01:16:16,600
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, u ovom borbi bitki ovakve vrste za moju braću i sestre,

2122
01:16:16,600 --> 01:16:18,840
[SPEAKER_02] ne moju nego našu braću i sestre,

2123
01:16:18,840 --> 01:16:27,520
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam dobio, ostvario, živim i imam ljubav njihovu prema meni

2124
01:16:27,520 --> 01:16:33,279
[SPEAKER_02] i moju prema njima i svima nam je zajedno lijepo u ljubavi koja je od Boga.

2125
01:16:33,279 --> 01:16:39,000
[SPEAKER_02] I tamo gdje je ljubav, poštovani su narodnjaci i braću i sestre,

2126
01:16:39,100 --> 01:16:44,920
[SPEAKER_02] koji slušate tamo gdje nema ljubavi, nemojte zva Boga jer njega tamo nema.

2127
01:16:46,819 --> 01:16:51,439
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno, šta na dodati, iskreno nije mi nikad lakše bilo voditi podcast,

2128
01:16:51,439 --> 01:16:56,560
[SPEAKER_00] toliko dobro sve zaokružiti da čovjek stvarno treba slušati i upijati.

2129
01:16:56,680 --> 01:17:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih rekao i isto šta bi vas vezano, zato volio pitat, sad evo neki mlada osoba,

2130
01:17:02,500 --> 01:17:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne mora biti mlada, koja želi pomoći kapi dobrote, evo sad ovo sluša i tjela bi se uključiti,

2131
01:17:10,199 --> 01:17:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] što sve ona može raditi, što sve, čime ona sve može doprinijeti osim donacijama?

2132
01:17:18,399 --> 01:17:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dragi ljudi, priključite se, mladi, pogotovo, evo mi probamo ponovo,

2133
01:17:23,460 --> 01:17:26,859
[SPEAKER_01] evo i danas spremamo, neki dan smo na upravnu odbor odlučivali,

2134
01:17:26,859 --> 01:17:30,939
[SPEAKER_01] da pošaljemo pismo ponovo svim dekanima u Zagrebu, u fakultetima,

2135
01:17:30,939 --> 01:17:36,739
[SPEAKER_01] da nas pozovu da budemo njihovi gosti, da naši članovi iz kapi dobrote posvjedoče

2136
01:17:36,739 --> 01:17:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] ko smo mi, što smo, čime se bavimo, kome pomažemo.

2137
01:17:39,880 --> 01:17:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki naš čovjek koji dođe u kap dobrote, puno je prošlo koz udrugu,

2138
01:17:47,020 --> 01:17:50,279
[SPEAKER_01] neki su došli, nisu mogli zdržati u tim uvjetima tu,

2139
01:17:50,279 --> 01:17:53,779
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno treba imati želodac, ulaziti u te podrume,

2140
01:17:53,779 --> 01:17:57,319
[SPEAKER_01] neko može pomagati materialno, neko dođe na teren,

2141
01:17:57,319 --> 01:18:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] isijepati drva, odnijeti hranu, otići u ljekarnu, donijeti ljekove,

2142
01:18:01,819 --> 01:18:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] pratnja kad idu na te svoje preglede, puno toga ima.

2143
01:18:05,239 --> 01:18:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] Puno puta ti ljudi traže samo razgovor, samoća strašno ubilja.

2144
01:18:09,880 --> 01:18:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] Najteži dani to mogu posvjedočiti našim siromasima,

2145
01:18:13,579 --> 01:18:15,939
[SPEAKER_01] štićenicima naše udruge su blagdani.

2146
01:18:16,640 --> 01:18:21,319
[SPEAKER_01] Svi nekoga očekuju, prijatelje, rodbinu, ta samoća strašna.

2147
01:18:21,319 --> 01:18:25,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je suza i plać, kad odješ, ja se trudim svake godine sa obitelji,

2148
01:18:25,340 --> 01:18:29,399
[SPEAKER_01] obići na sam blagdan i na Božić, na uskštiti do nekoga,

2149
01:18:29,399 --> 01:18:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] da i malo podignemo, da i ustrećemo,

2150
01:18:32,119 --> 01:18:35,399
[SPEAKER_01] da oni vide da nisu ostavljeni, da nisu zaboravljeni.

2151
01:18:35,680 --> 01:18:39,399
[SPEAKER_01] Na puno načina se može pomoći, evo, dođite, priključite se,

2152
01:18:39,399 --> 01:18:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] možete biti podupiratelji, možete biti članovi,

2153
01:18:43,000 --> 01:18:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] znači, kapi dobrote, zakon o volontiranju ima,

2154
01:18:46,659 --> 01:18:49,060
[SPEAKER_01] možete vidjeti to na internetu i tako dalje,

2155
01:18:49,060 --> 01:18:51,020
[SPEAKER_01] potpisuje se ugovor i tako dalje.

2156
01:18:51,020 --> 01:18:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] Na puno načina se može, da li je to kap dobrote,

2157
01:18:54,079 --> 01:18:57,819
[SPEAKER_01] da li su to neka udruga, bilo gdje samo pomozite,

2158
01:18:57,939 --> 01:19:01,560
[SPEAKER_01] onima, najmanjima, da li su to djeca, da li su to stari,

2159
01:19:01,560 --> 01:19:05,579
[SPEAKER_01] i stari i madi su potrebiti, znači, ljudske dobrote.

2160
01:19:05,579 --> 01:19:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, na bilo koji način.

2161
01:19:07,300 --> 01:19:09,020
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što treba još jednom na glas,

2162
01:19:09,020 --> 01:19:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] nema nikakvog pritiska, nema nikakve norme,

2163
01:19:11,819 --> 01:19:14,699
[SPEAKER_01] znači, sve dobra voja.

2164
01:19:14,699 --> 01:19:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedna obitelj, evo, mi smo članovi kapi dobrote,

2165
01:19:18,619 --> 01:19:21,060
[SPEAKER_01] smo kao jedna obitelj, imamo i druženje,

2166
01:19:21,060 --> 01:19:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] dva puta godišnje sa našim siromasima za Božić

2167
01:19:24,380 --> 01:19:27,060
[SPEAKER_01] i za usk smisu i druženje,

2168
01:19:27,060 --> 01:19:30,199
[SPEAKER_01] a evo, tako, trudimo se na sve načine

2169
01:19:30,199 --> 01:19:33,319
[SPEAKER_01] da i nekako lakšamo nositi njihove životne križeve.

2170
01:19:33,319 --> 01:19:37,720
[SPEAKER_00] A evo, onda smo došli polako do samog kraja,

2171
01:19:37,720 --> 01:19:41,560
[SPEAKER_00] ako nema još neke teme koje bi vi voljeli pokriti,

2172
01:19:41,560 --> 01:19:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] osim možda završenih riječi.

2173
01:19:43,859 --> 01:19:46,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pa evo, završenu riječ ću ja reći,

2174
01:19:46,960 --> 01:19:50,739
[SPEAKER_02] ne moju, nego ja bi za sve nas i za naše gledatelje

2175
01:19:50,739 --> 01:19:52,880
[SPEAKER_02] citirao Isusa Hrista.

2176
01:19:52,880 --> 01:19:56,699
[SPEAKER_02] Svi slušamo u našim crkvama,

2177
01:19:56,899 --> 01:19:58,899
[SPEAKER_02] svi slušamo u našim kućama,

2178
01:19:58,899 --> 01:20:00,260
[SPEAKER_02] u našim društima,

2179
01:20:00,260 --> 01:20:02,159
[SPEAKER_02] kako će Isus doći drugi put

2180
01:20:02,159 --> 01:20:04,880
[SPEAKER_02] i čak da su ovo sad posljednja vremena,

2181
01:20:04,880 --> 01:20:08,319
[SPEAKER_02] što ja ne znam, jesu, jer je Isus rekao da to samo zna Otac.

2182
01:20:08,319 --> 01:20:13,439
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ću završiti s njegovim riječima koje će on uputiti kad dođe.

2183
01:20:13,439 --> 01:20:17,779
[SPEAKER_02] Jer je on rekao da će to reći i da će nas tako odrediti.

2184
01:20:20,779 --> 01:20:24,399
[SPEAKER_02] Najljepšu rečenicu koju je on, riječi koju je rekao ljudskom rodu,

2185
01:20:24,399 --> 01:20:26,020
[SPEAKER_02] ja bolje ne znam,

2186
01:20:26,020 --> 01:20:29,760
[SPEAKER_02] glasa ovako kad dođe da će nama naš Isus reći.

2187
01:20:29,760 --> 01:20:31,920
[SPEAKER_02] Najljepše riječi.

2188
01:20:32,340 --> 01:20:34,819
[SPEAKER_02] Dođite blagoslovljeni Otca mojega.

2189
01:20:34,819 --> 01:20:36,640
[SPEAKER_02] To govori Isus, ne ja.

2190
01:20:36,640 --> 01:20:40,180
[SPEAKER_02] I primite u posjet kraljevstvo

2191
01:20:40,180 --> 01:20:44,380
[SPEAKER_02] koje je za vas pripravljeno od postanka svijeta.

2192
01:20:44,380 --> 01:20:47,399
[SPEAKER_02] Znači kaj je Bog stvorio svijet,

2193
01:20:47,399 --> 01:20:48,979
[SPEAKER_02] kaže Isus, a vas si dopril.

2194
01:20:48,979 --> 01:20:50,119
[SPEAKER_02] Ko su ti?

2195
01:20:50,119 --> 01:20:54,640
[SPEAKER_02] Kaže, to su oni koji su kad sam bio gladan meni dali jesti.

2196
01:20:54,640 --> 01:20:57,359
[SPEAKER_02] Kad sam bio žedan dali su mi piti.

2197
01:20:57,359 --> 01:20:59,819
[SPEAKER_02] Kad sam bio golo bukli su me.

2198
01:20:59,819 --> 01:21:02,420
[SPEAKER_02] Kad sam bio bolestan pohodili su me.

2199
01:21:02,420 --> 01:21:06,840
[SPEAKER_02] Kad sam bio u zatvoru obilazili su me.

2200
01:21:06,840 --> 01:21:08,439
[SPEAKER_02] To govori Isus Hrist.

2201
01:21:08,439 --> 01:21:12,880
[SPEAKER_02] Znači to je nešto najviše po njegovim, po božijim mjerilima

2202
01:21:12,880 --> 01:21:16,020
[SPEAKER_02] što može mlad i star čovjek napraviti.

2203
01:21:16,020 --> 01:21:20,060
[SPEAKER_02] Pomoć gladnome, pomoć žednome i čovjeku ne voli.

2204
01:21:20,060 --> 01:21:23,220
[SPEAKER_02] A onda Isus Hrist kaže

2205
01:21:23,220 --> 01:21:26,399
[SPEAKER_02] da će ovim drugim ljudima reći na žalost.

2206
01:21:26,399 --> 01:21:29,319
[SPEAKER_02] Odlazi, nema gore riječi,

2207
01:21:29,380 --> 01:21:32,760
[SPEAKER_02] da ne znam, u hrvatskom riječniku imali gore riječi.

2208
01:21:32,760 --> 01:21:35,279
[SPEAKER_02] Odlazite od mene prokleti.

2209
01:21:35,279 --> 01:21:38,899
[SPEAKER_02] Jer bio sam gladan, a niste mi dali jesti.

2210
01:21:38,899 --> 01:21:39,960
[SPEAKER_02] A mogli ste.

2211
01:21:39,960 --> 01:21:42,739
[SPEAKER_02] Sigurno ne misli na one koji nisu mogli.

2212
01:21:42,739 --> 01:21:45,359
[SPEAKER_02] Bio sam žedan, niste mi dali piti.

2213
01:21:45,359 --> 01:21:48,520
[SPEAKER_02] Bio sam gol, niste me obukli.

2214
01:21:48,520 --> 01:21:52,199
[SPEAKER_02] Bolestan, niste me pohodili u zatvoru, niste me obilazili.

2215
01:21:52,199 --> 01:22:07,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ako to o čemu govorimo večeras najvećim smatra Bog i najtežim, ako se to ne radi i ne pomaže bliži u nevolji, ja bi s time završio i tome više ne bi dodalo ništa.

2216
01:22:07,579 --> 01:22:18,760
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja ću kratko, činimo dobro, dobro se dobrim, vraća, zemljo Hrvatska, Bog te blagosovio, ljubimo našu dumovinu.

2217
01:22:19,460 --> 01:22:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] Bravo, evo, svaka čast, puno vam fala još jednom.

2218
01:22:22,659 --> 01:22:35,680
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno mi je drago da ste došli tu, a i što sam rekao na početku, drago mi je da vas mogu zvat prijateljima i dok ima ovakvih ljudi, dok ima ovako dobrih primjera, mislim da ne trebamo se ničeg bojati.

2219
01:22:35,680 --> 01:22:45,439
[SPEAKER_00] A vas, naravno ljudi, pozivam da se što više uključite i da sve ovo što su Marinko i Vinko pričali probate na svoj život primijeniti.

2220
01:22:45,439 --> 01:22:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, prvo onom najbližem do sebe pomozite, a za one koji to nisu u mogućnosti, ostavit ćemo također u opisu videa i ban od kapi dobrote,

2221
01:22:56,260 --> 01:23:05,699
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto tako od naše udruge, sada kada surađujemo, nećete pogriješiti jer sve ovo ne radimo za svoju korist, nego za Božju korist.

2222
01:23:05,699 --> 01:23:08,220
[SPEAKER_02] I naših bližnjih, naše braće i sestare.

2223
01:23:08,220 --> 01:23:19,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi na kraju poklonio jedan krijež, zove se krijež prijateljstva, jedna simbolika našim prijateljima, mladima za domovinu.

2224
01:23:19,319 --> 01:23:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on je jedan znak prijateljstva, to je ručni rad moj.

2225
01:23:22,880 --> 01:23:25,380
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti puno, evo ruka, evo ruka.

2226
01:23:25,380 --> 01:23:35,979
[SPEAKER_01] Da vas Bog blagoslovi, evo, budite naše svjetlo u ovoj tami koje puno ima, ali ima i puno dobra, znači činite dobro i naprijed.

2227
01:23:35,979 --> 01:23:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala puno i evo, svima Boži blagoslov i živjeli.

2228
01:23:44,380 --> 01:24:08,199
[UNKNOWN] Top 10 najboljih prijateljstva.

